#: templates/home/index.html:224
msgid ""
"International faculty exchange program expands to 15 new partner "
"universities"
msgstr ""
"Xalqaro professor-o'qituvchilar almashinuvi dasturi 15 ta yangi hamkor "
"universitetga kengaydi"

#: templates/home/index.html:225
msgid ""
"TIU has signed new agreements with universities across Europe and Asia, "
"expanding opportunities for faculty and student exchanges..."
msgstr ""
"TIU Yevropa va Osiyo bo'ylab universitetlar bilan yangi shartnomalar "
"imzoladi, professor-o'qituvchilar va talabalar almashinuvi imkoniyatlarini "
"kengaytirdi..."

#: templates/home/index.html:236
msgid ""
"TIU students showcase innovation at annual technology and entrepreneurship "
"fair"
msgstr ""
"TIU talabalari yillik texnologiya va tadbirkorlik ko'rgazmasida "
"innovatsiyalarni namoyish etdi"

#: templates/home/index.html:237
msgid ""
"Over 50 student projects were presented at the annual fair, featuring "
"solutions in AI, sustainability, and social impact..."
msgstr ""
"Yillik ko'rgazmada 50 dan ortiq talaba loyihasi taqdim etildi, sun'iy "
"intellekt, barqaror rivojlanish va ijtimoiy ta'sir bo'yicha yechimlar..."

#: templates/home/index.html:254
msgid "Your Gateway to Global Education."
msgstr "Global ta'limga yo'lingiz."

#: templates/home/index.html:256
msgid ""
"TIU is a modern university in Tashkent founded in 2023, offering "
"international partnerships, a 2+2 dual degree program, and a campus equipped"
" with the latest technology. We build a solid foundation for your success. "
"Start your future today — join TIU."
msgstr ""
"TIU — 2023-yilda tashkil etilgan Toshkentdagi zamonaviy universitet. Xalqaro"
" hamkorliklar, 2+2 qo'shma diplom dasturi va zamonaviy texnologiyalar bilan "
"jihozlangan kampus. Muvaffaqiyatingiz uchun mustahkam poydevor yaratamiz. "
"Kelajagingizni bugundan boshlang — TIUga qo'shiling."

#: templates/home/index.html:260
msgid "Schedule a Visit"
msgstr "Tashrif rejalashtirish"

#: templates/home/index.html:271
msgid ""
"Our unique dual degree program offers you the best of both worlds. Spend "
"your first two years at TIU in Tashkent, then complete your studies at one "
"of our prestigious partner universities abroad. Graduate with two "
"internationally recognized degrees that open doors to global career "
"opportunities. This is education without boundaries."
msgstr ""
"Bizning noyob qo'shma diplom dasturimiz sizga ikki dunyoning eng yaxshisini "
"taklif etadi. Birinchi ikki yilni Toshkentdagi TIUda o'tkazing, so'ngra "
"o'qishingizni xorijdagi nufuzli hamkor universitetlardan birida yakunlang. "
"Xalqaro karyera imkoniyatlarini ochadigan ikkita xalqaro tan olingan diplom "
"bilan bitiring. Bu chegarasiz ta'limdir."

#: templates/home/index.html:272
msgid "Explore Programs"
msgstr "Dasturlarni ko'rish"

#: templates/home/index.html:281
msgid "Five Dynamic"
msgstr "Beshta dinamik"

#: templates/home/index.html:282
msgid ""
"Choose from four cutting-edge departments: Business for future entrepreneurs"
" and economists, Education for tomorrow's teachers and leaders, IT for tech "
"innovators, and Foreign Languages for global communicators. Each department "
"offers bachelor's and master's programs taught entirely in English by "
"international faculty."
msgstr ""
"To'rtta ilg'or kafedradan tanlang: kelajakdagi tadbirkorlar va iqtisodchilar"
" uchun Biznes, ertangi o'qituvchilar va yetakchilar uchun Ta'lim, "
"texnologiya innovatorlari uchun IT va global muloqotchilar uchun Chet "
"tillari. Har bir kafedra xalqaro professor-o'qituvchilar tomonidan to'liq "
"ingliz tilida o'qitiladigan bakalavr va magistratura dasturlarini taklif "
"etadi."

#: templates/home/index.html:283
msgid "View Departments"
msgstr "Kafedralarni ko'rish"

#: templates/home/index.html:292
msgid "Student Life"
msgstr "Talaba hayoti"

#: templates/home/index.html:292
msgid "& Culture"
msgstr "va madaniyat"

#: templates/home/index.html:293
msgid ""
"At TIU, education goes beyond the classroom. Join 50+ student clubs, "
"participate in sports tournaments, cultural festivals, and hackathons. Our "
"students organize TEDx events, volunteer projects, and international "
"exchange programs. TIU is not just a university — it's a community where you"
" grow as a leader and build lifelong friendships."
msgstr ""
"TIUda ta'lim dars xonasi bilan chegaralanmaydi. 50 dan ortiq talabalar "
"klubiga qo'shiling, sport musobaqalari, madaniy festivallar va hakatonlarda "
"ishtirok eting. Talabalarimiz TEDx tadbirlari, ko'ngillilik loyihalari va "
"xalqaro almashinuv dasturlarini tashkil qiladi. TIU shunchaki universitet "
"emas — bu yetakchi sifatida o'sishingiz va umrbod do'stliklar qurishingiz "
"uchun jamiyatdir."

#: templates/home/index.html:294
msgid "Discover Student Life"
msgstr "Talaba hayotini kashf eting"

#: templates/home/index.html:313
msgid "Explore Campus"
msgstr "Kampusni ko'rish"

#: templates/home/index.html:310
msgid "Study in the Heart of Tashkent."
msgstr "Toshkent markazida o'qing."

#: templates/home/index.html:311
msgid ""
"Our campus at Little Ring Road 7 is located in the very center of Tashkent —"
" just minutes from Amir Temur Square, the National Library, and major metro "
"stations. Modern lecture halls, coworking spaces, a well-equipped library, "
"and comfortable rest areas create the perfect environment for productive "
"learning. Cafes, parks, and cultural landmarks surround the campus, making "
"student life convenient and inspiring."
msgstr ""
"Kichik halqa yo'li 7-dagi kampusimiz Toshkentning aynan markazida joylashgan"
" — Amir Temur maydoniga, Milliy kutubxonaga va yirik metro bekatlariga bir "
"necha daqiqalik masofada. Zamonaviy ma'ruza zallari, kovorking maydonlari, "
"yaxshi jihozlangan kutubxona va qulay dam olish hududlari samarali o'qish "
"uchun mukammal muhit yaratadi. Kampus atrofidagi kafelar, parklar va madaniy"
" obidalar talaba hayotini qulay va ilhomlantiruvchi qiladi."

#: templates/home/index.html:314
msgid "Book a Visit"
msgstr "Tashrif buyurish"

