#: templates/home/index.html:403
msgid ""
"Join leading researchers, academics, and industry leaders for a day of "
"groundbreaking presentations, panel discussions, and networking at TIU's "
"flagship annual research conference."
msgstr ""
"TIUning yillik ilmiy konferensiyasida yetakchi tadqiqotchilar, akademiklar "
"va sanoat yetakchilari bilan inqilobiy taqdimotlar, panel muhokamalar va "
"networking kunida ishtirok eting."

