msgid ""
"Our unique dual degree program offers you the best of both worlds. Spend "
"your first two years at TIU in Tashkent, then complete your studies at one "
"of our prestigious partner universities abroad. Graduate with two "
"internationally recognized degrees that open doors to global career "
"opportunities."
msgstr ""
"Noyob qo'shma diplom dasturimiz ikki dunyoning eng yaxshisini taklif etadi. "
"Birinchi ikki yilni TIU da o'tkazib, o'qishingizni xorijdagi sherik "
"universitetlardan birida yakunlang."

msgid "Five dynamic faculties,"
msgstr "Beshta dinamik fakultet,"

msgid "one bold vision."
msgstr "bitta jasur qarash."

msgid ""
"Choose from cutting-edge departments: Business for future entrepreneurs, "
"Education for tomorrow's teachers, IT for tech innovators, Foreign Languages"
" for global communicators, and Jurisprudence for legal minds. Each offers "
"programs taught by international faculty."
msgstr ""
"Ilg'or fakultetlardan tanlang: kelajak tadbirkorlar uchun Biznes, ertangi "
"o'qituvchilar uchun Pedagogika, texnologik innovatorlar uchun IT, global "
"muloqotchilar uchun Xorijiy tillar va huquqchilar uchun Huquqshunoslik."

msgid "More than lectures —"
