"50+ talabalar klublariga qo'shiling, sport musobaqalari, madaniy festivallar"
" va hakatonlarda ishtirok eting. TIU nafaqat universitet — bu umrbod "
"do'stlik qurish jamoasi."

msgid ""
"Our campus is in the center of Tashkent — minutes from Amir Temur Square and"
" major metro stations. Modern lecture halls, coworking spaces, and a well-"
"equipped library create the perfect environment for learning."
