#: templates/home/index.html
msgid "BACHELOR'S DEGREE"
msgstr "BAKALAVR DARAJASI"

#: templates/home/index.html
msgid "MASTER'S DEGREE"
msgstr "MAGISTR DARAJASI"

#: templates/home/index.html
msgid "PhD & DOCTORAL"
msgstr "PhD va DOKTORANTURA"

msgid "NEWS"
msgstr "YANGILIKLAR"

msgid "Admissions & International"
msgstr "Qabul va Xalqaro"

msgid "Clubs & Sports"
msgstr "Klublar va Sport"

msgid ""
"Tashkent International University is a modern university founded in 2023 "
"with a mission to provide world-class education in the heart of Uzbekistan. "
"With international partnerships, a unique 2+2 dual degree program, and a "
"campus built for the future — TIU gives you the tools and environment to "
"succeed. Whether you're starting your bachelor's or advancing through a "
"master's or PhD, your journey to a global career begins here."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent Xalqaro Universiteti — 2023-yilda O'zbekiston poytaxtida jahon "
"darajasidagi ta'lim berish maqsadida tashkil etilgan zamonaviy universitet. "
"Xalqaro hamkorliklar, noyob 2+2 qo'shma diplom dasturi va kelajak uchun "
"qurilgan kampus — TIU sizga muvaffaqiyatga erishish uchun barcha "
"imkoniyatlarni beradi. Bakalavr, magistratura yoki doktorantura — global "
"karyerangiz shu yerdan boshlanadi."

msgid ""
"Our campus on Little Ring Road is right in the center of Tashkent — just "
"minutes from Amir Temur Square, the National Library, and major metro "
"stations. You'll find modern lecture halls, coworking spaces, a fully "
"equipped library, and comfortable study areas all in one place. The "
"surrounding cafes, parks, and cultural landmarks make campus life both "
"convenient and inspiring."
msgstr ""
"Kichik Halqa yo'lidagi kampusimiz Toshkent markazida joylashgan — Amir Temur"
" maydonidan, Milliy kutubxonadan va asosiy metro bekatlaridan bir necha "
"daqiqa masofada. Zamonaviy auditoriyalar, kovorking maydonchalar, to'liq "
"jihozlangan kutubxona va qulay o'quv xonalari — barchasi bir joyda. "
"Atrofdagi kafelar, bog'lar va madaniy diqqatga sazovor joylar talaba "
"hayotini qulaylashtiradi."

msgid ""
"Discover Tashkent International University — a young, ambitious university "
"in the heart of Uzbekistan, built for the next generation of global "
"professionals."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent xalqaro universiteti — O'zbekiston poytaxtida joylashgan, "
"kelajakning global mutaxassislarini tayyorlash uchun tashkil etilgan yosh va"
" shijoatli universitet."

msgid "One campus. One city. A world of opportunity."
msgstr "Bitta kampus. Bitta shahar. Imkoniyatlar dunyosi."

msgid ""
"Founded in 2023, Tashkent International University brings together students "
"from across Uzbekistan and beyond. From your very first day, you become part"
" of a supportive academic community where you can challenge yourself, "
"discover new interests, and prepare for a career without borders. At TIU, "
"your potential has no limits."
msgstr ""
"2023-yilda tashkil etilgan Toshkent xalqaro universiteti O'zbekistonning "
"turli burchaklaridan va xorijdan talabalarni bir saqlash ostiga jamlaydi. "
"Birinchi kuningizdan boshlab siz o'zingizni sinash, yangi qiziqishlar kashf "
"etish va chegaralarni tan olmaydigan karera qurishga imkon beradigan "
"do'stona akademik jamoaning a'zosiga aylanasiz. TIUda sizning salohiyatingiz"
" cheksiz."

msgid "A modern campus designed for your success"
msgstr "Muvaffaqiyatingiz uchun yaratilgan zamonaviy kampus"

msgid ""
"Located on Little Ring Road in central Tashkent, our campus features modern "
"lecture halls, coworking spaces, a fully equipped library, computer labs, "
"and comfortable rest areas. Everything you need for productive learning and "
"a vibrant student life — all in one place."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent markazida, Kichik halqa yo'lida joylashgan kampusimizda zamonaviy "
"ma'ruza zallari, kovorking maydonlari, to'liq jihozlangan kutubxona, "
"kompyuter laboratoriyalari va qulay dam olish hududlari mavjud. Samarali "
"ta'lim va faol talabalar hayoti uchun zarur bo'lgan hamma narsa — bir joyda."

msgid "Live close to where you learn."
msgstr "O'qiydigan joyingizga yaqin yashang."

msgid ""
"TIU helps students find comfortable accommodation near campus. Whether it's "
"a university-recommended hostel or a shared apartment nearby, you'll never "
"be far from your lectures, the library, or your friends. We're here to help "
"you settle in quickly so you can focus on what matters — your studies."
msgstr ""
"TIU talabalarga kampus yaqinida qulay turar joy topishda yordam beradi. "
"Universitet tavsiya etgan yotoqxona yoki yaqin atrofdagi sherikli kvartira "
"bo'lsin — siz hech qachon darslar, kutubxona va do'stlaringizdan uzoqda "
"bo'lmaysiz. Biz sizga tezroq joylashishingizga ko'maklashamiz, shunda siz "
"eng muhim narsaga — o'qishga e'tiboringizni qarata olasiz."

msgid "A city that feels like home from day one"
msgstr "Birinchi kundan uyingizdek his qiladigan shahar"

msgid ""
"Tashkent is one of the most affordable and welcoming capital cities in "
"Central Asia. Safe streets, excellent public transport, diverse food, and a "
"growing international community make it easy to settle in. From the Old City"
" bazaars to modern shopping centers, Tashkent offers something for everyone."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent — Markaziy Osiyodagi eng qulay va mehmon do'st poytaxtlardan biri. "
"Xavfsiz ko'chalar, rivojlangan jamoat transporti, rang-barang taomlar va "
"tobora kengayib borayotgan xalqaro jamoa — bularning barchasi shaharga tez "
"ko'nikishingizga yordam beradi. Eski shahar bozorlaridan zamonaviy savdo "
"markazlarigacha — Toshkentda har kim uchun o'z joyi bor."

msgid "Your voice matters — let's make it heard."
msgstr "Sizning ovozingiz muhim — uni eshittiramiz."

msgid ""
"Every TIU student is automatically a member of the Student Union. It's your "
"platform to propose ideas, organize events, and represent student interests."
" From academic feedback to social initiatives, the Union is where your voice"
" shapes university life."
msgstr ""
"Har bir TIU talabasi avtomatik ravishda Talabalar ittifoqining a'zosi "
"hisoblanadi. Bu — g'oyalar ilgari surish, tadbirlar tashkil etish va "
"talabalar manfaatlarini ifodalash uchun sizning platformangiz. Akademik "
"fikr-mulohazalardan ijtimoiy tashabbuslargacha — ittifoq sizning ovozingiz "
"universitet hayotini shakllantiradigan joydir."

msgid "Stay active, stay sharp."
msgstr "Faol bo'ling, doim tayyor bo'ling."

msgid ""
"Our sports facilities include a modern gym, a multi-court sports hall, and "
"outdoor pitches. Join university sports teams, take part in inter-university"
" tournaments, or simply stay fit between lectures. Sport at TIU is for "
"everyone."
msgstr ""
"Sport inshootlarimiz zamonaviy trenajyor zali, ko'p tarmoqli sport zali va "
"ochiq sport maydonchalarini o'z ichiga oladi. Universitet sport jamoalariga "
"qo'shiling, universitetlararo musobaqalarda ishtirok eting yoki darslar "
"orasida shunchaki jismoniy shaklda bo'ling. TIUda sport — hamma uchun."

msgid "Find your people, find your passion."
msgstr "O'z jamoangizni toping, qiziqishingizni kashf eting."

msgid ""
"With 50+ clubs — from debate and photography to coding and chess — there's "
"something for everyone. Clubs are student-led and open to all. It's where "
"friendships form, skills develop, and university memories are made."
msgstr ""
"50 dan ortiq klub — munozara va fotografiyadan dasturlash va shaxmatgacha — "
"har kim uchun o'z joyi bor. Klublar talabalar tomonidan boshqariladi va "
"hamma uchun ochiq. Bu yerda do'stliklar paydo bo'ladi, ko'nikmalar "
"rivojlanadi va universitet xotiralari yaratiladi."

msgid "One day that launches a lifetime."
msgstr "Butun hayotingizni o'zgartiradigan kun."

msgid ""
"Your graduation from TIU marks the beginning of a new chapter. It's a "
"celebration of your hard work, dedication, and growth. As a TIU graduate, "
"you join a growing network of alumni making an impact in Uzbekistan and "
"around the world."
msgstr ""
"TIUni tugatganingiz — yangi bobning boshlanishi. Bu sizning mehnatingiz, "
"fidoyiligingiz va o'sishingizning bayramidir. TIU bitiruvchisi sifatida siz "
"O'zbekistonda va butun dunyoda o'z izini qoldirayotgan bitiruvchilar "
"tarmog'iga qo'shilasiz."

msgid "See TIU before you get here."
msgstr "Kelishdan oldin TIU ni virtual tarzda ko'ring."

msgid ""
"Curious about TIU but can't visit in person? Take our virtual campus tour — "
"explore the lecture halls, library, student spaces, and surroundings from "
"the comfort of your home. It's the next best thing to being here."
msgstr ""
"TIU haqida qiziqyapsiz, lekin shaxsan tashrif buyura olmaysizmi? Virtual "
"kampus sayohatimizdan foydalaning — ma'ruza zallari, kutubxona, talabalar "
"makonlari va atrofni uyingizdan turib ko'rib chiqing. Bu — bu yerda "
"bo'lishning eng yaqin muqobili."

msgid "Start your virtual tour"
msgstr "Virtual turni boshlang"

msgid "Talk to Students"
msgstr "Talabalar bilan suhbatlashing"

msgid "Hear it from those who know."
msgstr "Biladiganlardan eshiting."

msgid ""
"Want the real story? Chat with current TIU students about what life is "
"actually like — from academics and social life to settling in and finding "
"your way around Tashkent. They've been where you are."
msgstr ""
"Haqiqiy hikoyani bilmoqchimisiz? Hozirgi TIU talabalari bilan suhbatlashing "
"— o'qishdan tortib ijtimoiy hayotgacha, Toshkentda joylashish va shaharni "
"o'rganishgacha. Ular ham aynan sizning o'rningizda bo'lishgan."

msgid "Get in touch"
msgstr "Bog'lanish"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"Shaping the future through education, innovation, and global partnerships "
"that empower the next generation of leaders."
msgstr ""
"Ta'lim, innovatsiya va global hamkorliklar orqali kelajakni shakllantiramiz "
"— yangi avlod yetakchilarini tayyorlaymiz."

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "Together on the frontier of education's future"
msgstr "Ta'lim kelajagining chegarasida — birga"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"TIU Strategy 2030 is our roadmap for the next decade — a bold plan to become"
" Central Asia's most internationally connected university. It sets out how "
"we will expand global partnerships, pioneer dual-degree pathways, and "
"empower every student to build a career without borders."
msgstr ""
"TIU Strategiya 2030 — kelgusi o'n yillik uchun yo'l xaritamiz. Markaziy "
"Osiyoning eng xalqaro universitetiga aylanish bo'yicha jasur reja. U global "
"hamkorliklarni kengaytirish, qo'shma diplom yo'nalishlarini rivojlantirish "
"va har bir talabaga chegarasiz karyera qurish imkoniyatini berishni "
"belgilaydi."

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"From strengthening research and innovation to deepening our ties with "
"industry and communities, Strategy 2030 defines who we are, where we're "
"heading, and how we'll get there — together."
msgstr ""
"Tadqiqot va innovatsiyalarni mustahkamlashdan tortib sanoat va jamiyat bilan"
" aloqalarimizni chuqurlashtirishgacha — Strategiya 2030 biz kim "
"ekanligimizni, qayerga yo'l olayotganimizni va qanday erishishimizni "
"belgilaydi — birga."

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "Download Strategy 2030"
msgstr "Strategiya 2030 ni yuklab olish"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr "Bizning missiyamiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "An exceptional education for the"
msgstr "Barchaga ajoyib ta'lim —"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "many"
msgstr "ko'pchilik uchun"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "Our mission, as established in our founding charter, is to:"
msgstr "Ta'sis yoziqlashuvimizda belgilangan missiyamiz:"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"...advance education, bridge cultures, and empower students through world-"
"class teaching and global partnerships, for the benefit of individuals, "
"Uzbekistan, and the world."
msgstr ""
"...ta'limni rivojlantirish, madaniyatlarni bog'lash va jahon darajasidagi "
"ta'lim va global hamkorliklar orqali talabalarni kuchaytirish — shaxslar, "
"O'zbekiston va butun dunyo manfaati uchun."

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"We believe where you're from shouldn't decide how far you can go. At TIU, "
"it's more about what you know than who you know. And everyone is empowered "
"to achieve in their own way."
msgstr ""
"Biz qayerdan kelganingiz qanchalik uzoqqa borishingizni belgilamasligi kerak"
" deb ishonamiz. TIUda kimni tanishingizdan ko'ra nimani bilishingiz "
"muhimroq. Har bir inson o'z yo'lida muvaffaqiyatga erishishga qodir."

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"As one of Uzbekistan's pioneering international universities, we have a bold"
" commitment to academic excellence and a vision of creating life-changing "
"opportunities through education. We'll build on this foundation to fulfil "
"our strategy."
msgstr ""
"O'zbekistonning yetakchi xalqaro universitetlaridan biri sifatida biz "
"akademik mukammallikka sodiqmiz va ta'lim orqali hayotni o'zgartiruvchi "
"imkoniyatlar yaratish haqidagi tasavvurimiz bor. Strategiyamizni amalga "
"oshirish uchun shu poydevorni mustahkamlaymiz."

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "Our Vision"
msgstr "Bizning ko'zlagan maqsadimiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "Shaping a brighter, bolder future"
msgstr "Yorqinroq va jasurroq kelajakni shakllantiramiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "for all"
msgstr "barcha uchun"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"The world is more connected than ever, yet access to quality education "
"remains unequal. Think of the barriers facing young people across Central "
"Asia. The gap between potential and opportunity. Motivated by these "
"challenges and inspired by the power of international collaboration, we're "
"building a fairer, brighter future."
msgstr ""
"Dunyo har qachongidan ham ko'proq bog'langan, ammo sifatli ta'limga kirish "
"hali ham teng emas. Markaziy Osiyo yoshlari duch keladigan to'siqlarni "
"o'ylang. Salohiyat va imkoniyat o'rtasidagi farq. Ushbu qiyinchiliklardan "
"ilhomlangan va xalqaro hamkorlik kuchidan ruhlangan holda biz adolatli va "
"yorqin kelajakni quryapmiz."

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"Founded as Uzbekistan's first truly international university, TIU has been "
"pioneering dual-degree education and cross-border learning from the start. "
"Contributing to education, research, and the social, economic, and cultural "
"growth of our region. We'll continue this work into the next decade and "
"beyond."
msgstr ""
"O'zbekistonning birinchi chinakam xalqaro universiteti sifatida tashkil "
"etilgan TIU boshidanoq qo'shma diplom ta'limi va transchegaraviy o'qitishni "
"boshlab berdi. Ta'lim, tadqiqot va mintaqamizning ijtimoiy, iqtisodiy va "
"madaniy rivojlanishiga hissa qo'shib kelmoqda. Kelgusi o'n yillikda ham bu "
"ishni davom ettiramiz."

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"As an internationally engaged university, we address the challenges facing "
"our society. Sharing solutions across borders in an increasingly connected "
"world. And guided at every turn by the dedication of our people, our strong "
"sense of place, and the vitality of our partnerships."
msgstr ""
"Xalqaro miqyosda faol universitet sifatida biz jamiyatimiz duch keladigan "
"muammolarga javob beramiz. Tobora bog'langan dunyoda chegaralar oshib "
"yechimlarni almashmoqdamiz. Har bir qadamda xodimlarimiz sadoqati, o'z "
"o'rnimizni his etish va hamkorliklarimiz hayotiyligi bizga yo'l ko'rsatadi."

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "Our Values"
msgstr "Bizning qadriyatlarimiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "We're"
msgstr "Biz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "inclusive"
msgstr "inklyuzivmiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"A supportive, global community of students, scholars, and partners. The true"
" spirit of international friendship. Where everyone can grow into who, what,"
" and where they want to be in the world."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar, olimlar va hamkorlarning qo'llab-quvvatlovchi, global jamoasi. "
"Xalqaro do'stlikning chinakam ruhi. Har kim dunyoda bo'lishni xohlagan "
"shaxsga aylana oladigan muhit."

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "A welcoming community to discover your true potential"
msgstr "Haqiqiy salohiyatingizni ochish uchun mehribon jamoa"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"We provide a safe, friendly, and welcoming environment for all, where our "
"differences are celebrated"
msgstr ""
"Biz barcha uchun xavfsiz, do'stona va mehmondo'st muhit yaratamiz, bu yerda "
"farqlarimiz qadrlanadi"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"We help each and every one of our students, staff, and partners to achieve "
"their full potential with a personal, supportive approach"
msgstr ""
"Biz har bir talaba, xodim va hamkorimizga shaxsiy, qo'llab-quvvatlovchi "
"yondashuv bilan to'liq salohiyatiga erishishda yordam beramiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "We celebrate individual and collective success"
msgstr "Biz individual va jamoaviy muvaffaqiyatlarni nishonlaymiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"We're mindful of the positive impact of what we each do, every day, on other"
" individuals and communities both near and far"
msgstr ""
"Har birimiz har kuni boshqa shaxslar va jamoalarga — yaqin va uzoqdagilarga "
"— ko'rsatadigan ijobiy ta'sirni anglaymiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "empowering"
msgstr "kuchaytiruvchimiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"A civic university equipping people to understand the defining issues of our"
" time. And empowering them to act and shape their personal and collective "
"future for the better."
msgstr ""
"Insonlarni zamonamizning muhim muammolarini tushunishga tayyorlaydigan "
"fuqarolik universiteti. Ularni o'z shaxsiy va jamoaviy kelajaklarini "
"yaxshiroq tomonga shakllantirish uchun harakatga undaydigan kuch."

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "Defying convention to break new ground"
msgstr "Yangi yo'llar ochish uchun an'analarga qarshi borish"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"We empower people to succeed, recognizing that with empowerment comes "
"responsibility and accountability"
msgstr ""
"Biz insonlarni muvaffaqiyatga erishishga kuchlaytiramiz, kuch bilan birga "
"mas'uliyat va javobgarlik kelishini tan olib"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"We build people's confidence through understanding, knowledge, skills, and "
"experience"
msgstr ""
"Biz tushunish, bilim, ko'nikma va tajriba orqali insonlarga ishonch "
"bag'ishlaymiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"We stretch people's minds and help them develop new ways of thinking that "
"will help shape a fairer, brighter future"
msgstr ""
"Biz insonlarning tafakkurini kengaytiramiz va adolatliroq, yorqinroq "
"kelajakni shakllantirishga yordam beradigan yangi fikrlash usullarini "
"rivojlantirishga ko'maklashamiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"Through equal opportunity, we ensure everyone has the opportunity to shine"
msgstr ""
"Teng imkoniyatlar orqali har kimga o'z iste'dodini namoyon qilish imkonini "
"beramiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "progressive"
msgstr "progressivmiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"A living laboratory. A place where all students, scholars, and partners from"
" every faculty collaborate hands-on. Where we generate new thinking in "
"defiance of traditional academic barriers and conventions."
msgstr ""
"Tirik laboratoriya. Barcha fakultetlardan talabalar, olimlar va hamkorlar "
"amaliy hamkorlik qiladigan joy. An'anaviy akademik to'siqlarga qarshi yangi "
"fikrlarni yaratadigan muhit."

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "Driven by an unwavering desire for progress"
msgstr "Taraqqiyotga bo'lgan doimiy intilish bilan harakatda"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"We set high standards and challenge ourselves and others to deliver "
"meaningful progress with tangible outcomes"
msgstr ""
"Biz yuqori standartlarni belgilaymiz va o'zimizni hamda boshqalarni aniq "
"natijalarga ega mazmunli taraqqiyotga erishishga undaymiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "We follow and develop best practice across all areas of our activity"
msgstr ""
"Biz faoliyatimizning barcha sohalarida eng yaxshi amaliyotlarni qo'llaymiz "
"va rivojlantiramiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"We work at pace and are always future-facing and, with agility, ready to "
"adapt"
msgstr ""
"Biz tezkorlik bilan ishlaymiz, har doim kelajakka qaraymiz va "
"moslashuvchanlik bilan o'zgarishlarga tayyormiz"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid ""
"We learn to be self-reflective so we can seek improvement, make an even "
"bigger difference, and embrace a different future"
msgstr ""
"Biz o'z-o'zimizni tahlil qilishni o'rganamiz — yaxshilanishga intilish, "
"kattaroq o'zgarish qilish va yangi kelajakni qabul qilish uchun"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "Inclusive community"
msgstr "Inklyuziv jamoa"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "Empowering students"
msgstr "Talabalarni kuchaytirish"

#: templates/pages/about/mission-vision.html
msgid "Progressive thinking"
msgstr "Progressiv tafakkur"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Your one-stop destination for career guidance, job search support, and "
"professional development resources at TIU."
msgstr ""
"TIUda karyera bo'yicha maslahat, ish qidirish va kasbiy rivojlanish "
"resurslari uchun yagona manba."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Get job ready from day one"
msgstr "Birinchi kundan ishga tayyorlaning"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Whatever your goals, we're here to help you take the next step with "
"confidence."
msgstr ""
"Maqsadingiz qanday bo'lmasin, biz sizga ishonch bilan keyingi qadamni "
"qo'yishda yordam beramiz."

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"At TIU, you'll receive personalised career advice, hands-on experience "
"through our partner network, and dedicated support to boost your "
"employability across Uzbekistan and beyond."
msgstr ""
"TIUda siz shaxsiy karyera maslahati, hamkor tarmoq orqali amaliy tajriba va "
"O'zbekiston va undan tashqarida bandlikni oshirish uchun maxsus qo'llab-"
"quvvatlash olasiz."

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Employability is embedded in every programme — from internships with leading"
" companies to skills workshops, employer events, and one-to-one guidance "
"with our career advisors."
msgstr ""
"Bandlik har bir dasturga kiritilgan — yetakchi kompaniyalardagi amaliyotdan "
"tortib ko'nikma seminarlarigacha, ish beruvchilar tadbirlari va karyera "
"maslahatchilari bilan individual uchrashuvlar."

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Whether you're looking for part-time work, your first graduate role, or "
"exploring career paths, we're with you every step of the way."
msgstr ""
"Yarim stavkali ish, birinchi bitiruvchi lavozimi yoki karyera yo'llarini "
"o'rganayotgan bo'lsangiz — biz har qadamda siz bilan birgamiz."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Career mentoring"
msgstr "Karyera mentorlik"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Get advice from professionals who've been there. Our mentoring programme "
"connects you with TIU alumni and industry leaders in Uzbekistan and abroad "
"for guidance as you explore your career options."
msgstr ""
"Tajribali mutaxassislardan maslahat oling. Mentorlik dasturimiz sizni TIU "
"bitiruvchilari va O'zbekiston hamda xorijdagi sanoat yetakchilari bilan "
"bog'laydi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Skills workshops"
msgstr "Ko'nikma seminarlari"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Get practical support to feel career ready. From writing strong CVs and "
"cover letters to interview preparation and LinkedIn optimization, our "
"workshops give you the tools to succeed."
msgstr ""
"Karyeraga tayyorlanish uchun amaliy yordam oling. Kuchli rezyume yozishdan "
"tortib intervyuga tayyorgarlik va LinkedIn optimizatsiyasigacha — "
"seminarlarimiz muvaffaqiyat uchun vositalar beradi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Work placements"
msgstr "Ish amaliyoti"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Gain hands-on experience with structured placements at companies across "
"Tashkent and partner organisations internationally. Build your professional "
"network and develop the skills employers value most."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent va xalqaro hamkor tashkilotlardagi tizimli amaliyot orqali amaliy "
"tajriba oling. Professional tarmoqingizni kengaytiring va ish beruvchilar "
"eng ko'p qadrlaydigan ko'nikmalarni rivojlantiring."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Employer connections"
msgstr "Ish beruvchilar bilan aloqalar"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Meet employers at careers fairs, networking events, and on-campus talks. "
"Build relationships with organisations in Uzbekistan and internationally "
"that are looking to recruit talented TIU graduates."
msgstr ""
"Karyera yarmarkalari, networking tadbirlari va kampusdagi uchrashuvlarda ish"
" beruvchilar bilan tanishing. TIU bitiruvchilarini yollashni xohlagan "
"tashkilotlar bilan munosabatlarni rivojlantiring."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Find work and build experience"
msgstr "Ish toping va tajriba orttiring"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Our Career Center team helps you find part-time work, paid placements, and "
"summer internships with top employers in Uzbekistan and abroad."
msgstr ""
"Karyera markazi jamoamiz sizga O'zbekiston va xorijdagi yetakchi ish "
"beruvchilarda yarim stavkali ish, pullik amaliyot va yozgi stajировka "
"topishda yordam beradi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Browse job and internship listings"
msgstr "Ish va stajировka e'lonlarini ko'rish"

#: templates/pages
msgid "on the TIU Career Portal"
msgstr "TIU Karyera portalida"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Meet employers"
msgstr "Ish beruvchilar bilan uchrashing"

#: templates/pages
msgid "at our dedicated career fairs and networking events"
msgstr "maxsus karyera yarmarkalari va networking tadbirlarida"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Become a Student Ambassador"
msgstr "Talaba elchisi bo'ling"

#: templates/pages
msgid "to support events, lead campus tours, and represent TIU"
msgstr ""
"tadbirlarni qo'llab-quvvatlash, kampus ekskursiyalarini olib borish va TIUni"
" ifodalash uchun"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Join student-led projects"
msgstr "Talabalar loyihalariga qo'shiling"

#: templates/pages
msgid "from hackathons to startup incubators and community initiatives"
msgstr ""
"hakatonlardan tortib startup inkubatorlari va jamoat tashabbuslarigacha"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Explore paid placements"
msgstr "Pullik amaliyotlarni o'rganing"

#: templates/pages
msgid "to gain real-world experience at partner companies"
msgstr "hamkor kompaniyalarda haqiqiy tajriba olish uchun"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Students at work"
msgstr "Ishda talabalar"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Gain real-world experience and jumpstart your career with internship "
"opportunities at leading organisations partnered with TIU."
msgstr ""
"TIU hamkor yetakchi tashkilotlardagi stajировka imkoniyatlari bilan haqiqiy "
"tajriba oling va karyerangizni boshlang."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Why work with our students?"
msgstr "Nega bizning talabalar bilan ishlash kerak?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"At TIU, we go beyond sharing knowledge. Our students study across five "
"dynamic departments — Business & Economics, IT, Education, Foreign "
"Languages, and Jurisprudence — each programme designed to build the skills "
"and experience they need to thrive in the real world."
msgstr ""
"TIUda biz bilim ulashishdan nariroqqa boramiz. Talabalarimiz beshta kuchli "
"fakultetda o'qishadi — Biznes va iqtisodiyot, IT, Ta'lim, Chet tillari va "
"Huquqshunoslik — har bir dastur haqiqiy dunyoda rivojlanish uchun zarur "
"ko'nikma va tajribani shakllantirishga qaratilgan."

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"That creates outstanding opportunities for our employer partners to engage "
"with motivated, multilingual students and tap into a pipeline of career-"
"ready graduates every year."
msgstr ""
"Bu ish beruvchi hamkorlarga motivatsiyali, ko'p tilli talabalar bilan "
"ishlash va har yili karyeraga tayyor bitiruvchilar oqimidan foydalanish "
"uchun ajoyib imkoniyatlar yaratadi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "That's where you come in."
msgstr "Aynan shu yerda siz kerak bo'lasiz."

#: templates/pages
msgid "HOW YOU CAN GET INVOLVED"
msgstr "QANDAY QO'SHILISH MUMKIN"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Promote your job opportunities"
msgstr "Ish imkoniyatlaringizni targ'ib qiling"

#: templates/pages
msgid "directly to our students free of charge through the TIU Career Portal"
msgstr "TIU Karyera portali orqali talabalarimizga bevosita va bepul"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Access Central Asia's top emerging talent"
msgstr "Markaziy Osiyoning eng yaxshi yosh iste'dodlariga kirish"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"during their studies through internships, placements, and student projects"
msgstr ""
"o'qish davomida stajировkalar, amaliyot va talabalar loyihalari orqali"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Receive tailored support"
msgstr "Moslashtirilgan qo'llab-quvvatlash oling"

#: templates/pages
msgid "from our Career Center to find the right fit for your organisation"
msgstr ""
"tashkilotingiz uchun eng mos kadrni topish uchun Karyera markazimizdan"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Attend job fairs and events on campus"
msgstr "Kampusdagi ish yarmarkalari va tadbirlarga tashrif buyuring"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"to build brand awareness and create a talent pipeline of future graduates "
"ready to join your team"
msgstr ""
"brendingiz haqida xabardorlikni oshirish va jamoangizga qo'shilishga tayyor "
"kelajak bitiruvchilar quvurini yaratish uchun"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Bring in fresh ideas and insight"
msgstr "Yangi g'oyalar va fikrlarni keltiring"

#: templates/pages
msgid "from students equipped with the latest knowledge in their field"
msgstr "o'z sohasidagi eng so'nggi bilimlar bilan qurollangan talabalardan"

#: templates/pages
msgid "How to recruit one of our students or graduates"
msgstr "Talaba yoki bitiruvchimizni qanday yollash mumkin"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"We offer local, regional, and international employers the opportunity to "
"advertise full-time and part-time jobs, internships, and placements through "
"the TIU Career Portal."
msgstr ""
"Biz mahalliy, mintaqaviy va xalqaro ish beruvchilarga TIU Karyera portali "
"orqali to'liq va yarim stavkali ishlar, stajiovkalar va amaliyotlarni e'lon "
"qilish imkoniyatini taklif etamiz."

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Maintaining an active profile on our portal is quick, easy, and completely "
"free of charge. It allows you to:"
msgstr ""
"Portalimizda faol profil yuritish tez, oson va butunlay bepul. Bu sizga "
"imkon beradi:"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Advertise unlimited vacancies to TIU students and graduates across all "
"departments."
msgstr ""
"TIU talabalar va bitiruvchilariga barcha fakultetlar bo'yicha cheksiz "
"vakansiyalarni e'lon qilish."

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Increase your brand awareness among our multilingual, internationally-minded"
" student body."
msgstr ""
"Ko'p tilli, xalqaro fikrlaydigan talabalarimiz orasida brendingiz "
"xabardorligini oshiring."

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Send targeted communications to students and graduates matching your hiring "
"needs."
msgstr ""
"Yollash ehtiyojlaringizga mos talabalar va bitiruvchilarga maqsadli "
"xabarlarni yuboring."

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Post details of online or in-person recruitment events and career talks."
msgstr ""
"Onlayn yoki oflayn yollash tadbirlari va karyera suhbatlari haqida ma'lumot "
"joylashtiring."

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Our Career Center team works closely with you to maximise engagement and "
"advise on which students or programmes are best suited to your needs."
msgstr ""
"Karyera markazimiz jamoasi siz bilan yaqindan ishlab, jalb qilishni maksimal"
" darajada oshirish va qaysi talabalar yoki dasturlar ehtiyojlaringizga eng "
"mos kelishini maslahat beradi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Student ready for career"
msgstr "Kareraga tayyor talaba"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Other opportunities to speak to us about"
msgstr "Biz bilan gaplashish mumkin bo'lgan boshqa imkoniyatlar"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Across all five departments, TIU students are offered the chance to take "
"part in shorter placement programmes and live projects. We are always "
"interested in hearing from employers who want to get involved — please don't"
" hesitate to get in touch."
msgstr ""
"Barcha beshta fakultetda TIU talabalari qisqa muddatli amaliyot dasturlari "
"va jonli loyihalarda ishtirok etish imkoniyatiga ega. Biz har doim ishtirok "
"etmoqchi bo'lgan ish beruvchilardan eshitishga qiziqamiz — aloqaga "
"chiqishdan tortinmang."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Mentoring"
msgstr "Mentorlik"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Share your industry experience by becoming a mentor to TIU students. Our "
"mentoring programme connects professionals with students to provide guidance"
" on career development, industry insights, and professional skills."
msgstr ""
"TIU talabalariga mentor bo'lib sanoat tajribangizni ulashing. Mentorlik "
"dasturimiz mutaxassislarni talabalar bilan bog'lab, karyera rivojlanishi va "
"professional ko'nikmalar bo'yicha yo'l-yo'riq beradi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Events and careers fairs"
msgstr "Tadbirlar va karyera yarmarkalari"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Attend our regular careers fairs and employer events to meet students face-"
"to-face, showcase your organisation, and identify potential talent for your "
"business."
msgstr ""
"Muntazam karyera yarmarkalari va ish beruvchilar tadbirlarimizga tashrif "
"buyurib, talabalar bilan yuzma-yuz uchrashing va tashkilotingiz uchun "
"iste'dodlarni toping."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Part-time jobs and seasonal work"
msgstr "Yarim stavkali va mavsumiy ish"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Advertise part-time, casual, and seasonal work opportunities to our "
"students. Many TIU students are looking for flexible work that fits around "
"their studies."
msgstr ""
"Talabalarimizga yarim stavkali va mavsumiy ish imkoniyatlarini e'lon qiling."
" Ko'p TIU talabalari o'qishlari atrofida moslashuvchan ish qidirmoqda."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Student academic projects"
msgstr "Talaba ilmiy loyihalari"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Collaborate with TIU students on real-world academic projects. Provide a "
"brief or challenge and benefit from fresh perspectives while students gain "
"valuable practical experience."
msgstr ""
"TIU talabalari bilan haqiqiy ilmiy loyihalarda hamkorlik qiling. Topshiriq "
"yoki muammo taqdim eting va yangi fikrlardan foydalaning, talabalar esa "
"qimmatli amaliy tajriba oladi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Ko'p beriladigan savollar"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Find answers to the most common questions about admissions, programmes, "
"fees, and student life at TIU."
msgstr ""
"TIUga qabul, dasturlar, to'lovlar va talabalar hayoti haqida eng ko'p "
"beriladigan savollarga javoblarni toping."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Table of contents"
msgstr "Mundarija"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Programmes & Study"
msgstr "Dasturlar va o'qish"

#: templates/pages
msgid "International Students"
msgstr "Xorijiy talabalar"

#: templates/pages
msgid "Campus & Student Life"
msgstr "Kampus va talabalar hayoti"

#: templates/pages
msgid "After Graduation"
msgstr "Bitirganidan keyin"

#: templates/pages
msgid "How do I apply to TIU?"
msgstr "TIUga qanday ariza topshiraman?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"You can apply online through our admissions portal. Visit the Apply Now "
"page, select your programme (Bachelor's, Master's, or PhD), fill in the "
"application form, and upload the required documents. Our admissions team "
"will review your application and contact you within 5–10 business days."
msgstr ""
"Siz onlayn qabul portalimiz orqali ariza topshirishingiz mumkin. Ariza "
"berish sahifasiga tashrif buyuring, dasturingizni tanlang (Bakalavr, Magistr"
" yoki PhD), ariza shaklini to'ldiring va kerakli hujjatlarni yuklang. Qabul "
"jamoamiz arizangizni ko'rib chiqadi va 5-10 ish kuni ichida siz bilan "
"bog'lanadi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "What are the entry requirements?"
msgstr "Qabul talablari qanday?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Requirements vary by programme. For Bachelor's programmes, you need a "
"secondary school diploma (attestat) with competitive grades. For Master's "
"programmes, a Bachelor's degree is required. All applicants must demonstrate"
" English proficiency (IELTS 5.5+ or equivalent). Specific programme "
"requirements are listed on each programme page."
msgstr ""
"Talablar dasturga qarab farq qiladi. Bakalavr dasturlari uchun "
"raqobatbardosh baholi o'rta maktab diplomi (attestat) kerak. Magistratura "
"uchun bakalavr diplomi talab qilinadi. Barcha abituriyentlar ingliz tili "
"bilimini isbotlashi kerak (IELTS 5.5+ yoki ekvivalent)."

#: templates/pages
msgid "What documents do I need to submit?"
msgstr "Qanday hujjatlar topshirish kerak?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Typically you'll need: a copy of your passport or ID, your most recent "
"diploma/certificate with transcript, an English language proficiency "
"certificate (IELTS, TOEFL, or TIU internal test), a personal statement, and "
"a passport-sized photo. Some programmes may require additional documents "
"such as a portfolio or letters of recommendation."
msgstr ""
"Odatda sizga kerak: pasport yoki ID nusxasi, so'nggi diplom/sertifikat va "
"transkript, ingliz tili sertifikati (IELTS, TOEFL yoki TIU ichki testi), "
"shaxsiy bayonnoma va pasport formatidagi rasm. Ba'zi dasturlar portfolio "
"yoki tavsiya xatlari kabi qo'shimcha hujjatlar talab qilishi mumkin."

#: templates/pages
msgid "When is the application deadline?"
msgstr "Ariza topshirish muddati qachon?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"TIU accepts applications on a rolling basis. The main intake is in "
"September, with applications typically closing in late August. An early "
"application is recommended as popular programmes may fill up. Check the "
"Admissions page for the exact deadlines for the current academic year."
msgstr ""
"TIU arizalarni uzluksiz qabul qiladi. Asosiy qabul sentyabrda bo'lib, "
"arizalar odatda avgust oxirida yopiladi. Mashhur dasturlar to'lib ketishi "
"mumkinligi sababli erta ariza berish tavsiya etiladi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Can I apply for more than one programme?"
msgstr "Bir nechta dasturga ariza topshira olamanmi?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Yes, you can apply to up to two programmes simultaneously. If accepted to "
"both, you will choose which offer to accept. There is no additional fee for "
"a second application."
msgstr ""
"Ha, siz bir vaqtda ikkita dasturga ariza topshirishingiz mumkin. Ikkalasiga "
"ham qabul qilingan bo'lsangiz, qaysi taklifni qabul qilishni tanlaysiz. "
"Ikkinchi ariza uchun qo'shimcha to'lov yo'q."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Is there an entrance exam?"
msgstr "Kirish imtihoni bormi?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"For most programmes, admission is based on your academic record and English "
"proficiency. Some programmes may include an interview or written assessment."
" If you don't have an IELTS/TOEFL score, you can take TIU's internal English"
" placement test on campus."
msgstr ""
"Ko'pgina dasturlar uchun qabul akademik natijalar va ingliz tili bilimiga "
"asoslanadi. Ba'zi dasturlarga intervyu yoki yozma baholash kirishi mumkin. "
"Agar IELTS/TOEFL balingiz bo'lmasa, kampusda TIU ichki ingliz tili testini "
"topshirishingiz mumkin."

#: templates/pages
msgid "How long does it take to receive a decision?"
msgstr "Qaror olish qancha vaqt oladi?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Most applicants receive a decision within 5–10 business days after "
"submitting a complete application. During peak periods, it may take up to "
"two weeks. You'll be notified by email and can track your application status"
" online."
msgstr ""
"Ko'pgina abituriyentlar to'liq ariza topshirilgandan so'ng 5-10 ish kuni "
"ichida qaror oladi. Eng band davrda ikki haftagacha vaqt ketishi mumkin. "
"Sizga elektron pochta orqali xabar beriladi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Can I defer my offer to the next intake?"
msgstr "Taklifnomani keyingi qabulga ko'chirsa bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Yes, in most cases you can defer your offer by one academic year. Contact "
"the admissions office to request a deferral. Please note that some "
"scholarship offers may not carry over to the next intake."
msgstr ""
"Ha, ko'p hollarda taklifingizni bir o'quv yiliga qoldirish mumkin. "
"Kechiktirish so'rash uchun qabul bo'limi bilan bog'laning. Eslatib o'tamiz, "
"ba'zi stipendiya takliflari keyingi qabulga o'tmasligi mumkin."

#: templates/pages
msgid "What programmes does TIU offer?"
msgstr "TIU qanday dasturlar taklif qiladi?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"TIU offers Bachelor's, Master's, and PhD programmes across five departments:"
" Business & Economics, Information Technology, Education, Foreign Languages,"
" and Jurisprudence. We also offer a unique 2+2 dual degree programme with "
"international partner universities."
msgstr ""
"TIU beshta fakultet bo'yicha bakalavr, magistratura va PhD dasturlarini "
"taklif etadi: Biznes va iqtisodiyot, Axborot texnologiyalari, Ta'lim, Chet "
"tillari va Huquqshunoslik. Shuningdek, xalqaro hamkor universitetlar bilan "
"2+2 qo'shma diplom dasturini taklif etamiz."

#: templates/pages
msgid "What is the language of instruction?"
msgstr "Ta'lim qaysi tilda olib boriladi?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"The primary language of instruction at TIU is English. Some programmes may "
"include components in Uzbek or Russian. All students are expected to have a "
"working level of English by the start of their studies."
msgstr ""
"TIUda asosiy o'qitish tili ingliz tili. Ba'zi dasturlarda o'zbek yoki rus "
"tilidagi komponentlar bo'lishi mumkin. Barcha talabalar o'qishni boshlaganda"
" ingliz tilining ishchi darajasiga ega bo'lishi kutiladi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "How long are the degree programmes?"
msgstr "Dasturlar qancha davom etadi?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Bachelor's programmes are typically 4 years (or 2+2 with the dual degree "
"option). Master's programmes are 2 years. PhD programmes are 3 years. Part-"
"time options may have different durations depending on the programme."
msgstr ""
"Bakalavr dasturlari odatda 4 yil (yoki qo'shma diplom varianti bilan 2+2). "
"Magistratura — 2 yil. PhD — 3 yil."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Can I transfer from another university?"
msgstr "Boshqa universitetdan o'tkazila olamanmi?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Yes, TIU accepts transfer students. Credit transfer is evaluated on a case-"
"by-case basis depending on the courses completed and grades achieved. "
"Contact our admissions office with your transcript for a preliminary "
"assessment."
msgstr ""
"Ha, TIU transfer talabalarni qabul qiladi. Kreditlarni o'tkazish o'tilgan "
"fanlar va baholar asosida individual ko'rib chiqiladi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Are TIU degrees internationally recognized?"
msgstr "TIU diplomlari xalqaro miqyosda tan olinadimi?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Yes. TIU is licensed by the Ministry of Higher Education of Uzbekistan, and "
"our degrees are recognized both nationally and internationally. Our 2+2 dual"
" degree programme means graduates also receive a degree from our partner "
"university abroad."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU O'zbekiston Oliy ta'lim vazirligi tomonidan litsenziyalangan va "
"diplomlarimiz milliy va xalqaro miqyosda tan olinadi. 2+2 qo'shma diplom "
"dasturimiz bitiruvchilar xorijdagi hamkor universitetdan ham diplom olishini"
" anglatadi."

#: templates/pages
msgid "Does TIU offer joint or dual degree programmes?"
msgstr "TIU qo'shma yoki ikki tomonlama diplom dasturlarini taklif etadimi?"

#: templates/pages
msgid ""
"Yes, our flagship 2+2 programme allows you to study two years at TIU and two"
" years at a partner university abroad. You graduate with two degrees — one "
"from TIU and one from the partner institution. This is available for select "
"Bachelor's programmes."
msgstr ""
"Ha, bizning asosiy 2+2 dasturimiz TIUda ikki yil va xorijdagi hamkor "
"universitetda ikki yil o'qish imkonini beradi. Ikkita diplom bilan "
"bitiruvchi bo'lasiz. Bu tanlangan bakalavr dasturlari uchun mavjud."

msgid "Choose from programs in"
msgstr "Quyidagi yo'nalishlar bo'yicha dasturlardan tanlang:"

msgid "and"
msgstr "va"

msgid ""
"Our bachelor's degrees combine international standards with practical "
"skills, preparing you for the global job market."
msgstr ""
"Bakalavriat dasturlarimiz xalqaro standartlar bilan amaliy ko'nikmalarni "
"uyg'unlashtirgan holda, sizni jahon mehnat bozoriga tayyorlaydi."

msgid "Public Finance"
msgstr "Davlat moliyasi"

msgid "International Finance"
msgstr "Xalqaro moliya"

msgid "Finance"
msgstr "Moliya"

msgid "Our master's programs in"
msgstr "Magistratura dasturlarimiz"

msgid ""
"offer advanced research opportunities and expert faculty. Take the next step"
" in your academic and professional journey."
msgstr ""
"ilg'or ilmiy tadqiqot imkoniyatlari va tajribali professor-o'qituvchilar "
"jamoasini taqdim etadi. Ilmiy va kasbiy yo'lingizda navbatdagi qadamni "
"qo'ying."

msgid "Our doctoral programs in"
msgstr "Doktorantura dasturlarimiz"

msgid ""
"The story of Tashkent International University — from its founding to today."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent xalqaro universitetining tarixi — tashkil etilgan kundan "
"bugungacha."

msgid "University History"
msgstr "Universitet tarixi"

msgid ""
"Tashkent International University is a private university located in "
"Tashkent, the capital of Uzbekistan. It opened its doors to students in "
"October 2023."
msgstr ""
"Tashkent International University — O'zbekiston poytaxti Toshkent shahrida "
"joylashgan xususiy universitet. 2023-yil oktyabr oyida talabalar uchun o'z "
"eshiklarini ochdi."

msgid ""
"The university has four departments: Business, Education, IT, and Foreign "
"Languages. We offer bachelor's and master's programs in these fields."
msgstr ""
"Universitetda to'rtta bo'lim mavjud: Biznes, Ta'lim, IT va Chet tillar. Biz "
"mazkur sohalarda bakalavriat va magistratura dasturlarini taklif qilamiz."

msgid "Our Departments"
msgstr "Bizning yo'nalishlar"

msgid ""
"The TIU Business Department offers programs in economics, finance, "
"marketing, management, world economy, and international economic relations. "
"Graduates of this program become business professionals with strong "
"analytical and critical thinking skills."
msgstr ""
"Biznes yo'nalishi — iqtisodiyot, moliya, marketing, menejment, jahon "
"iqtisodiyoti va xalqaro iqtisodiy munosabatlar bo'yicha dasturlarni taqdim "
"etadi. Ushbu yo'nalish bitiruvchilari kuchli tahliliy va tanqidiy fikrlash "
"ko'nikmalariga ega biznes mutaxassislariga aylanadi."

msgid ""
"TIU's Education Department prepares students to become teachers and "
"educators in various fields such as preschool education, primary education, "
"and psychology. Graduates become effective teachers who can inspire and "
"motivate their students."
msgstr ""
"Pedagogika yo'nalishi — talabalarni maktabgacha ta'lim, boshlang'ich ta'lim "
"va psixologiya kabi sohalarda pedagog va tarbiyachi bo'lishga tayyorlaydi. "
"Bitiruvchilar o'z shogirdlarini ilhomlantira va rag'batlantira oladigan "
"samarali pedagoglar bo'lib yetishadi."

msgid ""
"The TIU IT Department offers specializations in computer engineering, "
"software engineering, information technology, and cybersecurity, helping "
"students become experts in the latest technologies and preparing them for "
"careers in software development, cybersecurity, and data analysis."
msgstr ""
"AT yo'nalishi — kompyuter injiniringi, dasturiy ta'minot injiniringi, "
"axborot texnologiyalari va kiberhavfsizlik bo'yicha ixtisosliklarni taqdim "
"etadi. Talabalar eng so'nggi texnologiyalar bo'yicha mutaxassis bo'lib, "
"dasturiy ta'minot ishlab chiqish, kiberhavfsizlik va ma'lumotlar tahlili "
"sohasida karera qurishga tayyorlanadi."

msgid ""
"TIU's Foreign Languages Department offers specializations in translation, "
"interpretation, and language teaching. Students of this program become "
"communication specialists through learning various languages in written and "
"oral forms."
msgstr ""
"Xorijiy tillar yo'nalishi — tarjima, izohli tarjima va til o'qitish bo'yicha"
" ixtisosliklarni taklif etadi. Ushbu yo'nalish talabalari turli tillarni "
"yozma va og'zaki shakllarda o'rganish orqali kommunikatsiya mutaxassislariga"
" aylanadi."

msgid "Faculty and Research"
msgstr "Professor-o'qituvchilar va ilmiy faoliyat"

msgid ""
"TIU is staffed by highly qualified professors and experienced teachers who "
"are experts in their fields. Their extensive teaching and research "
"experience sets a high standard for academic excellence."
msgstr ""
"TIU da yuqori malakali professor-o'qituvchilar va o'z sohasining "
"mutaxassislari bo'lgan tajribali o'qituvchilar talabalarga dars beradi. "
"Ularning keng ko'lamli o'qitish va tadqiqot tajribasi akademik mukammallik "
"uchun yuqori standartni o'rnatadi."

msgid ""
"TIU places great emphasis on research and innovation, supporting students' "
"involvement in research activities and collaboration with industry "
"organizations."
msgstr ""
"Shuningdek, TIU tadqiqot va innovatsiyalarga katta e'tibor qaratadi va "
"talabalarni tadqiqot faoliyatiga jalb qilish va sanoat tashkilotlari bilan "
"hamkorlik qilishini qo'llab-quvvatlaydi."

msgid "International Partnerships"
msgstr "Xalqaro hamkorlik"

msgid ""
"TIU establishes partnerships with prestigious universities and organizations"
" around the world, creating broad opportunities for students to study abroad"
" and gain international experience."
msgstr ""
"TIU dunyoning nufuzli universitetlari va tashkilotlari bilan hamkorlik "
"aloqalarini o'rnatib, talabalarning xorijda ta'lim olishlari hamda xalqaro "
"tajriba orttirishlari uchun keng imkoniyatlar yaratib beradi."

msgid ""
"In conclusion, we provide comprehensive support to our students, "
"contributing to their success in their chosen profession and personal life."
msgstr ""
"Xulosa qilib aytganda, biz talabalarimizga har tomonlama yordam beramiz, "
"tanlagan kasb va shaxsiy hayotlarida muvaffaqiyat qozonishlariga o'z "
"hissamizni qo'shamiz."

msgid "Key Milestones"
msgstr "Muhim bosqichlar"

msgid ""
"TIU is officially founded in Tashkent with four departments and English-"
"medium instruction."
msgstr ""
"TIU to'rtta yo'nalish va ingliz tilida ta'lim bilan Toshkentda rasman "
"tashkil etildi."

msgid ""
