"Xilma-xillikning ahamiyatini e'tirof etish, turli madaniyatlarni hurmat "
"qilish va o'zaro tushunishni rivojlantiradigan inklyuziv muhit yaratish."

msgid "Our Campus - TIU"
msgstr "Kampusimiz - TIU"

msgid "Discover Our Campus"
msgstr "Kampusimizni kashf eting"

msgid ""
"Live, learn and make friends on our modern single-site campus. With teaching"
" spaces, accommodation, sports facilities and social areas all close by, "
"you'll feel right at home from day one."
msgstr ""
"Zamonaviy yagona kampusimizda yashang, o'qing va do'stlar orttiring. O'quv "
"binolari, turar joy, sport inshootlari va dam olish hududlari — hammasi bir "
"joyda. Birinchi kundan o'zingizni uyingizdek his qilasiz."

msgid "Cross campus in"
msgstr "Kampusni aylanib chiqing"

msgid "10 minutes"
msgstr "10 daqiqada"

msgid ""
"Our campus on Little Ring Road 7 in Tashkent puts everything you need within"
" a short walk. Modern classrooms, a well-stocked library, sports center, "
"cafeteria, and green outdoor spaces — all designed to support your studies "
"and social life."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent shahri, Kichik halqa yo'li 7-da joylashgan kampusimizda hamma narsa"
" bir-biriga yaqin. Zamonaviy o'quv xonalari, boy kutubxona, sport markazi, "
"oshxona va yashil hududlar — barchasi o'qishingiz va ijtimoiy hayotingizni "
"qo'llab-quvvatlash uchun yaratilgan."

msgid "Take a Virtual Tour"
msgstr "Virtual turni boshlang"

msgid "Tap pins to explore"
msgstr "Belgilarni bosib ko'ring"

msgid "Main Academic Building"
msgstr "Asosiy o'quv binosi"

msgid ""
"Home to lecture halls, seminar rooms, and faculty offices across all five "
"departments"
msgstr ""
"Barcha beshta bo'lim uchun ma'ruza zallari, seminar xonalari va "
"o'qituvchilar kabinetlari"

msgid "Library & Study Center"
msgstr "Kutubxona va o'quv markazi"

msgid ""
"Thousands of books and digital resources, quiet study rooms, and "
"collaborative spaces"
msgstr ""
"Minglab kitoblar va raqamli resurslar, tinch o'quv xonalari va hamkorlik "
"maydonlari"

msgid "Sports Center"
msgstr "Sport markazi"

msgid ""
"Multi-court sports hall, gym, and outdoor pitches for students and staff"
msgstr "Ko'p maydonli sport zali, trenazhyor zali va ochiq maydonchalari"

msgid "Student Cafeteria"
msgstr "Talabalar oshxonasi"

msgid ""
"Fresh, affordable meals served daily with vegetarian and dietary options"
msgstr "Har kuni yangi va arzon taomlar, vegetarian va dietik variantlar"

msgid "Administration"
msgstr "Ma'muriyat"

msgid "Admissions, student services, finance, and the Rector's Reception"
msgstr "Qabul, talabalar xizmati, moliya va Rektor qabulxonasi"

msgid "Student Housing"
msgstr "Talabalar turar joyi"

msgid "On-campus accommodation just steps away from classes and facilities"
msgstr "Darslardan bir necha qadam masofadagi kampus ichidagi turar joy"

msgid "More to explore on campus"
msgstr "Kampusda yana nimalar bor"

msgid "Smart Classrooms & Lecture Halls"
msgstr "Aqlli o'quv xonalari va ma'ruza zallari"

msgid ""
"Our classrooms are equipped with the latest presentation technology, "
"comfortable seating, and layouts designed for collaboration. Whether it's a "
"large lecture or a small seminar, the space adapts to how you learn best."
msgstr ""
"O'quv xonalarimiz eng zamonaviy taqdimot texnologiyalari, qulay o'rindiqlar "
"va hamkorlikda ishlashga mo'ljallangan joylashuv bilan jihozlangan. Katta "
"ma'ruza yoki kichik seminar bo'lsin — xona sizning o'qish uslubingizga "
"moslashadi."

msgid "Green Spaces & Outdoor Areas"
msgstr "Yashil hududlar va ochiq maydonlar"

msgid ""
"Landscaped gardens, tree-lined walkways, and outdoor seating areas give you "
"places to relax, study, or meet friends between lectures. Fresh air and "
"green views are never far away."
msgstr ""
"Chiroyli bog'lar, daraxtli yo'laklar va ochiq havoda o'tirish joylari — "
"darslar orasida dam olish, o'qish yoki do'stlar bilan uchrashish uchun "
"ajoyib muhit. Toza havo va yashil manzara doimo yaqiningizda."

msgid "Getting Here — Transport & Parking"
msgstr "Qanday yetib kelish — transport va parkovka"

msgid ""
"TIU is accessible by bus, metro, and taxi from all parts of Tashkent. The "
"nearest metro station is a short walk away, multiple bus routes stop "
"directly outside campus, and parking is available on site."
msgstr ""
"TIUga Toshkentning barcha burchagidan avtobus, metro va taksi orqali oson "
"yetib kelish mumkin. Eng yaqin metro bekati bir necha daqiqalik yurish "
"masofasida, bir nechta avtobus yo'nalishlari to'g'ridan-to'g'ri kampus "
"oldida to'xtaydi, shuningdek avtoturargoh mavjud."

msgid "Virtual Tour"
msgstr "Virtual tur"

msgid "Visit our campus"
msgstr "Kampusimizni"

msgid "before"
msgstr "kelmasdan turib"

msgid "you arrive"
msgstr "ko'rib chiqing"

msgid ""
"Explore every corner of TIU from wherever you are. Our virtual tour lets you"
" walk through classrooms, the library, sports facilities, and student spaces"
" — all from your screen."
msgstr ""
"Qayerda bo'lsangiz ham TIUning har bir burchagini o'rganing. Virtual turimiz"
" orqali o'quv xonalari, kutubxona, sport inshootlari va talabalar "
"makonlarini ekran orqali aylanib chiqishingiz mumkin."

msgid "Start virtual tour"
msgstr "Virtual turni boshlang"

msgid "Tashkent International University, founded in 2023."
msgstr "Toshkent Xalqaro Universiteti, 2023-yilda tashkil etilgan."

msgid "The Future"
msgstr "Kelajak"

msgid "Accreditation - TIU"
msgstr "Akkreditatsiya - TIU"

msgid ""
"Recognized, accredited, and trusted — your degree from TIU meets the highest"
" national and international standards."
msgstr ""
"Tan olingan, akkreditatsiyadan o'tgan va ishonchli — TIU diplomi eng yuqori "
"milliy va xalqaro standartlarga javob beradi."

msgid "A degree worth earning should be a degree worth"
msgstr "O'qishga arzigulik diplom"

msgid "trusting."
msgstr "ishonchga loyiq bo'lishi kerak."

msgid "Our Quality Promise"
msgstr "Sifat kafolatimiz"

msgid "Quality you can count on"
msgstr "Ishonch bildirsa arziydigan sifat"

msgid ""
"Your TIU degree is officially recognized by the Ministry of Higher Education"
" of Uzbekistan and validated by our international partner universities. "
"Through our 2+2 dual degree partnerships, TIU programs align with the "
"academic requirements of partner institutions abroad."
msgstr ""
"TIU diplomi O'zbekiston Oliy ta'lim vazirligi tomonidan rasman tan olingan "
"va xalqaro hamkor universitetlar tomonidan tasdiqlangan. 2+2 qo'shma diplom "
"hamkorligi orqali TIU dasturlari xorijdagi hamkor muassasalarning akademik "
"talablariga mos keladi."

msgid ""
"This means seamless credit transfer — no extra exams, no lost credits. We "
"continuously review and improve our programs to stay aligned with global "
"best practices in higher education."
msgstr ""
"Bu muammosiz kredit transferi — qo'shimcha imtihonlar va yo'qolgan kreditlar"
" yo'q. Biz dasturlarimizni oliy ta'limdagi global amaliyotlarga mos ravishda"
" doimiy ko'rib chiqamiz va takomillashtiramiz."

msgid "TIU Accreditation"
msgstr "TIU akkreditatsiyasi"

msgid "Official Recognition"
msgstr "Rasmiy tan olinish"

msgid "Accredited at every level"
msgstr "Har bir darajada akkreditatsiyadan o'tgan"

msgid "Government Licensed"
msgstr "Davlat litsenziyasi"

msgid "Fully licensed by the Ministry of Higher Education of Uzbekistan."
msgstr "O'zbekiston Oliy ta'lim vazirligi tomonidan to'liq litsenziyalangan."

msgid "National"
msgstr "Milliy"

msgid "Partner Validated"
msgstr "Hamkorlar tomonidan tasdiqlangan"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"2+2 programs co-developed and validated by international partner "
"universities."
msgstr ""
"2+2 dasturlari xalqaro hamkor universitetlar bilan birgalikda ishlab "
"chiqilgan va tasdiqlangan."

msgid "Globally Recognized"
msgstr "Jahon miqyosida tan olingan"

msgid "Dual degrees recognized by employers and institutions worldwide."
msgstr ""
"Qo'sha diplomlar butun dunyo bo'ylab ish beruvchilar va ta'lim muassasalari "
"tomonidan tan olinadi."

msgid "International Recognition"
msgstr "Xalqaro tan olinishi"

msgid "Degrees that travel with you"
msgstr "Siz bilan birga sayohat qiladigan diplom"

msgid ""
"Every TIU program in the 2+2 pathway is validated by our partner "
"universities. When you transfer for your final two years, your credits move "
"with you — seamlessly. And when you graduate, you hold two degrees "
"recognized across the globe."
msgstr ""
"2+2 dasturidagi har bir TIU dasturi hamkor universitetlar tomonidan "
"tasdiqlangan. Oxirgi ikki yilga o'tganingizda kreditlaringiz siz bilan birga"
" muammosiz ko'chadi. Bitirganingizda esa dunyo bo'ylab tan olingan ikkita "
"diplomga ega bo'lasiz."

msgid "View partner universities"
msgstr "Hamkor universitetlarni ko'rish"

msgid "Your future deserves a degree that"
msgstr "Kelajagingiz shunday diplomga loyiq"

msgid "opens doors"
msgstr "eshiklarni ochadi"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Browse bachelor's and master's programs across five departments — all "
"accredited, all in English, all designed for your global future."
msgstr ""
"Beshta yo'nalish bo'yicha bakalavriat va magistratura dasturlarini ko'rib "
"chiqing — barchasi akkreditatsiyadan o'tgan, barchasi ingliz tilida, "
"barchasi sizning xalqaro kelajagingiz uchun yaratilgan."

msgid "View Programs"
msgstr "Dasturlarni ko'rish"

msgid "Have questions about accreditation?"
msgstr "Akkreditatsiya bo'yicha savollaringiz bormi?"

msgid ""
"Our admissions team can answer any questions about credit transfer, degree "
"recognition, and how TIU programs are validated internationally. Whether "
"you're a student, parent, or employer — we're happy to provide documentation"
" and clarity."
msgstr ""
"Qabul bo'limimiz kreditlarni o'tkazish, diplomning tan olinishi va TIU "
"dasturlarining xalqaro miqyosda qanday tasdiqlanishi haqidagi har qanday "
"savolga javob beradi. Talaba, ota-ona yoki ish beruvchi bo'lsangiz ham — biz"
" zarur hujjatlar va aniq ma'lumotlarni taqdim etishdan mamnunmiz."

msgid "Sustainability - TIU"
msgstr "Barqaror rivojlanish - TIU"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Building a greener future through responsible campus practices, sustainable "
"education, and community engagement."
msgstr ""
"Mas'uliyatli kampus amaliyotlari, barqaror ta'lim va jamoatchilik bilan "
"hamkorlik orqali yashilroq kelajak quramiz."

msgid ""
"Great universities don't just prepare students for the world — they help "
"<strong>protect it.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"Buyuk universitetlar talabalarni dunyoga tayyorlash bilan birga — "
"<strong>uni himoya qilishga</strong> ham yordam beradi."

msgid "Our Sustainability Promise"
msgstr "Barqaror rivojlanish bo'yicha va'damiz"

msgid "A campus that cares for tomorrow"
msgstr "Ertangi kunga g'amxo'rlik qiladigan kampus"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"At TIU, sustainability is woven into how we operate, teach, and think — from"
" energy-efficient buildings to green spaces designed with the future in "
"mind."
msgstr ""
"TIUda barqaror rivojlanish bizning ishlash, o'qitish va fikrlash tarzimizga "
"singdirilgan — energiyatejamkor binolardan tortib kelajakni o'ylab "
"yaratilgan yashil hududlargacha."

msgid "TIU Green Campus"
msgstr "TIU Yashil Kampus"

msgid "Our Focus Areas"
msgstr "Asosiy yo'nalishlarimiz"

msgid "Three pillars of sustainability"
msgstr "Barqaror rivojlanishning uchta ustuni"

msgid "Green Campus"
msgstr "Yashil kampus"

msgid ""
"Landscaped gardens, tree-lined walkways, and outdoor areas that improve air "
"quality and create peaceful learning environments."
msgstr ""
"Chiroyli bog'lar, daraxtli yo'laklar va havo sifatini yaxshilaydigan hamda "
"tinch o'quv muhitini yaratadigan ochiq hududlar."

msgid "Energy Efficiency"
msgstr "Energiya samaradorligi"

msgid ""
"Energy-efficient lighting, heating systems, and building designs that reduce"
" consumption without compromising comfort."
msgstr ""
"Qulaylikdan voz kechmasdan iste'molni kamaytiradigan energiyatejamkor "
"yoritish, isitish tizimlari va bino yechimlari."

msgid "Sustainable Thinking"
msgstr "Barqaror fikrlash"

msgid ""
"Sustainability embedded across our curriculum so students in every "
"department explore environmental and social responsibility."
msgstr ""
"Barqaror rivojlanish g'oyalari o'quv dasturlarimizga singdirilgan — har bir "
"yo'nalish talabasi ekologik va ijtimoiy mas'uliyatni o'rganadi."

msgid "Want to get involved?"
msgstr "Qo'shilmoqchimisiz?"

msgid ""
"Join a green initiative or share your sustainability ideas — together we can"
" build a greener TIU."
msgstr ""
"Yashil tashabbuslarga qo'shiling yoki barqaror rivojlanish bo'yicha "
"g'oyalaringizni baham ko'ring — birgalikda yanada yashilroq TIU quramiz."

msgid ""
"Study at two universities, earn two internationally recognized degrees, and "
"gain the skills and experience to stand out in the global job market."
msgstr ""
"Ikkita universitetda tahsil oling, ikkita xalqaro miqyosda tan olingan "
"diplomga ega bo'ling va jahon mehnat bozorida ajralib turish uchun zarur "
"ko'nikma va tajribani orttiring."

msgid "Two degrees."
msgstr "Ikki diplom."

msgid "One journey."
msgstr "Bitta yo'l."

msgid ""
"In this program, bachelor's students earn two academic degrees upon "
"completion. The first is from Tashkent International University, and the "
"second from one of our partner universities. Students complete two years at "
"TIU and another two years at the partner institution."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu dasturda bakalavriat talabalari o'qishni tamomlagandan so'ng ikkita "
"ilmiy darajaga ega bo'ladi. Birinchisi Toshkent Xalqaro Universitetida, "
"ikkinchisi esa hamkor universitetlarimizdan birida. Talabalar TIUda ikki yil"
" va hamkor universitetda yana ikki yil o'qishadi."

msgid ""
"Those wishing to study in this program must follow a specialized curriculum "
"that meets the course and credit requirements of both TIU and the partner "
"university."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu dasturda o'qishni istaganlar TIU va hamkor universitetning kurs va "
"kredit talablariga mos keladigan maxsus o'quv dasturiga amal qilishlari "
"kerak."

msgid ""
"Participating in a dual degree program gives students numerous advantages. "
"This unique educational path not only equips graduates with a diverse skill "
"set that makes them highly adaptable in the job market, but also provides a "
"competitive edge."
msgstr ""
"Qo'shma diplom dasturida qatnashish talabalarga ko'plab afzalliklarni "
"beradi. Bu noyob ta'lim yo'li nafaqat bitiruvchilarni mehnat bozorida "
"moslashuvchan qiladigan turli ko'nikmalar bilan ta'minlaydi, balki "
"raqobatbardosh ustunlik ham beradi."

msgid "Interested in applying?"
msgstr "Qiziqdingizmi?"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Contact the International Relations Department for detailed information "
"about the program, requirements, and available partner universities."
msgstr ""
"Dastur, talablar va mavjud hamkor universitetlar haqida batafsil ma'lumot "
"olish uchun Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limiga murojaat qiling."

msgid "How it works"
msgstr "Qanday ishlaydi"

msgid ""
"Your step-by-step path from application to graduation with two degrees."
msgstr ""
"Ariza topshirishdan ikkita diplom bilan bitirguncha — bosqichma-bosqich "
"yo'lingiz."

msgid "Apply to TIU"
msgstr "TIUga ariza topshiring"

msgid ""
"Submit your application to TIU and indicate your interest in the joint "
"degree program during the admissions process."
msgstr ""
"TIUga ariza topshiring va qabul jarayonida qo'sha diplom dasturida o'qish "
"istagingizni bildiring."

msgid "Study at TIU"
msgstr "TIUda tahsil oling"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Complete your first two years at TIU, following the specialized curriculum "
"that meets both universities' requirements."
msgstr ""
"Birinchi ikki yilni TIUda o'tkazib, ikkala universitet talablariga javob "
"beradigan maxsus o'quv rejasi bo'yicha o'qing."

msgid "Transfer abroad"
msgstr "Chet elga o'ting"

msgid ""
"Move to a partner university to complete the remaining two years. Your "
"credits transfer seamlessly — no extra exams needed."
msgstr ""
"Qolgan ikki yilni tugatish uchun hamkor universitetga o'ting. Kreditlaringiz"
" muammosiz o'tkaziladi — qo'shimcha imtihonlar talab qilinmaydi."

msgid "Graduate with two degrees"
msgstr "Ikkita diplom bilan bitiring"

msgid ""
"Receive diplomas from both TIU and the partner university — fully recognized"
" in Uzbekistan and internationally."
msgstr ""
"TIU va hamkor universitetdan diplomlarni qo'lga kiriting — O'zbekistonda "
"ham, xalqaro miqyosda ham to'liq tan olingan."

msgid "Why choose a joint degree?"
msgstr "Nima uchun qo'shma diplomni tanlash kerak?"

msgid "Competitive Advantage"
msgstr "Raqobatbardosh ustunlik"

msgid ""
"Holders of two degrees stand out in front of employers, expanding career "
"opportunities across multiple fields and industries."
msgstr ""
"Ikki diplomga ega bo'lganlar ish beruvchilar oldida ajralib turadi va turli "
"sohalarda karyera imkoniyatlarini kengaytiradi."

msgid "Global Experience"
msgstr "Xalqaro tajriba"

msgid ""
"Living and studying in another country develops your international "
"perspective, cross-cultural skills, and professional network."
msgstr ""
"Boshqa mamlakatda yashash va o'qish xalqaro dunyoqarash, madaniyatlararo "
"ko'nikmalar va professional aloqalarni rivojlantiradi."

msgid "Personal Growth"
msgstr "Shaxsiy o'sish"

msgid ""
"The program fosters independence, problem-solving skills, and adaptability —"
" qualities that prepare you for success in today's fast-changing world."
msgstr ""
"Dastur mustaqillik, muammolarni hal qilish ko'nikmalari va "
"moslashuvchanlikni rivojlantiradi — bugungi tez o'zgarayotgan dunyoda "
"muvaffaqiyatga tayyorlaydigan sifatlar."

msgid "Fast Track"
msgstr "Tez yo'l"

msgid ""
"Earn two bachelor's degrees in a shorter time compared to completing each "
"program separately, allowing you to enter the job market sooner."
msgstr ""
"Har bir dasturni alohida tugatishga nisbatan qisqa vaqtda ikkita bakalavriat"
" darajasini oling va mehnat bozoriga tezroq kiring."

msgid "Important Information"
msgstr "Muhim ma'lumot"

msgid "Fees and scholarships"
msgstr "To'lovlar va grantlar"

msgid ""
"Students participating in the 2+2 program are not required to pay any fees "
"to TIU after transferring to the partner university. Any scholarships held "
"at TIU before the transfer are considered cancelled."
msgstr ""
"2+2 dasturida qatnashayotgan talabalar hamkor universitetga o'tgandan keyin "
"TIUga hech qanday to'lov amalga oshirishi shart emas. O'tkazilgunga qadar "
"TIUda mavjud bo'lgan grantlar bekor qilingan hisoblanadi."

msgid ""
"However, in some cases, agreements between TIU and the receiving university "
"may require students to continue paying TIU fees. Students are advised to "
"consult with the International Relations Department regarding payment terms "
"and scholarships before applying."
msgstr ""
"Biroq, ba'zi hollarda TIU va qabul qiluvchi universitet o'rtasidagi "
"kelishuvlarga ko'ra talabalardan TIU to'lovlarini to'lashni davom ettirish "
"talab qilinishi mumkin. Talabalarga ariza topshirishdan oldin to'lov "
"shartlari va grantlar bo'yicha Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi bilan "
"maslahatlashish tavsiya etiladi."

msgid "Contact International Relations"
msgstr "Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limiga murojaat qilish"

msgid ""
"Study at an international partner university for a semester or academic year"
" — expand your horizons without extending your studies."
msgstr ""
"Xalqaro hamkor universitetda bir semestr yoki bir o'quv yili davomida tahsil"
" oling — o'qish muddatingizni uzaytirmasdan dunyoqarashingizni kengaytiring."

msgid "Discover the world"
msgstr "Dunyoni kashf eting"

msgid "while you study."
msgstr "o'qish davomida."

msgid ""
"TIU's academic exchange program is organized in partnership with "
"international universities. It gives students the opportunity to study "
"abroad, gain international experience, and broaden their academic and "
"cultural skills — all while remaining enrolled at TIU."
msgstr ""
"TIUning akademik almashinuv dasturi xalqaro universitetlar bilan hamkorlikda"
" tashkil etilgan. Dastur talabalarga TIUda ro'yxatda qolgan holda chet elda "
"tahsil olish, xalqaro tajriba orttirish hamda akademik va madaniy "
"ko'nikmalarini kengaytirish imkonini beradi."

msgid ""
"Exchange students immerse themselves in a different academic environment, "
"improve their language abilities, and develop the independence and "
"adaptability that employers highly value. Credits earned at the partner "
"university transfer directly back to your TIU degree."
msgstr ""
"Almashinuv talabalari boshqa akademik muhitga to'liq singishadi, til "
"bilimlarini oshiradi va ish beruvchilar yuqori baholaydigan mustaqillik "
"hamda moslashuvchanlikni rivojlantiradi. Hamkor universitetda to'plangan "
"kreditlar bevosita TIU diplomingizga o'tkaziladi."

msgid ""
"The International Relations Department supports you at every step — from "
"choosing a destination and preparing documents to arranging accommodation "
"and visa support."
msgstr ""
"Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi sizga har bir bosqichda — yo'nalish tanlashdan "
"tortib hujjatlar tayyorlash, turar joy va viza masalalarini hal qilishgacha "
"— yordam beradi."

msgid "Want two full degrees instead?"
msgstr "Ikkita to'liq diplomni xohlaysizmi?"

msgid ""
"If you're looking to graduate with diplomas from two universities, explore "
"our Joint Degrees program."
msgstr ""
"Agar ikkita universitetdan diplom bilan bitirmoqchi bo'lsangiz, Qo'sha "
"diplom dasturimiz bilan tanishing."

msgid "What you gain"
msgstr "Nimaga ega bo'lasiz"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"An exchange at TIU is more than studying abroad — it's a complete "
"international experience."
msgstr ""
"TIUdagi almashinuv dasturi shunchaki chet elda o'qish emas — bu to'laqonli "
"xalqaro tajriba."

msgid "Seamless Credit Transfer"
msgstr "Kreditlarning muammosiz o'tkazilishi"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All credits earned at the partner university transfer directly to your TIU "
"degree. No repeated courses, no time lost."
msgstr ""
"Hamkor universitetda to'plangan barcha kreditlar bevosita TIU diplomingizga "
"o'tkaziladi. Takroriy fanlar yo'q, vaqt yo'qotilmaydi."

msgid "No Extra Tuition"
msgstr "Qo'shimcha to'lovsiz"

msgid ""
"You continue paying TIU fees during your exchange. Partner university "
"tuition is waived under our agreements."
msgstr ""
"Almashinuv davomida siz TIU to'lovlarini to'lashda davom etasiz. Hamkor "
"universitetdagi to'lov kelishuvlarimiz asosida olib tashlanadi."

msgid "Cultural Immersion"
msgstr "Madaniy tajriba"

msgid ""
"Live in a new country, experience a different academic culture first-hand, "
"and develop cross-cultural skills valued by employers worldwide."
msgstr ""
"Yangi mamlakatda yashang, boshqa akademik madaniyatni bevosita his qiling va"
" butun dunyo ish beruvchilari qadrlaydigan madaniyatlararo ko'nikmalarni "
"rivojlantiring."

msgid "International Network"
msgstr "Xalqaro aloqalar tarmog'i"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Build lasting friendships and professional connections with students from "
"around the world."
msgstr ""
"Dunyo bo'ylab talabalar bilan uzoq muddatli do'stlik va kasbiy aloqalar "
"o'rnating."

msgid "Full Support"
msgstr "To'liq qo'llab-quvvatlash"

