#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid ""
"TIU degrees are recognized worldwide. Our partnerships with international "
"universities mean your qualification opens doors globally."
msgstr ""
"TIU diplomlari butun dunyoda tan olinadi. Xalqaro universitetlar bilan "
"hamkorligimiz sizning malakangiz global eshiklarni ochishini anglatadi."

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
