#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid ""
"Dedicated visa assistance, housing help, academic advising, language "
"support, and a 24/7 student helpline — all for international students."
msgstr ""
"Viza yordami, turar joy topishda ko'mak, akademik maslahat, til bo'yicha "
"qo'llab-quvvatlash va 24/7 talabalar yordami — barchasi xorijiy talabalar "
"uchun."

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid "International application deadline: 1 June 2026"
msgstr ""
"Xorijiy abituriyentlar uchun ariza topshirish muddati: 2026-yil 1-iyun"

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid ""
"Don't leave it too late. International applicants have an earlier deadline "
"to allow time for visa processing, document verification, and travel "
"arrangements. Apply early to secure your place."
msgstr ""
"Kechikmang. Xorijiy abituriyentlar uchun viza rasmiyatlari, hujjatlarni "
"tekshirish va sayohat rejalari uchun vaqt ajratish maqsadida muddatlar "
"ertaroq belgilangan. O'rningizni ta'minlash uchun erta ariza topshiring."

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid "View all deadlines"
msgstr "Barcha muddatlarni ko'rish"

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid "International Applicant FAQs"
msgstr "Xorijiy abituriyentlar uchun ko'p beriladigan savollar"

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid "Do I need a visa to study in Uzbekistan?"
msgstr "O'zbekistonda o'qish uchun viza kerakmi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid ""
"Most international students require a student visa (type \"O'T-2\") to study"
" in Uzbekistan. Citizens of some CIS countries may be exempt. TIU's "
"International Office will issue an official invitation letter to support "
"your visa application once you've been accepted."
msgstr ""
"Ko'pchilik xorijiy talabalar O'zbekistonda o'qish uchun talaba vizasiga "
"(\"O'T-2\" turi) muhtoj. Ba'zi MDH davlatlari fuqarolari bundan mustasno "
"bo'lishi mumkin. TIUning Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi qabul qilinganingizdan "
"so'ng viza arizangizni qo'llab-quvvatlash uchun rasmiy taklifnoma xatini "
"beradi."

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid "Does TIU provide accommodation for international students?"
msgstr "TIU xorijiy talabalar uchun turar joy bilan ta'minlaydimi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid ""
"Yes. TIU offers student housing options both on and near campus. "
"International students are given priority for university accommodation. "
"Alternatively, we can help you find private rental options in Tashkent at "
"affordable rates."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU kampus ichida va yaqinida talabalar turar joyi variantlarini taklif "
"qiladi. Xorijiy talabalarga universitet yotoqxonasida ustunlik beriladi. "
"Bundan tashqari, Toshkentda arzon narxlarda xususiy ijaraga uy topishda "
"yordam berishimiz mumkin."

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid "What is the cost of living in Tashkent?"
msgstr "Toshkentda yashash qancha turadi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid ""
"Tashkent is one of the most affordable capital cities in the region. On "
"average, students spend approximately $300-500 USD per month on rent, food, "
"transport, and personal expenses — significantly lower than most European or"
" Asian cities."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent mintaqadagi eng arzon poytaxtlardan biri. O'rtacha talabalar oyiga "
"ijara, ovqat, transport va shaxsiy xarajatlarga taxminan 300-500 AQSh "
"dollari sarflaydi — bu ko'pgina Yevropa yoki Osiyo shaharlariga qaraganda "
"sezilarli darajada kam."

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid "Can I work while studying on a student visa?"
msgstr "Talaba vizasi bilan o'qish paytida ishlasam bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid ""
"Part-time work opportunities may be available depending on your visa "
"conditions. TIU also offers on-campus work-study positions and internship "
"placements through our Career Centre. Contact the International Office for "
"the latest regulations."
msgstr ""
"Viza shartlaringizga qarab yarim kunlik ish imkoniyatlari mavjud bo'lishi "
"mumkin. TIU shuningdek kampus ichida ish-o'qish lavozimlarini va Karyera "
"markazi orqali amaliyot o'rinlarini taklif qiladi. So'nggi qoidalar haqida "
"Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limiga murojaat qiling."

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid "Is there an orientation programme for new international students?"
msgstr "Yangi xorijiy talabalar uchun moslashuv dasturi bormi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Absolutely. Every September, we run a dedicated International Orientation "
"Week that includes campus tours, city tours, registration support, SIM card "
"and bank account setup, and social events to help you settle in and make "
"friends before classes begin."
msgstr ""
"Albatta. Har yili sentyabr oyida biz maxsus Xalqaro moslashuv haftasini "
"o'tkazamiz — kampus va shahar bo'yicha ekskursiyalar, ro'yxatdan o'tish "
"yordami, SIM-karta va bank hisobi ochish, shuningdek darslar boshlanishidan "
"oldin joylashish va yangi do'stlar orttirish uchun ijtimoiy tadbirlar."

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid "Are scholarships available for international students?"
msgstr "Xorijiy talabalar uchun grantlar mavjudmi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/apply-international.html
msgid ""
"Yes. TIU offers merit-based scholarships for high-achieving international "
"applicants covering up to 50% of tuition fees. Additional financial aid and "
"fee discounts may be available. Visit our scholarships page for full details"
" and eligibility criteria."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU yuqori natijalarga erishgan xorijiy abituriyentlarga kontrakt "
"to'lovining 50% gacha qoplaydigan grantlarni taklif qiladi. Qo'shimcha "
"moliyaviy yordam va chegirmalar ham mavjud bo'lishi mumkin. To'liq ma'lumot "
"va mezonlar uchun grantlar sahifamizga tashrif buyuring."

msgid "Are there scholarships available?"
msgstr "Stipendiya va grantlar bormi?"

msgid ""
"Yes! TIU offers merit-based and need-based scholarships covering up to 100% "
"of tuition fees. Scholarships are awarded based on academic achievement, "
"entrance exam results, and financial need. Visit our Scholarships page for "
"details and application deadlines."
msgstr ""
"Albatta! TIU o'quv to'lovining 100% gacha qoplaydigan iqtidor va ehtiyojga "
"asoslangan grantlar taklif etadi. Grantlar akademik yutuqlar, kirish "
"imtihoni natijalari va moliyaviy ahvol asosida beriladi. Batafsil ma'lumot "
"uchun Stipendiyalar sahifasiga qarang."

msgid "Can I pay tuition in instalments?"
msgstr "Kontrakt to'lovini bo'lib to'lasa bo'ladimi?"

msgid ""
"Yes, TIU offers flexible payment plans. Tuition can be paid per semester or "
"in monthly instalments. Contact the finance office for payment plan options "
"and deadlines."
msgstr ""
"Ha, TIU qulay to'lov rejalarini taklif etadi. To'lovni semestr bo'yicha yoki"
" oylik qilib to'lash mumkin. To'lov tartibi va muddatlari haqida moliya "
"bo'limiga murojaat qiling."

msgid "Is there student housing available?"
msgstr "Talabalar uchun turar joy bormi?"

msgid ""
"TIU offers modern student housing near campus. Rooms are furnished and "
"include internet, utilities, and shared common areas. Housing is allocated "
"on a first-come, first-served basis, so early application is recommended."
msgstr ""
"TIU kampus yaqinida zamonaviy turar joy taklif etadi. Xonalar jihozlangan, "
"internet va kommunal xizmatlar kiradi. Joylar navbat tartibida taqsimlanadi,"
" shuning uchun erta murojaat qilish tavsiya etiladi."

msgid "Are there student clubs and organizations?"
msgstr "Talabalar klublari va tashkilotlari bormi?"

msgid ""
"Yes! TIU has 50+ student clubs covering debate, robotics, entrepreneurship, "
"languages, arts, sports, volunteering, and more. Students also organize TEDx"
" events, hackathons, and cultural festivals throughout the year."
msgstr ""
"Albatta! TIU da 50 dan ortiq klub bor — munozara, robototexnika, "
"tadbirkorlik, tillar, san'at, sport, ko'ngillilik va boshqalar. Talabalar "
"yil davomida TEDx tadbirlari, hakatonlar va madaniy festivallar ham tashkil "
"etishadi."

msgid "Does TIU offer career support?"
msgstr "TIU karera bo'yicha yordam beradimi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. Our Career Center provides CV workshops, mock interviews, career fairs,"
" employer networking events, and one-to-one career counselling. Support is "
"available from your first year through graduation and beyond."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Karyera markazimiz rezyume tayyorlash, sinov intervyular, karyera "
"yarmarkalari, ish beruvchilar bilan uchrashuvlar va shaxsiy maslahatlar "
"xizmatini ko'rsatadi. Yordam birinchi kursdan boshlab bitiruvdan keyin ham "
"davom etadi."

msgid "Are there internship opportunities during my studies?"
msgstr "O'qish davomida amaliyot imkoniyatlari bormi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. TIU partners with companies and organisations across Uzbekistan and "
"internationally to provide internship placements. Many programmes include a "
"mandatory internship component to ensure you graduate with real-world "
"experience."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU O'zbekiston va xorijdagi kompaniyalar bilan hamkorlikda amaliyot "
"joylarini taqdim etadi. Ko'plab dasturlarda majburiy amaliyot bo'limi mavjud"
" — bu sizni amaliy tajriba bilan bitiruvchi bo'lishingizni ta'minlaydi."

