#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid "Ready to start your application?"
msgstr "Ariza topshirishga tayyormisiz?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid ""
"Head to our application portal to begin the process. Make sure you have your"
" documents ready and apply before the deadline for your chosen programme."
msgstr ""
"Jarayonni boshlash uchun ariza portalimizga o'ting. Hujjatlaringiz tayyor "
"ekanligiga ishonch hosil qiling va tanlagan yo'nalishingiz muddati "
"tugashidan oldin ariza topshiring."

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid "Start your application"
msgstr "Ariza topshirishni boshlang"

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid "What happens if I miss the application deadline?"
msgstr "Ariza topshirish muddatini o'tkazib yuborsam nima bo'ladi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid ""
"If you miss the deadline for your chosen intake, you may still be considered"
" for late admission depending on programme availability. Contact the "
"Admissions Office at admissions@tiu.uz to discuss your options. We recommend"
" applying as early as possible to secure your place."
msgstr ""
"Tanlangan qabul muddatini o'tkazib yuborsangiz, yo'nalishda bo'sh o'rin "
"mavjudligiga qarab kech qabul ko'rib chiqilishi mumkin. Imkoniyatlaringizni "
"muhokama qilish uchun Qabul bo'limiga admissions@tiu.uz orqali murojaat "
"qiling. O'rningizni ta'minlash uchun imkon qadar erta ariza topshirishni "
"tavsiya etamiz."

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid "When does the academic year start and end?"
msgstr "O'quv yili qachon boshlanadi va tugaydi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid ""
"The academic year begins in September with Orientation Week and runs through"
" to June the following year. Semester 1 covers September to January, "
"Semester 2 runs from February to May, and the summer period (June-August) "
"includes graduation ceremonies and resit examinations."
msgstr ""
"O'quv yili sentyabrda Moslashuv haftasi bilan boshlanadi va keyingi yilning "
"iyunigacha davom etadi. 1-semestr sentyabrdan yanvargacha, 2-semestr "
"fevraldan maygacha bo'lib, yozgi davr (iyun-avgust) bitirish marosimlari va "
"qayta imtihonlarni o'z ichiga oladi."

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid "Are there different deadlines for international students?"
msgstr "Xorijiy talabalar uchun boshqa muddatlar bormi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid ""
"Yes. International applicants typically have an earlier deadline to allow "
"time for visa processing, document verification, and travel arrangements. "
"Check the Application Deadlines table above for the specific dates that "
"apply to your category."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Xorijiy abituriyentlar uchun viza rasmiyatlari, hujjatlarni tekshirish "
"va sayohat rejalarini tuzish uchun vaqt ajratish maqsadida muddatlar odatda "
"ertaroq belgilanadi. Sizning kategoriyangizga tegishli aniq sanalar uchun "
"yuqoridagi Ariza topshirish muddatlari jadvalini tekshiring."

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid "How long does it take to receive a decision after applying?"
msgstr "Ariza topshirgandan keyin qaror qancha vaqtda keladi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid ""
"Most applicants receive a decision within 2-4 weeks of submitting a complete"
" application. During peak periods, it may take slightly longer. You can "
"track your application status through the student portal or by contacting "
"admissions@tiu.uz."
msgstr ""
"Ko'pchilik abituriyentlar to'liq ariza topshirgandan keyin 2-4 hafta ichida "
"qaror oladi. Eng ko'p murojaat kelgan davrlarda biroz ko'proq vaqt ketishi "
"mumkin. Ariza holatini talabalar portali orqali yoki admissions@tiu.uz ga "
"murojaat qilib kuzatishingiz mumkin."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "Admission Process - International Students | TIU"
msgstr "Qabul tartibi — Xorijiy talabalar | TIU"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Your step-by-step guide to joining TIU as an international student — from "
"application to arrival."
msgstr ""
"Xorijiy talaba sifatida TIUga qo'shilish bo'yicha bosqichma-bosqich "
"yo'riqnoma — ariza topshirishdan kelishgacha."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "Applying to TIU is simple and straightforward"
msgstr "TIUga ariza topshirish oddiy va tushunarli"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Whether you're applying from Kazakhstan, South Korea, Turkey, or anywhere "
"else in the world — the process is the same. Everything can be completed "
"online, there's no application fee, and our International Office is "
"available to assist you at every stage. Most applicants receive a decision "
"within two weeks."
msgstr ""
"Qozog'istondan, Janubiy Koreyadan, Turkiyadan yoki dunyoning boshqa "
"burchagidan ariza topshirayotgan bo'lsangiz ham — jarayon bir xil. Hamma "
"narsa onlayn tarzda amalga oshiriladi, ariza uchun to'lov yo'q va Xalqaro "
"aloqalar bo'limimiz har bir bosqichda yordamga tayyor. Aksariyat "
"abituriyentlar ikki hafta ichida javob oladi."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "No Application Fee"
msgstr "Ariza uchun to'lovsiz"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "Apply at zero cost"
msgstr "Bepul ariza topshiring"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"International students pay no application fee. Submit your application and "
"documents online completely free of charge."
msgstr ""
"Xorijiy talabalar ariza uchun hech narsa to'lamaydi. Ariza va "
"hujjatlaringizni onlayn tarzda mutlaqo bepul topshiring."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "Fast Decision"
msgstr "Tezkor javob"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "Get a response within 2 weeks"
msgstr "2 hafta ichida javob oling"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Our admissions committee reviews applications promptly. Most international "
"applicants receive their admission decision within 10–14 working days."
msgstr ""
"Qabul komissiyamiz arizalarni tezkor ko'rib chiqadi. Aksariyat xorijiy "
"abituriyentlar 10–14 ish kuni ichida qabul qarori haqida xabar oladi."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
