#: templates/pages/current-students/it-services.html
msgid "How do I access the student portal (LMS)?"
msgstr "Talabalar portaliga (LMS) qanday kiraman?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/it-services.html
msgid ""
"Visit the LMS website and log in with your student ID and password. You can "
"access course materials, assignments, and grades from any device."
msgstr ""
"LMS veb-saytiga kiring va talaba ID raqamingiz hamda parolingiz bilan "
"tizimga kiring. Dars materiallari, topshiriqlar va baholarni istalgan "
"qurilmadan ko'rishingiz mumkin."

