"To ensure a safe and comfortable environment for all residents, the "
"following rules apply in the TIU dormitory. Violation of these rules may "
"result in termination of your housing contract."
msgstr ""
"Barcha yashlovchilar uchun xavfsiz va qulay muhitni ta'minlash maqsadida TIU"
" yotoqxonasida quyidagi qoidalar amal qiladi. Bu qoidalarni buzish turar joy"
" shartnomangiz bekor qilinishiga olib kelishi mumkin."

#: templates/pages/current-students/housing.html
msgid "Housing FAQs"
