#: templates/pages/current-students/housing.html
msgid "Can I stay in the dormitory over the summer?"
msgstr "Yozda yotoqxonada qolsam bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/housing.html
msgid ""
"Students enrolled in summer courses may request to stay during the summer "
"period. Contact the housing office for details and availability."
msgstr ""
"Yozgi kurslarga yozilgan talabalar yozgi davrda qolishni so'rashi mumkin. "
"Batafsil va mavjudlik uchun turar joy bo'limiga murojaat qiling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/housing.html
msgid "Can I choose my roommate?"
msgstr "Xonado'shimni o'zim tanlasam bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/housing.html
msgid ""
"Yes. If you and another student both request to share a room, we will do our"
" best to accommodate that. Note your preferred roommate's name on the "
"application form."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Agar siz va boshqa talaba birga yashashni so'rasangiz, imkon qadar buni "
"amalga oshiramiz. Ariza shaklida xohlagan xonado'shingiz ismini yozing."

#: templates/pages/current-students/housing.html
msgid "Is the dormitory safe?"
msgstr "Yotoqxona xavfsizmi?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/housing.html
msgid ""
"Yes. The dormitory has 24/7 security, CCTV coverage, access control, and a "
"staffed reception desk. Visitors must sign in and be accompanied by a "
"resident."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Yotoqxonada kunlik qo'riqlash, videokuzatuv, kirish nazorati va xodimli "
"qabulxona bor. Mehmonlar ro'yxatdan o'tishi va yashlovchi hamrohligida "
"bo'lishi shart."

#: templates/pages/current-students/housing.html
msgid "How do I contact the housing office?"
msgstr "Turar joy bo'limiga qanday murojaat qilaman?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/housing.html
msgid ""
"You can reach the housing office by phone at +998 91 798 28 85 or visit us "
"at Minor 76, Tashkent."
msgstr ""
"+998 91 798 28 85 raqamiga qo'ng'iroq qiling yoki Toshkent, Minor 76 "
"manziliga tashrif buyuring."

#: templates/pages/current-students/housing.html
msgid "Can I bring my own furniture?"
msgstr "O'z mebelimni olib kelsam bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/housing.html
msgid ""
"Rooms are fully furnished with a bed, desk, and wardrobe. You are welcome to"
" bring personal items like a desk lamp or bedding. Large furniture is not "
"permitted due to space limitations."
msgstr ""
"Xonalar karavot, ish stoli va shkaf bilan to'liq jihozlangan. Stol chiroq "
"yoki ko'rpa-to'shak kabi shaxsiy narsalarni olib kelishingiz mumkin. Joy "
"cheklanganligi sababli katta mebellar ruxsat etilmaydi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Clubs & Societies - TIU"
msgstr "Klublar va to'garaklar - TIU"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"Join a student club or start your own — connect with like-minded students at"
" TIU."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar klubiga qo'shiling yoki o'zingiznikini yarating — TIUda hamfikr "
"talabalar bilan bog'laning."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Where like-minded students <em>connect</em>"
msgstr "Hamfikr talabalar <em>uchrashadi</em>gan joy"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As a young and fast-growing university founded in 2023, TIU is building a "
"vibrant student community from the ground up. Our clubs give you a chance to"
" find your people — whether you're diving deeper into something you love or "
"trying something completely new."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"2023-yilda tashkil etilgan yosh va tez rivojlanayotgan universitet sifatida TIU faol talabalar jamoasini noldan yaratmoqda. Klublarimiz sizga o'z odamlaringizni topish imkonini beradi — yoqtirgan narsangizni chuqurroq o'rganmoqchimisiz yoki butunlay yangi narsani sinab ko'rmoqchimisiz.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"2023-yilda tashkil etilgan yosh va tez rivojlanayotgan universitet sifatida TIU jonli talabalar jamoasini noldan qurmoqda. Bizning to'garaklarimiz sizga o'z odamlaringizni topish imkonini beradi — sevimli mashg'ulotingizni chuqurlashtirmoqchimisiz yoki butunlay yangi narsani sinab ko'rmoqchimisiz."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"From debate and programming to photography and volunteering, TIU's growing "
"list of student clubs covers a wide range of interests. Whatever you're "
"into, there's a place for you here."
msgstr ""
"Munozara va dasturlashdan tortib fotografiya va ko'ngillilik faoliyatigacha "
"— TIUning tobora ko'payib borayotgan talabalar klublari keng qiziqishlarni "
"qamrab oladi. Qanday sohaga qiziqsangiz ham, bu yerda siz uchun joy bor."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Heads up"
msgstr "Diqqat"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "You'll need to be an enrolled TIU student to join a club or society"
msgstr ""
"Klubga qo'shilish uchun TIUda ro'yxatdan o'tgan talaba bo'lishingiz kerak"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "TIU student clubs"
msgstr "TIU talabalar klublari"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Our clubs and activities"
msgstr "Klublar va faoliyatlarimiz"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"TIU currently has over 10 active student clubs, and the number keeps growing"
" every semester. Our clubs include Debate Club, IT & Programming, Business &"
" Entrepreneurship, Photography, English Speaking Club, Korean Culture Club, "
"Volunteer Club, and Sports Club."
msgstr ""
"TIUda hozirda 10 dan ortiq faol talabalar klubi mavjud va ularning soni har "
"semestrda oshib bormoqda. Klublarimiz orasida Munozara klubi, IT va "
"dasturlash, Biznes va tadbirkorlik, Fotografiya, Ingliz tili suhbat klubi, "
"Koreya madaniyati klubi, Ko'ngillilar klubi va Sport klubi bor."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"Whether you join a casual meetup or a competitive team, clubs are the "
"perfect way to meet new people, develop skills, and make unforgettable "
"memories during your time at TIU."
msgstr ""
"Oddiy uchrashuv yoki raqobatbardosh jamoaga qo'shilsangiz ham, klublar yangi"
" odamlar bilan tanishish, ko'nikmalarni rivojlantirish va TIUda unutilmas "
"xotiralar yaratishning eng yaxshi yo'lidir."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"You'll be supported by dedicated club coordinators and TIU staff who help "
"student initiatives grow and thrive."
msgstr ""
"Sizga maxsus klub koordinatorlari va talabalar tashabbuslarini "
"rivojlantirishga yordam beradigan TIU xodimlari ko'mak beradi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "See all sports teams"
msgstr "Barcha sport jamoalarini ko'rish"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "TIU Clubs"
msgstr "TIU klublari"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Debate Club"
msgstr "Munozara klubi"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "IT & Programming"
msgstr "AT va dasturlash"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Photography"
msgstr "Fotografiya"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "English Speaking Club"
msgstr "Ingliz tili muloqot klubi"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Korean Culture Club"
msgstr "Koreya madaniyati klubi"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Volunteer Club"
msgstr "Ko'ngillilar klubi"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "CAN'T FIND WHAT YOU'RE LOOKING FOR?"
msgstr "IZLAGANINGIZNI TOPA OLMADINGIZMI?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Start your own club or society"
msgstr "O'z klubingizni yarating"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"Don't see anything that suits you? At TIU, you can start your own club with "
"just a few friends. As a young university, we encourage every student "
"initiative — all you need is 3 members and a good idea."
msgstr ""
"O'zingizga mos narsa topa olmadingizmi? TIUda bir necha do'stingiz bilan o'z"
" klubingizni ochishingiz mumkin. Yosh universitet sifatida biz har bir "
"talaba tashabbusini qo'llab-quvvatlaymiz — sizga faqat 3 a'zo va yaxshi "
"g'oya kerak."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"Whether it's a robotics club, a book circle, a music group, or anything else"
" you're passionate about — talk to our Student Affairs office and make it "
"happen."
msgstr ""
"Robototexnika klubi, kitob to'garagi, musiqa guruhi yoki boshqa qiziqarli "
"narsa bo'lsin — Talabalar ishlari bo'limiga murojaat qiling va amalga "
"oshiring."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "New clubs are launching every semester. Yours could be next."
msgstr ""
"Har semestrda yangi klublar ochilmoqda. Navbatdagisi sizniki bo'lishi "
"mumkin."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"TIU's Student Union represents the voice of all students. Every enrolled "
"student is automatically a member — no fees, no sign-up needed."
msgstr ""
"TIU Talabalar kengashi barcha talabalarning ovozini ifodalaydi. Har bir "
"ro'yxatdan o'tgan talaba avtomatik ravishda a'zo bo'ladi — to'lov yoki "
"ro'yxatdan o'tish talab etilmaydi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"The Student Union organizes events, supports club activities, and ensures "
"students have a say in university life. It's your platform to lead, "
"collaborate, and make a difference."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar kengashi tadbirlar tashkil etadi, klub faoliyatini qo'llab-"
"quvvatlaydi va talabalarning universitet hayotida o'z so'zini aytishini "
"ta'minlaydi. Bu sizning boshchilik qilish, hamkorlik qilish va o'zgarish "
"yaratish uchun platformangiz."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"From cultural events and sports days to community projects, the Student "
"Union is at the heart of campus life at TIU."
msgstr ""
"Madaniy tadbirlar va sport kunlaridan jamoa loyihalarigacha — Talabalar "
"kengashi TIU kampus hayotining markazida turadi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Visit TIU Student Union"
msgstr "TIU Talabalar ittifoqiga tashrif buyuring"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Club"
msgstr "Klub"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "TIU Student Union"
msgstr "TIU Talabalar ittifoqi"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"Stay active and healthy with TIU's growing sports facilities, fitness "
"classes, and inter-faculty competitions."
msgstr ""
"TIUning rivojlanayotgan sport inshootlari, fitnes mashg'ulotlari va "
"fakultetlararo musobaqalari bilan faol va sog'lom bo'ling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Move more, achieve more"
msgstr "Ko'proq harakatlaning, ko'proq erishing"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"TIU is a young university, founded in 2023, and our sports programme is "
"growing every semester. Whether you are a seasoned athlete or just looking "
"to stay fit between lectures, there is a place for you here."
msgstr ""
"TIU 2023-yilda tashkil etilgan yosh universitet bo'lib, sport dasturimiz har"
" semestrda rivojlanib bormoqda. Tajribali sportchi bo'lasizmi yoki "
"ma'ruzalar orasida sog'lom bo'lishni xohlaysizmi — bu yerda siz uchun joy "
"bor."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"We offer football, basketball, volleyball, table tennis, and regular fitness"
" classes. Our students take part in inter-faculty tournaments and friendly "
"matches with other Tashkent universities. No experience required — just "
"bring your energy."
msgstr ""
"Biz futbol, basketbol, voleybol, stol tennisi va muntazam fitnes "
"mashg'ulotlarini taklif etamiz. Talabalarimiz fakultetlararo musobaqalarda "
"va Toshkentdagi boshqa universitetlar bilan do'stona o'yinlarda ishtirok "
"etishadi. Tajriba talab qilinmaydi — faqat shijoatingizni olib keling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Our Teams"
msgstr "Jamoalarimiz"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Sport is for everyone at TIU"
msgstr "TIUda sport — hamma uchun"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"You do not need to be a professional to join. Our teams train regularly in "
"the multi-court hall and outdoor pitches. From inter-faculty football "
"tournaments to table tennis leagues, there are plenty of ways to compete and"
" have fun."
msgstr ""
"Qo'shilish uchun professional bo'lishingiz shart emas. Jamoalarimiz ko'p "
"maqsadli sport zalida va ochiq maydonchalarda muntazam mashq qiladi. "
"Fakultetlararo futbol musobaqalaridan stol tennisi ligalarigacha — "
"raqobatlashish va zavqlanish uchun ko'plab imkoniyatlar mavjud."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Explore Clubs & Societies"
msgstr "Klublar va to'garaklarni ko'rish"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Our facilities"
msgstr "Sport inshootlarimiz"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As a growing university, we are steadily expanding our sports "
"infrastructure. All facilities are available to TIU students free of charge."
msgstr ""
"Rivojlanayotgan universitet sifatida sport infratuzilmamizni bosqichma-"
"bosqich kengaytiryapmiz. Barcha inshootlar TIU talabalari uchun bepul."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Gym with cardio equipment and free weights"
msgstr "Kardio jihozlar va erkin og'irliklar bilan trenajyor zali"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Multi-court hall for basketball, volleyball, and futsal"
msgstr "Basketbol, voleybol va futzal uchun ko'p tarmoqli sport zali"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Outdoor football and mini-football pitches"
msgstr "Ochiq futbol va mini-futbol maydonchalar"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Table tennis room"
msgstr "Stol tennisi xonasi"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Changing rooms and showers"
msgstr "Kiyinish xonalari va dushlar"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "How to get involved"
msgstr "Qanday qo'shilish mumkin"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Getting started is easy — no tryouts, no pressure. Just show up."
msgstr "Boshlash oson — sinov yo'q, bosim yo'q. Shunchaki keling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Check the schedule"
msgstr "Jadvalni tekshiring"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"Training times and fitness class schedules are posted on the LMS portal and "
"the sports noticeboard in Building B."
msgstr ""
"Mashg'ulot vaqtlari va fitnes darslar jadvali LMS portalida va B binodagi "
"sport e'lonlar taxtasida joylashtirilgan."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Turn up"
msgstr "Keling"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"Most sessions are open to everyone. Just come to the sports hall or gym at "
"the listed time — no registration needed."
msgstr ""
"Ko'pchilik mashg'ulotlar hamma uchun ochiq. Belgilangan vaqtda sport zaliga "
"yoki trenajyor zaliga keling — ro'yxatdan o'tish shart emas."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Join a team"
msgstr "Jamoaga qo'shiling"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"If you want to compete in inter-faculty tournaments, speak to the team "
"captain or the Sports Coordinator to join the squad."
msgstr ""
"Fakultetlararo musobaqalarda ishtirok etmoqchi bo'lsangiz, jamoa sardori "
"yoki Sport koordinatoriga murojaat qilib jamoaga qo'shiling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Sports FAQs"
msgstr "Sport bo'yicha savollar"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Do I need experience to join a sports team?"
msgstr "Sport jamoasiga qo'shilish uchun tajriba kerakmi?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"Not at all. Our teams welcome all skill levels. Recreational sessions are "
"open to complete beginners, and regular training sessions will help you "
"improve quickly."
msgstr ""
"Umuman yo'q. Jamoalarimiz barcha darajadagi sportchilarni qabul qiladi. Dam "
"olish mashg'ulotlari yangi boshlovchilar uchun ochiq, muntazam mashqlar esa "
"tezda rivojlanishingizga yordam beradi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Are sports facilities free for students?"
msgstr "Sport inshootlari talabalar uchun bepulmi?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"Yes. All on-campus sports facilities are free for enrolled TIU students. "
"Just bring your student ID card."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Kampusdagi barcha sport inshootlari TIU talabalari uchun bepul. Faqat "
"talaba guvohnomangizni olib keling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "What are the opening hours?"
msgstr "Ish vaqti qanday?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"The gym and sports hall are open Monday to Saturday, 08:00–21:00. Team "
"training sessions are usually held in the evenings, 17:00–20:00. Morning "
"exercise sessions start at 07:30 on weekdays."
msgstr ""
"Sport zali va trenajyor zali dushanba–shanba kunlari 08:00–21:00 gacha "
"ochiq. Jamoa mashqlari odatda kechqurun 17:00–20:00 da o'tkaziladi. "
"Ertalabki mashqlar ish kunlari soat 07:30 da boshlanadi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Can I start a new sports team?"
msgstr "Yangi sport jamoasini ochsam bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"Yes. If you have at least 5 interested students, you can propose a new team "
"through the Student Union. The Sports Coordinator will help you arrange "
"training slots and equipment."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Kamida 5 nafar qiziquvchi talaba bo'lsa, Talabalar kengashi orqali yangi"
" jamoa taklif qilishingiz mumkin. Sport koordinatori mashq vaqtlari va "
"jihozlarni tashkil qilishda yordam beradi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"Your voice on campus — learn about the Student Union and how to get "
"involved."
msgstr ""
"Kampusdagi ovozingiz — Talabalar ittifoqi haqida va qanday qo'shilish "
"mumkinligi haqida bilib oling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "What is the Student Union?"
msgstr "Talabalar ittifoqi nima?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"Tashkent International University's Student Union — Talabalar Kengashi — is "
"the student-led body that represents all TIU students. Founded alongside the"
" university in 2023, the Student Union is still young and growing, just like"
" TIU itself."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent xalqaro universitetining Talabalar Kengashi — bu barcha TIU "
"talabalarini ifodalovchi, talabalar tomonidan boshqariladigan tashkilotdir. "
"2023-yilda universitet bilan birga tashkil etilgan Talabalar Kengashi hali "
"yosh va rivojlanmoqda — xuddi TIU ning o'zi kabi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"Our mission is simple: represent student interests, organize memorable "
"events, and serve as a bridge between students and the university "
"administration. Every enrolled student is automatically a member."
msgstr ""
"Bizning maqsadimiz oddiy: talabalar manfaatlarini himoya qilish, esda "
"qolarli tadbirlar tashkil etish va talabalar bilan universitet ma'muriyati "
"o'rtasida ko'prik bo'lib xizmat qilish. Har bir ro'yxatga olingan talaba "
"avtomatik ravishda a'zo hisoblanadi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"The Student Union is where your ideas turn into real campus life. We are a "
"small but active team, and every student voice matters."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar Kengashi — bu sizning g'oyalaringiz haqiqiy kampus hayotiga "
"aylanadigan joy. Biz kichik, lekin faol jamoamiz va har bir talabaning ovozi"
" muhim."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Sardor Alimov"
msgstr "Sardor Alimov"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "President of Student Union 2025/26"
msgstr "Talabalar ittifoqi raisi 2025/26"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "For"
msgstr "Talabalar"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "students,"
msgstr "uchun,"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "by"
msgstr "talabalar"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "students"
msgstr "tomonidan"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"The Student Union is run entirely by students. Our elected leaders work "
"closely with the university administration to voice your concerns, improve "
"campus life, and make sure every student feels heard. Anyone can run for a "
"leadership role — no experience required, just passion."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar Kengashi to'liq talabalar tomonidan boshqariladi. Saylangan "
"rahbarlarimiz sizning tashvishlaringizni bildirish, kampus hayotini "
"yaxshilash va har bir talabaning ovozi eshitilishini ta'minlash uchun "
"universitet ma'muriyati bilan yaqin hamkorlik qiladi. Har kim rahbarlik "
"lavozimiga nomzod bo'lishi mumkin — tajriba shart emas, faqat ishtiyoq "
"kerak."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "TIU Student Union members"
msgstr "TIU Talabalar ittifoqi a'zolari"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Meet new people, make lasting friendships"
msgstr "Yangi odamlar bilan tanishing, uzoq muddatli do'stliklar quling"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"Join a club, play sports, or volunteer — these are the best ways to find "
"your people at TIU. We have a growing number of student clubs, sports teams,"
" and creative groups. You can also start your own."
msgstr ""
"Klubga qo'shiling, sport bilan shug'ullaning yoki ko'ngillilik qiling — TIU "
"da o'z odamlaringizni topishning eng yaxshi yo'llari shu. Talabalar "
"klublari, sport jamoalari va ijodiy guruhlar soni ortib bormoqda. O'zingiz "
"ham yangi guruh tashkil qilishingiz mumkin."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Make your voice heard"
msgstr "Ovozingizni eshittiring"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"The Student Union represents your interests — from course feedback to "
"university decisions. Attend Student Council meetings, vote in elections, or"
" run for a leadership position yourself."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar Kengashi sizning manfaatlaringizni ifodalaydi — kurs bo'yicha "
"fikr-mulohazalardan tortib universitet qarorlarigacha. Talabalar kengashi "
"yig'ilishlarida qatnashing, saylovlarda ovoz bering yoki o'zingiz rahbarlik "
"lavozimiga nomzod bo'ling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Get involved"
msgstr "Qo'shiling"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Events that bring campus to life"
msgstr "Kampusni jonlantiradigan tadbirlar"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"From Navro'z celebrations and sport tournaments to cultural evenings and "
"end-of-year festivities — the Student Union organizes events throughout the "
"year that make student life unforgettable."
msgstr ""
"Navro'z bayramlari va sport musobaqalaridan madaniy kechalar va yil "
"yakunidagi tantanalargacha — Talabalar Kengashi yil davomida talabalar "
"hayotini unutilmas qiladigan tadbirlar tashkil etadi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "View events"
msgstr "Tadbirlarni ko'rish"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Connect with university administration"
msgstr "Universitet ma'muriyati bilan bog'laning"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"The Student Union serves as your direct link to the university "
"administration. If you have questions, concerns, or ideas — we bring them to"
" the table on your behalf."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar Kengashi sizning universitet ma'muriyati bilan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri "
"aloqangiz hisoblanadi. Savollaringiz, tashvishlaringiz yoki g'oyalaringiz "
"bo'lsa — biz ularni sizning nomingizdan yetkazamiz."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Get support"
msgstr "Yordam oling"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Where to find the Student Union on campus?"
msgstr "Talabalar ittifoqini kampusda qayerdan topish mumkin?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"The Student Union office is located in the main building. Drop by during "
"working hours — our team is always happy to chat, answer questions, or hear "
"your ideas for campus life."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar Kengashi ofisi asosiy binoda joylashgan. Ish vaqtida tashrif "
"buyuring — jamoamiz har doim suhbatlashishga, savollarga javob berishga yoki"
" kampus hayoti bo'yicha g'oyalaringizni eshitishga tayyor."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "FOLLOW TIUSU"
msgstr "TIUSU NI KUZATIB BORING"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "TIU Student Union building"
msgstr "TIU Talabalar ittifoqi binosi"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Visit TIU"
msgstr "TIUga tashrif buyuring"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "you get here"
msgstr "kelmasdan turib"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"Take a virtual tour of our modern campus, student spaces, and Tashkent "
"itself: a city that combines rich history with a vibrant student scene. "
"There's lots to see and loads to do. So, let's get going..."
msgstr ""
"Zamonaviy kampusimiz, talabalar makonlari va Toshkent shahrining virtual "
"sayohatiga chiqing: boy tarixi va jonli talabalar muhitini birlashtirgan "
"shahar. Ko'rish va qilish uchun juda ko'p narsa bor. Xo'sh, boshlaylik..."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Start your virtual tour now"
msgstr "Virtual turni hozir boshlang"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "TIU campus life"
msgstr "TIU kampus hayoti"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"Helping TIU students prepare for their first professional steps — with CV "
"support, interview coaching, and direct employer connections."
msgstr ""
"TIU talabalariga kasbiy hayotdagi birinchi qadamlariga tayyorlanishda yordam"
" — rezyume yozish, suhbatga tayyorgarlik va ish beruvchilar bilan "
"to'g'ridan-to'g'ri aloqa."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "Find your path from the start"
msgstr "Yo'lingizni boshidanoq toping"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"TIU was founded in 2023, and our Career Center has been part of the journey "
"since the very beginning. We believe career preparation should start early —"
" not after graduation."
msgstr ""
"TIU 2023-yilda tashkil etilgan va Karyera markazi boshidanoq bu yo'lning bir"
" qismi. Kareraga tayyorgarlik erta boshlanishi kerak — bitirganidan keyin "
"emas."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"Our small but dedicated team works with every student individually, offering"
" practical guidance on building a strong CV, preparing for interviews, and "
"understanding what employers in Uzbekistan are looking for."
msgstr ""
"Kichik, ammo fidoyi jamoamiz har bir talaba bilan yakka tartibda ishlaydi — "
"kuchli rezyume tuzish, suhbatga tayyorlanish va O'zbekistondagi ish "
"beruvchilar nimani izlashini tushunish bo'yicha amaliy maslahatlar beradi."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"We organise regular CV workshops, mock interview sessions, and career "
"counseling meetings to help you feel confident and ready when opportunities "
"come your way."
msgstr ""
"Imkoniyatlar kelganda o'zingizga ishonchli va tayyor bo'lishingiz uchun "
"muntazam rezyume seminarlari, sinov suhbatlari va karera maslahatlari "
"tashkil qilamiz."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"Whether you are looking for an internship, part-time work, or simply want to"
" explore your options — our door is always open."
msgstr ""
"Amaliyot, yarim kunlik ish izlayotgan bo'lsangiz yoki shunchaki "
"imkoniyatlaringizni o'rganmoqchi bo'lsangiz — eshigimiz doimo ochiq."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "CV workshops"
msgstr "Rezyume seminarlari"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"Learn how to write a clear, professional CV that stands out. Our workshops "
"cover formatting, content, and how to tailor your application for different "
"roles — practical skills you will use throughout your career."
msgstr ""
"Aniq va professional rezyume yozishni o'rganing. Seminarlarimizda "
"formatlash, mazmun va turli lavozimlar uchun arizani moslashtirish ko'rib "
"chiqiladi — kareraning har bir bosqichida kerak bo'ladigan amaliy "
"ko'nikmalar."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "Interview preparation"
msgstr "Suhbatga tayyorgarlik"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"Practice with mock interviews and get honest feedback from our career "
"advisors. We help you prepare answers, build confidence, and learn what "
"hiring managers in Uzbekistan expect from candidates."
msgstr ""
"Sinov suhbatlarda mashq qiling va karyera maslahatchilarimizdan samimiy fikr"
" oling. Javoblarni tayyorlash, o'ziga ishonchni mustahkamlash va "
"O'zbekistondagi ish beruvchilar nomzodlardan nimani kutishini tushunishda "
"yordam beramiz."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "Career counseling"
msgstr "Karyera maslahati"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"Not sure which direction to go? Our advisors sit down with you one-on-one to"
" discuss your interests, strengths, and the career paths available to you "
"after graduation."
msgstr ""
"Qaysi yo'nalishga borishni bilmayapsizmi? Maslahatchilarimiz siz bilan yakka"
" tartibda o'tirib, qiziqishlaringiz, kuchli tomonlaringiz va bitirganidan "
"keyingi karera yo'llarini muhokama qiladi."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"We are building relationships with companies across Tashkent and beyond. "
"Through career fairs, guest lectures, and networking events, we connect you "
"directly with employers who are looking for fresh talent."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent va undan tashqaridagi kompaniyalar bilan aloqalar o'rnatyapmiz. "
"Karera yarmarkalari, mehmon ma'ruzalar va tarmoq tadbirlari orqali sizni "
"yangi iste'dodlar izlayotgan ish beruvchilar bilan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri "
"bog'laymiz."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "Start building your experience now"
msgstr "Tajribangizni hozirdanoq orttiring"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"You do not need to wait until graduation to start your career journey. Our "
"Career Center helps you find real opportunities while you study."
msgstr ""
"Karera yo'lini boshlash uchun bitirguncha kutish shart emas. Karyera "
"markazimiz o'qish davomida haqiqiy imkoniyatlar topishda yordam beradi."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "Internship placements"
msgstr "Amaliyot o'rinlari"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"We help match students with internship opportunities at companies in "
"Tashkent and across Uzbekistan"
msgstr ""
"Talabalarga Toshkent va butun O'zbekistondagi kompaniyalarda amaliyot "
"o'rinlarini topishda yordam beramiz"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "Job fairs and employer events"
msgstr "Ish yarmarkalari va ish beruvchilar tadbirlari"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "meet hiring managers face-to-face and learn about career opportunities"
msgstr ""
"ish beruvchilar bilan yuzma-yuz uchrashing va karera imkoniyatlari haqida "
"bilib oling"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "Guest lectures from industry professionals"
msgstr "Soha mutaxassislaridan mehmon ma'ruzalar"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "hear firsthand what it takes to succeed in different fields"
msgstr ""
"turli sohalarda muvaffaqiyatga erishish uchun nima kerakligini bevosita "
"eshiting"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "One-on-one career consultations"
msgstr "Yakka tartibdagi karyera maslahatlari"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"book a session with our career advisor to discuss your personal goals and "
"next steps"
msgstr ""
"shaxsiy maqsadlaringiz va keyingi qadamlaringizni muhokama qilish uchun "
"karyera maslahatchi bilan uchrashuv belgilang"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "Skills development sessions"
msgstr "Ko'nikmalar rivojlantirish mashg'ulotlari"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"from professional communication to time management — practical skills for "
"the workplace"
msgstr ""
"professional muloqotdan vaqtni boshqarishgacha — ish joyida zarur amaliy "
"ko'nikmalar"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"Gain real-world experience through internship placements at local companies,"
" government agencies, and international partner organisations coordinated by"
" TIU."
msgstr ""
"TIU tashkil etgan mahalliy kompaniyalar, davlat tashkilotlari va xalqaro "
"hamkor muassasalardagi amaliyot orqali haqiqiy tajriba orttiring."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Why host a TIU intern?"
msgstr "Nega TIU amaliyotchisini qabul qilish kerak?"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"TIU is a young and ambitious university founded in 2023, with students "
"studying across five departments — Business & Economics, IT, Education, "
"Foreign Languages, and Jurisprudence. Our students are multilingual, "
"motivated, and eager to apply their knowledge in real workplace settings."
msgstr ""
"TIU — 2023-yilda tashkil etilgan yosh va shijoatli universitet. "
"Talabalarimiz beshta yo'nalishda — Biznes va iqtisodiyot, AT, Pedagogika, "
"Xorijiy tillar va Huquqshunoslikda tahsil oladi. Ular ko'p tilli, g'ayratli "
"va bilimlarini haqiqiy ish muhitida qo'llashga tayyor."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By hosting one of our interns, your organisation gains access to fresh "
"talent while helping shape the next generation of professionals in "
"Uzbekistan."
msgstr ""
"Amaliyotchilarimizdan birini qabul qilib, tashkilotingiz yangi iste'dodlarga"
" ega bo'ladi va O'zbekistondagi yangi avlod mutaxassislarni shakllantirishga"
" hissa qo'shadi."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"We are actively building our network of internship partners and would love "
"to work with you."
msgstr ""
"Amaliyot hamkorlari tarmog'imizni faol kengaytiryapmiz va siz bilan "
"ishlashdan mamnun bo'lamiz."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Offer internship placements"
msgstr "Amaliyot o'rinlarini taklif qiling"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "for our students during the summer period or their final year of study"
msgstr "talabalarimiz uchun yozgi davrda yoki o'qishning oxirgi yilida"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Connect with motivated, multilingual students"
msgstr "G'ayratli, ko'p tilli talabalar bilan bog'laning"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"who are ready to contribute to your team and learn from experienced "
"professionals"
msgstr ""
"jamoangizga hissa qo'shishga va tajribali mutaxassislardan o'rganishga "
"tayyor"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Receive support from our Career Center"
msgstr "Karyera markazimizdan yordam oling"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "to match the right students with your organisation's needs"
msgstr "tashkilotingiz ehtiyojlariga mos talabalarni tanlash uchun"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Participate in career events on campus"
msgstr "Kampusdagi karyera tadbirlarida ishtirok eting"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"to meet students in person and introduce your company to future graduates"
msgstr ""
"talabalar bilan shaxsan tanishing va kompaniyangizni bo'lajak "
"bitiruvchilarga tanishtiring"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Benefit from fresh perspectives"
msgstr "Yangicha fikrlardan foydalaning"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "from students trained in the latest approaches in their field of study"
msgstr ""
"o'z sohasidagi eng zamonaviy yondashuvlar bo'yicha tayyorlangan talabalardan"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Internship programme for students"
msgstr "Talabalar uchun amaliyot dasturi"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"TIU students can undertake internships during the summer break or as part of"
" their final-year requirements. Our Career Center and International "
"Relations Department work together to help students find suitable placements"
" both locally and abroad."
msgstr ""
"TIU talabalari yozgi ta'til davomida yoki oxirgi kurs talabi sifatida "
"amaliyot o'tashlari mumkin. Karyera markazi va Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi "
"birgalikda talabalarga mahalliy va xorijda mos amaliyot o'rinlarini topishda"
" yordam beradi."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Current internship opportunities include placements at:"
msgstr "Hozirda mavjud amaliyot imkoniyatlari:"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Banks and financial institutions in Tashkent"
msgstr "Toshkentdagi banklar va moliya muassasalari"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "IT and technology companies across Uzbekistan"
msgstr "O'zbekiston bo'ylab AT va texnologiya kompaniyalari"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Law firms, courts, and government agencies"
msgstr "Yuridik firmalar, sudlar va davlat organlari"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Schools, language centres, and educational organisations"
msgstr "Maktablar, til markazlari va ta'lim tashkilotlari"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"The International Relations Department also assists students interested in "
"internships abroad through our growing network of international partner "
"universities and organisations."
msgstr ""
"Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi chet elda amaliyotga qiziqgan talabalarga tobora "
"kengayib borayotgan xalqaro hamkor universitetlar va tashkilotlar tarmog'i "
"orqali yordam beradi."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Frequently asked questions about internships"
msgstr "Amaliyot bo'yicha ko'p beriladigan savollar"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Below you will find answers to the most common questions about the TIU "
"internship programme. If you have further questions, please contact our "
"Career Center."
msgstr ""
"Quyida TIU amaliyot dasturi haqidagi eng ko'p beriladigan savollarga "
"javoblar keltirilgan. Qo'shimcha savollaringiz bo'lsa, Karyera markazimizga "
"murojaat qiling."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "When can I do an internship?"
msgstr "Amaliyotni qachon o'tash mumkin?"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"Students can complete internships during the summer break (June–August) or "
"during their final year of study as part of the graduation requirements. The"
" Career Center can help you plan the timing that works best for your "
"schedule."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar yozgi ta'tilga (iyun–avgust) yoki oxirgi kursda bitirish "
"talablarining bir qismi sifatida amaliyot o'tashlari mumkin. Karyera markazi"
" jadvalingizga eng mos vaqtni rejalashtirishda yordam beradi."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Can I do an internship abroad?"
msgstr "Chet elda amaliyot o'tasa bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"Yes. The International Relations Department helps students find internship "
"opportunities with our international partner organisations. While the "
"programme is still developing, we are expanding our partnerships each year "
"to offer more options abroad."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi talabalarga xalqaro hamkor tashkilotlarda "
"amaliyot imkoniyatlarini topishda yordam beradi. Dastur hali rivojlanish "
"bosqichida, ammo har yili chet elda ko'proq imkoniyat taklif qilish uchun "
"hamkorliklarimizni kengaytiryapmiz."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Do I need to submit an internship report?"
msgstr "Amaliyotdan keyin hisobot topshirish kerakmi?"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"Yes. All students are required to submit an internship report at the end of "
"their placement. Your academic supervisor will provide guidelines on the "
"report format and evaluation criteria."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Barcha talabalar amaliyot yakunida hisobot topshirishlari shart. Ilmiy "
"rahbaringiz hisobot shakli va baholash mezonlari bo'yicha ko'rsatmalar "
"beradi."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "How do I find an internship placement?"
msgstr "Amaliyot o'rnini qanday topaman?"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"Visit the Career Center to browse available placements with our partner "
"companies. You can also propose your own placement — if you have a company "
"in mind, the Career Center can help you formalise the arrangement."
msgstr ""
"Hamkor kompaniyalardagi mavjud o'rinlarni ko'rish uchun Karyera markaziga "
"tashrif buyuring. O'zingiz ham taklif qilishingiz mumkin — agar ko'zda "
"tutgan kompaniyangiz bo'lsa, Karyera markazi kelishuvni rasmiylashtirishda "
"yordam beradi."

