#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "Why Recruit From TIU?"
msgstr "Nega TIU bitiruvchilarini yollash kerak?"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"Tashkent International University produces graduates who are not only "
"academically excellent but also professionally prepared. Our curriculum "
"integrates real-world projects, international standards, and industry "
"partnerships to ensure students are job-ready from day one."
msgstr ""
"TIU nafaqat akademik jihatdan kuchli, balki ko'p tilli va amaliy "
"ko'nikmalarga ega bitiruvchilarni tayyorlaydi. O'quv dasturimiz real "
"loyihalar, xalqaro standartlar va sanoat hamkorligini o'z ichiga oladi."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"Our students are fluent in multiple languages including Uzbek, Russian, "
"English, and often a fourth language. They bring diverse perspectives, "
"strong analytical skills, and a global mindset to every organization they "
"join."
msgstr ""
"Talabalarimiz o'zbek, rus, ingliz va boshqa tillarni biladi. Ular har bir "
"tashkilotga xilma-xil nuqtai nazar, kuchli tahliliy ko'nikmalar va global "
"tafakkurni olib keladi."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"With programs spanning Business & Economics, IT & Engineering, Law, and "
"Humanities, we offer a broad talent pool across disciplines. Our Career "
"Center team works directly with employers to understand hiring needs and "
"match the right candidates."
msgstr ""
"Biznes, IT, Huquq va Gumanitar fanlar bo'yicha dasturlarimiz keng iqtidor "
"havzasini taklif etadi. Karyera markazimiz ish beruvchilar bilan bevosita "
"ishlaydi."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "What Sets Us Apart"
msgstr "Bizni ajratib turadigan narsa"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "International Curriculum"
msgstr "Xalqaro o'quv dasturi"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"Programs aligned with global standards, accredited internationally, and "
"taught by faculty from leading universities worldwide."
msgstr ""
"Global standartlarga mos dasturlar, xalqaro akkreditatsiya va dunyoning "
"yetakchi universitetlaridan kelgan o'qituvchilar."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "Multilingual Graduates"
msgstr "Ko'p tilli bitiruvchilar"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"Students are proficient in at least three languages, making them ideal for "
"multinational teams and global operations."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar kamida uchta tilni biladi, bu ularni ko'p millatli jamoalar va "
"global operatsiyalar uchun ideal qiladi."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "Industry-Ready Skills"
msgstr "Sohaga tayyor ko'nikmalar"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Capstone projects, internships, and hands-on training ensure graduates can "
"contribute from their first day on the job."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Bitiruv loyihalari, amaliyot va amaliy mashg'ulotlar bitiruvchilarning ishning birinchi kunidan hissa qo'shishini ta'minlaydi.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Yakuniy loyihalar, amaliyotlar va amaliy mashg'ulotlar bitiruvchilarning ishning birinchi kunidanoq samarali bo'lishini ta'minlaydi."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "Proven Track Record"
msgstr "Isbotlangan natijalar"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"92% of our graduates are employed within six months, many at top companies "
"in Central Asia and beyond."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Bitiruvchilarimizning 92% olti oy ichida ishga joylashadi, ko'pchiligi Markaziy Osiyo va undan tashqaridagi yetakchi kompaniyalarda.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Bitiruvchilarimizning 92% olti oy ichida ishga joylashadi, ko'pchiligi Markaziy Osiyo va undan tashqaridagi yetakchi kompaniyalarda ishlaydi."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "Partnership Opportunities"
msgstr "Hamkorlik imkoniyatlari"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"We offer flexible partnership models designed to meet your recruitment "
"goals, whether you are a startup looking for interns or a multinational "
"corporation seeking top graduates."
msgstr ""
"Biz moslashuvchan hamkorlik modellarini taklif etamiz, xoh siz stajyorlarni "
"qidirayotgan startap bo'ling, xoh eng yaxshi bitiruvchilarni izlayotgan "
"xalqaro korporatsiya."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"Each partnership tier includes dedicated support from our employer relations"
" team, access to our student database, and branding opportunities across "
"campus."
msgstr ""
"Har bir hamkorlik darajasi maxsus qo'llab-quvvatlashni o'z ichiga oladi, "
"talabalar bazasiga kirish va kampus bo'ylab brending imkoniyatlari."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"Custom packages are also available for organizations with unique needs. "
"Contact us to discuss a tailored partnership plan."
msgstr ""
"Maxsus paketlar ham mavjud. Moslashtirilgan hamkorlik rejasini muhokama "
"qilish uchun biz bilan bog'laning."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "Job Board Access"
msgstr "Ish e'lonlari"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"Post unlimited job and internship listings on our exclusive job board, "
"reaching thousands of qualified TIU students and alumni."
msgstr ""
"Cheksiz ish va amaliyot e'lonlarini joylashtiring, minglab malakali TIU "
"talabalariga va bitiruvchilariga yeting."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "Career Fair Participation"
msgstr "Karyera yarmarkasida ishtirok"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"Reserve a booth at our biannual career fairs and meet hundreds of candidates"
" in person. Includes branding materials and interview rooms."
msgstr ""
"Ikki yillik karyera yarmarkalarimizda stend band qiling va yuzlab nomzodlar "
"bilan shaxsan uchrashing. Brending materiallari va suhbat xonalari kiradi."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "On-Campus Presence"
msgstr "Kampusda ishtirok"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"Host branded info sessions, workshops, and hackathons on campus. Build your "
"employer brand directly with students."
msgstr ""
"Kampusda info sessiyalar, seminarlar va xakatonlar tashkil eting. Ish "
"beruvchi brendingizni to'g'ridan-to'g'ri talabalar bilan quling."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "Strategic Partnership"
msgstr "Strategik hamkorlik"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"Co-develop curriculum, sponsor research projects, and gain priority access "
"to top talent through our exclusive strategic partner program."
msgstr ""
"O'quv dasturini birgalikda ishlab chiqing, tadqiqot loyihalarini homiylik "
"qiling va strategik hamkorlik dasturimiz orqali eng yaxshi iqtidorlarga "
"ustuvor kirish huquqiga ega bo'ling."

