msgstr "Asl nusxani ko'rish"

msgid "Your Student Union"
msgstr "Talabalar Kengashingiz"

msgid "Your journey starts here"
msgstr "Yo'lingiz shu yerdan boshlanadi"

msgid "Live close to where you learn"
msgstr "O'qish joyingizga yaqin yashang"

msgid "Your voice matters — let's make it heard"
msgstr "Sizning ovozingiz muhim — uni eshittiring"

msgid "Stay active, stay sharp"
msgstr "Faol bo'ling, doimo tetik bo'ling"

msgid "Find your people, find your passion"
msgstr "O'zingizga yaqin odamlarni toping, qiziqishlaringizni kashf eting"

msgid "One day that launches a lifetime"
msgstr "Butun umrga yo'l ochadigan bir kun"

msgid "See TIU before you get here"
msgstr "TIUni kelmasdan ko'ring"

msgid "Hear it from those who know"
msgstr "Bilganlardan eshiting"

msgid ""
"Tashkent International University is a private university located in "
"Tashkent, the capital of Uzbekistan. It opened its doors to students in "
"October 2023. The university has four departments: Business, Education, IT, "
"and Foreign Languages. We offer bachelor's and master's programs in these "
"fields."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent xalqaro universiteti — O'zbekiston poytaxti Toshkentda joylashgan "
"nodavlat oliy ta'lim muassasasi. Universitet 2023-yil oktabr oyida talabalar"
" uchun o'z eshiklarini ochgan. Universitetda to'rtta yo'nalish faoliyat "
"yuritadi: Biznes, Pedagogika, AT va Xorijiy tillar. Ushbu sohalarda "
"bakalavriat va magistratura dasturlari taqdim etiladi."

msgid ""
"TIU is staffed by highly qualified professors and experienced teachers who "
"are experts in their fields. Their extensive teaching and research "
"experience sets a high standard for academic excellence. TIU places great "
"emphasis on research and innovation, supporting students' involvement in "
"research activities and collaboration with industry organizations."
msgstr ""
"TIUda o'z sohalarining mutaxassisi bo'lgan yuqori malakali professorlar va "
"tajribali pedagoglar faoliyat yuritadi. Ularning boy o'qituvchilik va ilmiy "
"tadqiqot tajribasi akademik mukammallikning yuqori darajasini belgilaydi. "
"TIU tadqiqot va innovatsiyaga alohida e'tibor qaratib, talabalarning ilmiy "
"faoliyatda ishtirokini va sanoat tashkilotlari bilan hamkorligini qo'llab-"
"quvvatlaydi."

msgid ""
"TIU establishes partnerships with prestigious universities and organizations"
" around the world, creating broad opportunities for students to study abroad"
" and gain international experience. In conclusion, we provide comprehensive "
"support to our students, contributing to their success in their chosen "
"profession and personal life."
msgstr ""
"TIU dunyo bo'ylab nufuzli universitetlar va tashkilotlar bilan hamkorlik "
"o'rnatib, talabalarga chet elda tahsil olish va xalqaro tajriba orttirish "
"uchun keng imkoniyatlar yaratadi. Xulosa qilib aytganda, biz talabalarimizga"
" har tomonlama yordam ko'rsatib, ularning tanlagan kasbi va shaxsiy hayotida"
" muvaffaqiyatga erishishlariga hissa qo'shamiz."

msgid ""
"Your TIU degree is officially recognized by the Ministry of Higher Education"
" of Uzbekistan and validated by our international partner universities. "
"Through our 2+2 dual degree partnerships, TIU programs align with the "
"academic requirements of partner institutions abroad. This means seamless "
"credit transfer — no extra exams, no lost credits. We continuously review "
"and improve our programs to stay aligned with global best practices in "
"higher education."
msgstr ""
"TIU diplomi O'zbekiston Oliy ta'lim vazirligi tomonidan rasman tan olingan "
"va xalqaro hamkor universitetlarimiz tomonidan tasdiqlangan. 2+2 qo'sha "
"diplom hamkorligi orqali TIU dasturlari chet eldagi hamkor muassasalarning "
"akademik talablariga to'liq mos keladi. Bu degani — kreditlar muammosiz "
"o'tkaziladi, qo'shimcha imtihonlar yoki yo'qotilgan kreditlar bo'lmaydi. Biz"
" dasturlarimizni oliy ta'limdagi ilg'or xalqaro amaliyotlarga mos ravishda "
"doimiy takomillashtirib boramiz."

msgid "Your future deserves a degree that opens doors"
msgstr "Kelajagingiz eshiklarni ochadigan diplomga loyiq"

msgid ""
"Great universities don't just prepare students for the world — they help "
"protect it."
msgstr ""
"Buyuk universitetlar talabalarni faqat dunyoga tayyorlamaydi — ular dunyoni "
"asrashga ham yordam beradi."

msgid "Fees and Scholarships"
msgstr "To'lovlar va grantlar"

msgid ""
"Students participating in the 2+2 program are not required to make any "
"payments to TIU after transferring to the partner university. Any "
"scholarships held at TIU prior to the transfer are considered void."
msgstr ""
"2+2 dasturida qatnashayotgan talabalar hamkor universitetga o'tgandan keyin "
"TIUga hech qanday to'lov amalga oshirishi shart emas. O'tkazilgunga qadar "
"TIUda mavjud bo'lgan grantlar bekor qilingan hisoblanadi."

msgid ""
"However, in some cases, agreements between TIU and the receiving university "
"may require students to continue paying TIU fees. Students are advised to "
"consult the International Relations Office regarding fee conditions and "
"scholarships before applying."
msgstr ""
"Biroq, ba'zi hollarda TIU va qabul qiluvchi universitet o'rtasidagi "
"kelishuvlarga ko'ra talabalardan TIU to'lovlarini to'lashni davom ettirish "
"talab qilinishi mumkin. Talabalarga ariza topshirishdan oldin to'lov "
"shartlari va grantlar bo'yicha Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi bilan "
"maslahatlashish tavsiya etiladi."

msgid "Contact the International Relations Office"
msgstr "Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limiga murojaat qilish"

msgid "Two degrees. One journey."
msgstr "Ikki diplom — bitta ta'lim yo'li."

msgid ""
"In this program, bachelor's students earn two academic degrees upon "
"completion. The first is from Tashkent International University, and the "
"second from one of our partner universities. Students complete two years at "
"TIU and another two years at the partner institution. Those wishing to study"
" in this program must follow a specialized curriculum that meets the course "
"and credit requirements of both TIU and the partner university. "
"Participating in a dual degree program gives students numerous advantages. "
"This unique educational path not only equips graduates with a diverse skill "
"set that makes them highly adaptable in the job market, but also provides a "
"competitive edge."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu dasturda bakalavriat talabalari o'qishni tugatgach ikkita akademik "
"darajaga ega bo'ladi. Birinchisi Toshkent xalqaro universitetidan, "
"ikkinchisi esa hamkor universitetlardan biridan beriladi. Talabalar ikki yil"
" TIUda, yana ikki yil hamkor muassasada tahsil oladi. Ushbu dasturda "
"o'qishni istagan talabalar TIU va hamkor universitetning fan va kredit "
"talablariga javob beradigan maxsus o'quv rejasiga amal qilishi kerak. Qo'sha"
" diplom dasturida ishtirok etish talabalarga ko'plab afzalliklar beradi. Bu "
"noyob ta'lim yo'li bitiruvchilarni mehnat bozorida moslashuvchan qiladigan "
"turli ko'nikmalar bilan qurollantiribgina qolmay, raqobatbardosh ustunlik "
"ham ta'minlaydi."

msgid "Discover the world while you study"
msgstr "O'qish davomida dunyoni kashf eting"

msgid ""
"During your exchange semester, you continue paying your regular TIU tuition."
" Partner university tuition fees are waived under our bilateral agreements. "
"However, students are responsible for their own travel, accommodation, and "
"living expenses abroad. Students are advised to consult with the "
"International Relations Department for detailed information about costs and "
"available financial support before applying."
msgstr ""
"Almashinuv semestri davomida siz TIUdagi oddiy kontrakt to'lovini to'lashda "
"davom etasiz. Hamkor universitetdagi o'qish to'lovi ikki tomonlama "
"kelishuvlarimiz asosida olib tashlanadi. Biroq, chet eldagi yo'l, turar joy "
"va kun tartibidagi xarajatlar talabaning o'z zimmasida qoladi. Talabalarga "
"ariza topshirishdan oldin xarajatlar va mavjud moliyaviy yordam haqida "
"batafsil ma'lumot olish uchun Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limiga murojaat qilish "
"tavsiya etiladi."

msgid ""
"Yes, admission to Bachelor's programmes is based on entrance exam results. "
"Exam subjects are determined according to your chosen programme. "
"Additionally, if you don't have an IELTS/TOEFL score, you can take TIU's "
"internal English test."
msgstr ""
"Ha, bakalavriat dasturlariga qabul kirish imtihoni natijalari asosida amalga"
" oshiriladi. Imtihon fanlari tanlagan yo'nalishingizga qarab belgilanadi. "
"Bundan tashqari, IELTS/TOEFL natijangiz bo'lmasa, TIUning ichki ingliz tili "
"testidan o'tishingiz mumkin."

msgid ""
"Tuition fees vary by programme, ranging from approximately 14,000,000 to "
"25,000,000 UZS per year. Scholarships of up to 100%% are available for high-"
"achieving students. Visit our"
msgstr ""
"Kontrakt to'lovi yo'nalishga qarab farqlanadi va yiliga 14 000 000 dan 25 "
"000 000 so'mgacha. Yuqori natijalarga erishgan talabalar uchun 100%%gacha "
"grant ajratiladi. Batafsil ma'lumot uchun"

msgid ""
"Yes, admission to Master's programmes is based on entrance exam results. "
"Exam subjects are determined according to your chosen programme. "
"Additionally, if you don't have an IELTS/TOEFL score, you can take TIU's "
"internal English test. Some programmes may include an interview as part of "
"the assessment process."
msgstr ""
"Ha, magistratura dasturlariga qabul kirish imtihoni natijalari asosida "
"amalga oshiriladi. Imtihon fanlari tanlagan yo'nalishingizga qarab "
"belgilanadi. Bundan tashqari, IELTS/TOEFL natijangiz bo'lmasa, TIUning ichki"
" ingliz tili testidan o'tishingiz mumkin. Ba'zi dasturlarda baholash "
"jarayonining bir qismi sifatida suhbat ham o'tkazilishi mumkin."

msgid ""
"Tuition fees vary by programme, up to 25,000,000 UZS per year. Scholarships "
"of up to 100%% are available for high-achieving students. Visit our"
msgstr ""
"Kontrakt to'lovi yo'nalishga qarab farqlanadi va yiliga 25 000 000 "
"so'mgacha. Yuqori natijalarga erishgan talabalar uchun 100%%gacha grant "
"ajratiladi. Batafsil ma'lumot uchun"

msgid ""
"Admission to TIU is based on entrance exam results, academic merit, and "
"readiness for an international learning environment. Requirements vary by "
"programme level, but we've made the process as clear and straightforward as "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"TIUga qabul kirish imtihoni natijalari, akademik yutuqlar va xalqaro ta'lim "
"muhitiga tayyorlik asosida amalga oshiriladi. Talablar dastur darajasiga "
"qarab farqlanadi, ammo biz jarayonni iloji boricha aniq va sodda qildik."

msgid ""
"Yes, admission to TIU is based on entrance exam results. Exam subjects are "
"determined according to your chosen programme. If you don't have an "
"IELTS/TOEFL score, you can also take TIU's internal English test. Some "
"programmes may include an interview as part of the assessment."
msgstr ""
"Ha, TIUga qabul kirish imtihoni natijalari asosida amalga oshiriladi. "
"Imtihon fanlari tanlagan yo'nalishingizga qarab belgilanadi. IELTS/TOEFL "
"natijangiz bo'lmasa, TIUning ichki ingliz tili testidan ham o'tishingiz "
"mumkin. Ba'zi dasturlarda baholashning bir qismi sifatida suhbat "
"o'tkazilishi mumkin."

msgid ""
"Deferral requests are considered on a case-by-case basis. If you've received"
" an offer but need to delay your start date, contact the Admissions Office "
"as soon as possible. Deferrals are generally granted for up to one academic "
"year, subject to programme availability."
msgstr ""
"Ko'chirish so'rovlari har bir holat uchun alohida ko'rib chiqiladi. Agar "
"taklifnoma olgan bo'lsangiz, lekin o'qishni boshlanish sanasini kechiktirish"
" kerak bo'lsa, imkon qadar tezroq Qabul bo'limiga murojaat qiling. "
"Ko'chirishlar odatda bir o'quv yiligacha, yo'nalishda o'rin mavjudligiga "
"qarab ruxsat etiladi."

msgid "Tuition & Grants"
msgstr "Kontrakt va grantlar"

msgid "Graduation & Career"
msgstr "Bitirish va karera"

msgid ""
"You can apply online through our admissions portal. Select your programme "
"(Bachelor's, Master's, or PhD), fill in the application form, and upload the"
" required documents. After document review, you will be invited to take the "
"entrance exam. Our admissions team will contact you within 5–10 business "
"days."
msgstr ""
"Onlayn qabul portalimiz orqali ariza topshirishingiz mumkin. "
"Yo'nalishingizni tanlang (bakalavriat, magistratura yoki PhD), ariza "
"shaklini to'ldiring va kerakli hujjatlarni yuklang. Hujjatlar ko'rib "
"chiqilgandan so'ng, sizni kirish imtihoniga taklif qilamiz. Qabul bo'limimiz"
" 5–10 ish kuni ichida siz bilan bog'lanadi."

msgid ""
"For Bachelor's programmes: a secondary school diploma (attestat) and "
"successful completion of the entrance exam. For Master's: a Bachelor's "
"degree and entrance exam. All applicants must demonstrate English "
"proficiency (IELTS 5.5+ for Bachelor's, IELTS 6.0+ for Master's) or pass "
"TIU's internal English test."
msgstr ""
"Bakalavriat uchun: o'rta ta'lim attestati va kirish imtihonidan "
"muvaffaqiyatli o'tish. Magistratura uchun: bakalavriat diplomi va kirish "
"imtihoni. Barcha abituriyentlar ingliz tili bilimini tasdiqlanishi kerak "
"(bakalavriat uchun IELTS 5.5+, magistratura uchun IELTS 6.0+) yoki TIUning "
"ichki ingliz tili testidan o'tish."

msgid ""
"You will need: a copy of your passport or national ID, your diploma/attestat"
" with transcript, an English language certificate (IELTS, TOEFL, or TIU "
"internal test result), a motivation letter, 2 passport-sized photos, and a "
"medical certificate for international students. Some Master's programmes "
"also require a CV and recommendation letters."
msgstr ""
"Sizga kerak bo'ladi: pasport yoki shaxsni tasdiqlovchi hujjat nusxasi, "
"diplom/attestat va transkript, ingliz tili sertifikati (IELTS, TOEFL yoki "
"TIU ichki test natijasi), motivatsion xat, 2 dona pasport formatidagi "
"fotosurat va xorijiy talabalar uchun tibbiy ma'lumotnoma. Ba'zi magistratura"
" yo'nalishlari uchun rezyume va tavsiya xatlari ham talab qilinadi."

msgid ""
"Yes. Admission to all programmes is based on entrance exam results. Exam "
"subjects are determined according to your chosen programme. If you don't "
"have an IELTS/TOEFL score, you can also take TIU's internal English "
"placement test."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Barcha yo'nalishlarga qabul kirish imtihoni natijalari asosida amalga "
"oshiriladi. Imtihon fanlari tanlagan yo'nalishingizga qarab belgilanadi. "
"IELTS/TOEFL natijangiz bo'lmasa, TIUning ichki ingliz tili testidan ham "
"o'tishingiz mumkin."

msgid ""
"The main application deadline for Fall 2026 intake is 15 July 2026 for "
"Bachelor's programmes and 1 August 2026 for Master's. International "
"applicants have an earlier deadline of 1 June 2026. We recommend applying "
"early as popular programmes may fill up."
msgstr ""
"2026-yil kuzgi qabul uchun asosiy muddat: bakalavriat — 2026-yil 15-iyul, "
"magistratura — 2026-yil 1-avgust. Xorijiy abituriyentlar uchun — 2026-yil "
"1-iyun. Mashhur yo'nalishlar tez to'lishi mumkinligi sababli erta ariza "
"topshirishni tavsiya etamiz."

msgid "Can I transfer from another university to TIU?"
msgstr "Boshqa universitetdan TIUga ko'chirsa bo'ladimi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. Transfer students are welcome. You will need to provide your current "
"transcript for credit evaluation. The number of transferable credits depends"
" on programme compatibility. Contact the Admissions Office at "
"admissions@tiu.uz for individual assessment."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Ko'chirma talabalar qabul qilinadi. Kreditlarni baholash uchun joriy "
"transkriptingizni taqdim etishingiz kerak. O'tkaziladigan kreditlar soni "
"yo'nalishlar mosligiga bog'liq. Individual baholash uchun Qabul bo'limiga "
"admissions@tiu.uz orqali murojaat qiling."

msgid ""
"There are no strict age limits. Bachelor's programmes are typically for "
"school leavers aged 17+, but mature students are welcome. Master's and PhD "
"programmes are open to applicants of all ages who meet the entry "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"Qat'iy yosh chegarasi yo'q. Bakalavriat dasturlari odatda 17 yoshdan maktab "
"bitiruvchilari uchun, ammo kattaroq yoshdagi talabalar ham qabul qilinadi. "
"Magistratura va PhD dasturlari qabul talablariga javob beradigan barcha "
"yoshdagi abituriyentlar uchun ochiq."

msgid "Can international students apply to TIU?"
msgstr "Xorijiy talabalar TIUga ariza topshira oladimi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. TIU welcomes international students from all countries. The application"
" process is the same, with an earlier deadline to allow time for visa "
"processing. Our International Relations Department provides full support "
"with visas, accommodation, and orientation."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU barcha mamlakatlardan xorijiy talabalarni qabul qiladi. Ariza "
"topshirish jarayoni bir xil, faqat viza rasmiyatlari uchun vaqt ajratish "
"maqsadida muddatlar ertaroq belgilangan. Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limimiz viza, "
"turar joy va moslashuv bo'yicha to'liq yordam ko'rsatadi."

msgid ""
"TIU offers Bachelor's (4 years), Master's (2 years), and PhD programmes "
"across five departments: Business & Economics, IT, Education, Foreign "
"Languages & Literature, and Jurisprudence. We also offer a 2+2 dual degree "
"programme with international partner universities."
msgstr ""
"TIU beshta yo'nalish bo'yicha bakalavriat (4 yil), magistratura (2 yil) va "
"PhD dasturlarini taklif qiladi: Biznes va iqtisodiyot, AT, Pedagogika, "
"Xorijiy tillar va adabiyot, Huquqshunoslik. Shuningdek, xalqaro hamkor "
"universitetlar bilan 2+2 qo'sha diplom dasturi mavjud."

msgid ""
"All programmes at TIU are taught entirely in English by international "
"faculty. You do not need to know Uzbek or Russian to study at TIU, though "
"learning the local language is encouraged."
msgstr ""
"TIUdagi barcha dasturlar xalqaro professor-o'qituvchilar tomonidan to'liq "
"ingliz tilida olib boriladi. TIUda o'qish uchun o'zbek yoki rus tilini "
"bilish shart emas, ammo mahalliy tilni o'rganish rag'batlantiriladi."

msgid "What is the academic calendar?"
msgstr "O'quv yili qanday tashkil etilgan?"

msgid ""
"The academic year consists of two semesters. The fall semester runs from "
"September to January, and the spring semester from February to May. The "
"summer period (June–August) includes final exams, graduation ceremonies, and"
" a break before the new academic year."
msgstr ""
"O'quv yili ikki semestrdan iborat. Kuzgi semestr sentyabrdan yanvargacha, "
"bahorgi semestr fevraldan maygacha davom etadi. Yozgi davr (iyun–avgust) "
"yakuniy imtihonlar, bitirish marosimlari va yangi o'quv yili oldidan "
"ta'tilni o'z ichiga oladi."

msgid "What grading system does TIU use?"
msgstr "TIU qanday baholash tizimidan foydalanadi?"

msgid ""
"TIU uses a GPA-based grading system on a 4.0 scale, alongside the "
"traditional 5-point scale used in Uzbekistan (5 = excellent, 4 = good, 3 = "
"satisfactory). Your transcript will show both formats for international "
"compatibility."
msgstr ""
"TIU 4.0 shkalali GPA baholash tizimini qo'llaydi, shuningdek O'zbekistonda "
"qo'llaniladigan an'anaviy 5 balli tizim ham (5 = a'lo, 4 = yaxshi, 3 = "
"qoniqarli) ishlatiladi. Transkriptingizda xalqaro moslik uchun ikkala format"
" ko'rsatiladi."

msgid "Can I change my programme after enrolling?"
msgstr "Ro'yxatdan o'tgandan keyin yo'nalishni almashtirsa bo'ladimi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. TIU is licensed by the Ministry of Higher Education of Uzbekistan. Our "
"degrees are recognized nationally and internationally. The 2+2 dual degree "
"programme additionally grants a diploma from the partner university abroad."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU O'zbekiston Oliy ta'lim vazirligi tomonidan litsenziyalangan. "
"Diplomlarimiz milliy va xalqaro miqyosda tan olinadi. 2+2 qo'sha diplom "
"dasturi qo'shimcha ravishda xorijdagi hamkor universitetdan diplom beradi."

msgid "How much is the tuition fee?"
msgstr "Kontrakt to'lovi qancha?"

msgid ""
"Tuition (kontrakt) starts from 25,000,000 UZS per year and varies by "
"programme and study format. Full details are available on our Tuition & Fees"
" page. There are no hidden fees — the published rate covers all standard "
"academic costs."
msgstr ""
"Kontrakt to'lovi yiliga 25 000 000 so'mdan boshlanadi va yo'nalish hamda "
"ta'lim shakliga qarab farqlanadi. Batafsil ma'lumot Kontrakt to'lovi "
"sahifamizda mavjud. Yashirin to'lovlar yo'q — e'lon qilingan narx barcha "
"standart o'quv xarajatlarini qamrab oladi."

msgid "Are there grants available?"
msgstr "Grantlar mavjudmi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. TIU offers grants covering up to 100% of tuition based on entrance exam"
" results and academic performance. Grants are awarded automatically during "
"the admissions process — no separate application is needed for most grants."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU kirish imtihoni natijalari va akademik ko'rsatkichlar asosida "
"kontrakt to'lovining 100% gacha qoplaydigan grantlar taqdim etadi. Grantlar "
"qabul jarayonida avtomatik ravishda ajratiladi — ko'pgina grantlar uchun "
"alohida ariza talab qilinmaydi."

msgid ""
"Yes. TIU offers flexible payment options. Tuition can be paid per academic "
"year or per semester. Contact the Finance Office for instalment plan details"
" and deadlines."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU moslashuvchan to'lov variantlarini taklif qiladi. Kontrakt to'lovini"
" o'quv yili yoki semestr bo'yicha to'lash mumkin. Bo'lib to'lash rejalari va"
" muddatlar haqida batafsil Moliya bo'limiga murojaat qiling."

msgid "How are grants renewed each year?"
msgstr "Grantlar har yili qanday yangilanadi?"

msgid ""
"Grants are renewed annually provided you maintain the required GPA "
"(typically 3.0+ on a 4.0 scale) and remain in good academic standing. "
"Renewal conditions are specified in your grant letter."
msgstr ""
"Grantlar har yili yangilanadi — buning uchun talab qilinadigan GPA "
"darajasini (odatda 4.0 shkalada 3.0+) saqlab, yaxshi akademik "
"ko'rsatkichlarni ko'rsatishingiz kerak. Yangilash shartlari grant xatingizda"
" belgilangan."

msgid "Are there any additional costs beyond tuition?"
msgstr "Kontrakt to'lovidan tashqari qo'shimcha xarajatlar bormi?"

msgid ""
"Tuition covers all standard academic costs. Students should budget "
"separately for accommodation, textbooks, personal expenses, and optional "
"activities. TIU provides access to digital learning resources and the campus"
" library at no extra charge."
msgstr ""
"Kontrakt to'lovi barcha standart o'quv xarajatlarini qamrab oladi. Talabalar"
" turar joy, darsliklar, shaxsiy xarajatlar va ixtiyoriy faoliyatlar uchun "
"alohida byudjet ajratishi kerak. TIU raqamli o'quv resurslari va kampus "
"kutubxonasidan foydalanishni qo'shimcha to'lovsiz ta'minlaydi."

msgid "What is the 2+2 dual degree programme?"
msgstr "2+2 qo'sha diplom dasturi nima?"

msgid ""
"The 2+2 programme allows Bachelor's students to study two years at TIU and "
"two years at a partner university abroad. Upon completion, you graduate with"
" two diplomas — one from TIU and one from the partner institution. Both are "
"fully recognized."
msgstr ""
"2+2 dasturi bakalavriat talabalariga ikki yil TIUda va ikki yil xorijdagi "
"hamkor universitetda tahsil olish imkonini beradi. Tugatgach siz ikkita "
"diplom olasiz — biri TIUdan, biri hamkor muassasadan. Ikkalasi ham to'liq "
"tan olinadi."

msgid "How does the student exchange programme work?"
msgstr "Talabalar almashinuvi dasturi qanday ishlaydi?"

msgid ""
"TIU students can spend one or two semesters at a partner university abroad. "
"Credits earned transfer directly back to your TIU degree. You continue "
"paying TIU tuition — partner university fees are waived under our bilateral "
"agreements."
msgstr ""
"TIU talabalari xorijdagi hamkor universitetda bir yoki ikki semestr "
"o'qishlari mumkin. To'plangan kreditlar bevosita TIU diplomingizga "
"o'tkaziladi. Siz TIU kontrakt to'lovini to'lashda davom etasiz — hamkor "
"universitetdagi to'lov ikki tomonlama kelishuvlar asosida olib tashlanadi."

msgid "Who pays for studying abroad?"
msgstr "Chet elda o'qish xarajatlarini kim to'laydi?"

msgid ""
"During exchange or 2+2 programmes, tuition at the partner university is "
"covered by our agreements. However, students are responsible for travel, "
"accommodation, and living expenses abroad. The International Relations "
"Department can advise on costs and available support."
msgstr ""
"Almashinuv yoki 2+2 dasturlari davomida hamkor universitetdagi kontrakt "
"to'lovi kelishuvlarimiz asosida qoplanadi. Biroq, chet eldagi yo'l, turar "
"joy va yashash xarajatlari talabaning o'z zimmasida. Xalqaro aloqalar "
"bo'limi xarajatlar va mavjud yordam haqida maslahat beradi."

msgid "Does TIU help with visas for studying abroad?"
msgstr "TIU chet elda o'qish uchun viza olishda yordam beradimi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. The International Relations Department provides full support — from "
"issuing invitation letters and preparing documents to advising on visa "
"applications and travel logistics."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi to'liq yordam ko'rsatadi — taklifnoma xatlari "
"berish va hujjatlar tayyorlashdan tortib viza arizalari va sayohat "
"logistikasi bo'yicha maslahat berishgacha."

msgid "Which partner universities does TIU work with?"
msgstr "TIU qaysi hamkor universitetlar bilan ishlaydi?"

msgid ""
"TIU partners with universities across Europe and Asia. The list of partner "
"institutions is available on our International Programs page. New "
"partnerships are regularly added — contact the International Relations "
"Department for the latest information."
msgstr ""
"TIU Yevropa va Osiyo bo'ylab universitetlar bilan hamkorlik qiladi. Hamkor "
"muassasalar ro'yxati Xalqaro dasturlar sahifamizda mavjud. Yangi "
"hamkorliklar muntazam ravishda qo'shilmoqda — so'nggi ma'lumotlar uchun "
"Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limiga murojaat qiling."

msgid ""
"TIU helps students find comfortable accommodation near campus — either in "
"university-recommended hostels or shared apartments. International students "
"are given priority. Contact the Student Services Office to arrange housing "
"before arrival."
msgstr ""
"TIU talabalarga kampus yaqinida qulay turar joy topishda yordam beradi — "
"universitet tavsiya etgan yotoqxona yoki sherikli kvartiralar. Xorijiy "
"talabalarga ustunlik beriladi. Kelishdan oldin turar joyni tashkil qilish "
"uchun Talabalar xizmati bo'limiga murojaat qiling."

msgid ""
"Yes! TIU has 50+ student clubs — from debate and photography to coding and "
"chess. All clubs are student-led and open to everyone. The Student Union "
"also organizes events, festivals, and social activities throughout the year."
msgstr ""
"Ha! TIUda 50 dan ortiq talabalar klubi bor — munozara va fotografiyadan "
"dasturlash va shaxmatgacha. Barcha klublar talabalar tomonidan boshqariladi "
"va hamma uchun ochiq. Talabalar ittifoqi yil davomida tadbirlar, festivallar"
" va ijtimoiy faoliyatlar tashkil qiladi."

msgid "What sports facilities are available?"
msgstr "Qanday sport inshootlari mavjud?"

msgid ""
"Our campus includes a modern gym, a multi-court sports hall, and outdoor "
"pitches. Students can join university teams, take part in inter-university "
"tournaments, or simply stay active between lectures."
msgstr ""
"Kampusimizda zamonaviy trenajyor zali, ko'p tarmoqli sport zali va ochiq "
"sport maydonchalar mavjud. Talabalar universitet jamoalariga qo'shilishlari,"
" universitetlararo musobaqalarda ishtirok etishlari yoki darslar orasida "
"faol bo'lishlari mumkin."

msgid "Is there medical support on campus?"
msgstr "Kampusda tibbiy yordam bormi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. TIU has a medical services point on campus providing first aid, basic "
"consultations, and referrals to local healthcare providers. All students "
"have access to campus medical support during working hours."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU kampusida birinchi yordam, asosiy konsultatsiyalar va mahalliy "
"tibbiyot muassasalariga yo'naltirish ko'rsatadigan tibbiy xizmat nuqtasi "
"mavjud. Barcha talabalar ish soatlari davomida kampus tibbiy yordamidan "
"foydalanishlari mumkin."

msgid "How do I get to campus?"
msgstr "Kampusga qanday yetib boraman?"

msgid ""
"TIU is located on Little Ring Road 7 in central Tashkent. The campus is "
"accessible by bus, metro, and taxi. The nearest metro station is a short "
"walk away, and multiple bus routes stop directly outside campus. Parking is "
"also available on site."
msgstr ""
"TIU Toshkent markazida, Kichik halqa yo'li 7-da joylashgan. Kampusga "
"avtobus, metro va taksi orqali yetib kelish mumkin. Eng yaqin metro bekati "
"bir necha daqiqalik yurish masofasida, bir nechta avtobus yo'nalishlari "
"to'g'ridan-to'g'ri kampus oldida to'xtaydi. Avtoturargoh ham mavjud."

msgid "Is there a cafeteria on campus?"
msgstr "Kampusda oshxona bormi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. The campus cafeteria serves affordable meals throughout the day, "
"including hot dishes, salads, snacks, and beverages. Vegetarian and dietary "
"options are available."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Kampus oshxonasi kun davomida issiq taomlar, salatlar, yengil taomlar va"
" ichimliklar kabi arzon narxlardagi ovqatlarni taqdim etadi. Vegetarian va "
"parhez ovqatlari ham mavjud."

msgid ""
"Yes. Our Career Center provides CV workshops, mock interviews, career fairs,"
" employer networking events, and one-to-one counselling. Career support is "
"available from your first year through graduation and beyond."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Karyera markazimiz rezyume yozish bo'yicha seminarlar, sinov suhbatlar, "
"karera yarmarkalari, ish beruvchilar bilan tarmoq tadbirlari va individual "
"maslahatlar taqdim etadi. Karera yordami birinchi kursdan boshlab bitirish "
"va undan keyinga qadar mavjud."

msgid ""
"Yes. TIU partners with companies and organisations in Uzbekistan and "
"internationally to provide internship placements. Many programmes include a "
"mandatory internship component, ensuring you graduate with real-world "
"experience."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU O'zbekiston va xorijdagi kompaniyalar va tashkilotlar bilan "
"hamkorlikda amaliyot o'rinlarini taqdim etadi. Ko'pgina dasturlarda majburiy"
" amaliyot komponenti mavjud bo'lib, bu sizning haqiqiy tajriba bilan "
"bitirganingizni ta'minlaydi."

msgid "Is there an alumni network?"
msgstr "Bitiruvchilar tarmog'i bormi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. TIU graduates join a growing alumni network that provides career "
"support, networking opportunities, and access to exclusive events. As TIU "
"grows, so does the community of graduates making an impact across "
"industries."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU bitiruvchilari karera yordami, tarmoq imkoniyatlari va maxsus "
"tadbirlarga kirish huquqini beradigan tobora o'sib borayotgan bitiruvchilar "
"tarmog'iga qo'shiladi. TIU o'sgan sari, turli sohalarda o'z izini "
"qoldirayotgan bitiruvchilar jamoasi ham kengayadi."

msgid "Will my TIU degree be recognized by employers?"
msgstr "TIU diplomini ish beruvchilar tan oladimi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. TIU is licensed by the Ministry of Higher Education of Uzbekistan, and "
"our degrees are fully recognized nationally and internationally. The 2+2 "
"programme additionally provides a diploma from a partner university abroad, "
"further strengthening your credentials."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU O'zbekiston Oliy ta'lim vazirligi tomonidan litsenziyalangan va "
"diplomlarimiz milliy hamda xalqaro miqyosda to'liq tan olinadi. 2+2 dasturi "
"qo'shimcha ravishda xorijdagi hamkor universitetdan diplom beradi, bu "
"sizning malakangizni yanada mustahkamlaydi."

msgid "Do I need to submit a report after my internship?"
msgstr "Amaliyotdan keyin hisobot topshirish kerakmi?"

msgid ""
"Everything you need to know about getting your student visa, arriving in "
"Uzbekistan, and staying legally registered during your studies."
msgstr ""
"O'quv vizasini olish, O'zbekistonga kelish va o'qish davomida qonuniy "
"ro'yxatda turish haqida bilishingiz kerak bo'lgan hamma narsa."

msgid "We handle the paperwork — you focus on your future"
msgstr ""
"Hujjatlar bilan biz shug'ullanamiz — siz kelajagingizga e'tibor qarating"

msgid ""
"Getting a student visa to Uzbekistan is straightforward, and TIU's "
"International Relations Department guides you through every step. From your "
"Letter of Invitation to local registration after arrival — we make sure the "
"process is smooth and stress-free."
msgstr ""
"O'zbekistonga o'quv vizasini olish oddiy jarayon. TIUning Xalqaro aloqalar "
"bo'limi sizga har bir bosqichda yo'l ko'rsatadi. Taklif xatidan tortib "
"kelgandan keyingi ro'yxatdan o'tishgacha — jarayon silliq va tashvishsiz "
"bo'lishini ta'minlaymiz."

msgid "How to get your student visa"
msgstr "O'quv vizasini qanday olish mumkin"

msgid "A simple process from admission to arrival"
msgstr "Qabul qilinishdan kelishgacha — oddiy jarayon"

msgid "Get admitted"
msgstr "Qabul qilining"

msgid ""
"Apply to TIU, pass the entrance exams, and receive your official admission "
"letter."
msgstr ""
"TIUga ariza topshiring, kirish imtihonidan o'ting va rasmiy qabul xatini "
"oling."

msgid "Receive your Letter of Invitation"
msgstr "Taklif xatini oling"

msgid ""
"After you accept your offer and pay the tuition deposit, TIU issues your "
"official Letter of Invitation (LOI) for the visa application."
msgstr ""
"Taklifni qabul qilib, boshlang'ich to'lovni amalga oshirganingizdan so'ng "
"TIU viza arizasi uchun rasmiy taklif xatini (LOI) beradi."

msgid "Apply for your visa"
msgstr "Vizaga ariza topshiring"

msgid ""
"Submit your visa application at the nearest Uzbekistan embassy or consulate "
"with the LOI, passport, photos, medical certificate, and visa fee."
msgstr ""
"Yaqin atrofdagi O'zbekiston elchixonasi yoki konsulligiga taklif xati, "
"pasport, fotosuratlar, tibbiy ma'lumotnoma va viza to'lovi bilan viza "
"arizasini topshiring."

msgid "Travel to Tashkent"
msgstr "Toshkentga keling"

msgid ""
"Once your visa is approved, book your travel. TIU can arrange airport pickup"
" and help you settle into your accommodation."
msgstr ""
"Viza tasdiqlangach, sayohatingizni rejalashtiring. TIU aeroportdan kutib "
"olish va turar joyga joylashishda yordam beradi."

msgid "Register on arrival"
msgstr "Kelgach ro'yxatdan o'ting"

msgid ""
"Within the required period after arrival, TIU helps you complete local "
"migration registration. Your student visa is renewed annually through the "
"university."
msgstr ""
"Kelganingizdan keyin belgilangan muddat ichida TIU mahalliy migratsiya "
"ro'yxatidan o'tishda yordam beradi. O'quv vizangiz har yili universitet "
"orqali yangilanadi."

msgid "Visa Documents"
msgstr "Viza hujjatlari"

msgid "What you need for your visa application"
msgstr "Viza arizasi uchun kerak bo'ladigan hujjatlar"

msgid ""
"After receiving your Letter of Invitation from TIU, submit the following to "
"the Uzbekistan embassy or consulate in your country."
msgstr ""
"TIUdan taklif xatini olganingizdan so'ng, mamlakatingizdagi O'zbekiston "
"elchixonasi yoki konsulligiga quyidagilarni topshiring."

msgid "Letter of Invitation from TIU"
msgstr "TIUdan taklif xati"

msgid ""
"Official document issued by TIU after admission confirmation and tuition "
"deposit"
msgstr ""
"Qabul tasdiqlangach va boshlang'ich to'lov amalga oshirilgach TIU tomonidan "
"beriladigan rasmiy hujjat"

msgid "With at least 12 months validity beyond your intended arrival date"
msgstr "Kelish sanangizdan kamida 12 oy amal qilish muddati bo'lishi kerak"

msgid "4 recent photos (3.5 x 4.5 cm) on white background"
msgstr "Oq fonda 4 dona yangi fotosurat (3,5 x 4,5 sm)"

msgid ""
"Including HIV test and TB screening — required by Uzbekistan immigration "
"authorities"
msgstr ""
"OIV testi va sil kasalligi tekshiruvi bilan — O'zbekiston migratsiya "
"organlari tomonidan talab qilinadi"

msgid "Completed visa application form"
msgstr "To'ldirilgan viza ariza shakli"

msgid "Available at the Uzbekistan embassy or consulate in your country"
msgstr "Mamlakatingizdagi O'zbekiston elchixonasi yoki konsulligida mavjud"

msgid "Visa fee payment"
msgstr "Viza to'lovi"

msgid "Amount varies by country — check with your local Uzbekistan embassy"
msgstr ""
"Miqdori mamlakatga qarab farqlanadi — yaqin atrofdagi O'zbekiston "
"elchixonasidan tekshiring"

msgid "CIS Citizens"
msgstr "MDH fuqarolari"

msgid "Visa-free entry for many CIS countries"
msgstr "Ko'pgina MDH davlatlari fuqarolari uchun vizasiz kirish"

msgid ""
"Citizens of several CIS countries can enter Uzbekistan without a visa. You "
"may still need to complete migration registration after arrival. Contact us "
"to check if your country qualifies."
msgstr ""
"Bir qancha MDH davlatlari fuqarolari O'zbekistonga vizasiz kirishlari "
"mumkin. Kelgandan keyin migratsiya ro'yxatidan o'tish talab qilinishi "
"mumkin. Mamlakatingiz shartlarga mos kelishini tekshirish uchun biz bilan "
"bog'laning."

msgid "Check your eligibility"
msgstr "Muvofiqligingizni tekshiring"

msgid "Processing Time"
msgstr "Ko'rib chiqish muddati"

msgid "Visa in 5–10 working days"
msgstr "Viza 5–10 ish kunida"

msgid ""
"After submitting your documents, the student visa is typically processed "
"within 5–10 working days. We recommend starting the process at least 4–6 "
"weeks before the semester begins."
msgstr ""
"Hujjatlarni topshirgandan so'ng o'quv vizasi odatda 5–10 ish kuni ichida "
"rasmiylashtiriladi. Jarayonni semestr boshlanishidan kamida 4–6 hafta oldin "
"boshlashni tavsiya etamiz."

msgid "Annual Renewal"
msgstr "Har yilgi yangilanish"

msgid "We renew your visa every year"
msgstr "Vizangizni har yili yangilaymiz"

msgid ""
"Your student visa is renewed annually through TIU. The International "
"Relations Department handles the paperwork — you just need to provide "
"updated documents."
msgstr ""
"O'quv vizangiz har yili TIU orqali yangilanadi. Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi "
"hujjatlarni rasmiylashtirib beradi — sizdan faqat yangilangan hujjatlar "
"talab qilinadi."

msgid "Contact support"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlash xizmatiga murojaat"

msgid "After You Arrive"
msgstr "Kelganingizdan keyin"

msgid "What happens when you land in Tashkent"
msgstr "Toshkentga kelganingizda nima bo'ladi"

msgid ""
"TIU arranges airport pickup for international students. Within the first "
"days, we help you with migration registration, SIM card setup, bank account "
"opening, and campus orientation. Our International Relations Department is "
"your point of contact for any questions or concerns during your entire stay."
msgstr ""
"TIU xorijiy talabalar uchun aeroportdan kutib olishni tashkil qiladi. "
"Dastlabki kunlarda migratsiya ro'yxati, SIM-karta olish, bank hisobi ochish "
"va kampus bo'yicha tanishuv bilan yordam beramiz. Xalqaro aloqalar "
"bo'limimiz butun yashash davringizda har qanday savol va muammolar uchun "
"aloqa nuqtangiz."

msgid "Accommodation & settling in"
msgstr "Turar joy va joylashish"

msgid "Visa & Immigration FAQs"
msgstr "Viza va migratsiya bo'yicha savollar"

msgid ""
"Most international students need a student visa to study in Uzbekistan. "
"Citizens of some CIS countries may enter visa-free but still need migration "
"registration. TIU's International Relations Department will advise you based"
" on your nationality."
msgstr ""
"Ko'pchilik xorijiy talabalar O'zbekistonda o'qish uchun o'quv vizasiga "
"muhtoj. Ba'zi MDH davlatlari fuqarolari vizasiz kirishlari mumkin, ammo "
"migratsiya ro'yxatidan o'tishlari kerak. TIUning Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi "
"fuqaroligingiz asosida maslahat beradi."

msgid "How long does visa processing take?"
msgstr "Viza rasmiyatlari qancha vaqt oladi?"

msgid ""
"Typically 5–10 working days after submitting all documents to the Uzbekistan"
" embassy. Processing times may vary by country. Start the process at least "
"4–6 weeks before the semester."
msgstr ""
"Odatda barcha hujjatlarni O'zbekiston elchixonasiga topshirgandan so'ng 5–10"
" ish kuni. Ko'rib chiqish muddati mamlakatga qarab farqlanishi mumkin. "
"Jarayonni semestrdan kamida 4–6 hafta oldin boshlang."

msgid "What is the Letter of Invitation?"
msgstr "Taklif xati nima?"

msgid ""
"The Letter of Invitation (LOI) is an official document issued by TIU that "
"you need to apply for a student visa. It confirms your admission and "
"enrollment at the university. TIU sends it to you after you accept your "
"offer and pay the tuition deposit."
msgstr ""
"Taklif xati (LOI) — bu o'quv vizasiga ariza topshirish uchun zarur bo'lgan "
"TIU tomonidan beriladigan rasmiy hujjat. U sizning universitetga qabul "
"qilinganingiz va ro'yxatdan o'tganingizni tasdiqlaydi. TIU uni taklifni "
"qabul qilib, boshlang'ich to'lovni amalga oshirganingizdan keyin yuboradi."

msgid "Do I need medical insurance?"
msgstr "Tibbiy sug'urta kerakmi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. Medical insurance is required for all international students studying "
"in Uzbekistan. You can arrange insurance in your home country or upon "
"arrival in Tashkent. TIU can recommend local insurance providers."
msgstr ""
"Ha. O'zbekistonda o'qiyotgan barcha xorijiy talabalar uchun tibbiy sug'urta "
"talab qilinadi. Sug'urtani o'z mamlakatingizda yoki Toshkentga kelganingizda"
" rasmiylashtirish mumkin. TIU mahalliy sug'urta kompaniyalarini tavsiya "
"qilishi mumkin."

msgid "What is migration registration?"
msgstr "Migratsiya ro'yxati nima?"

msgid ""
"All foreign nationals in Uzbekistan must register with local migration "
"authorities within a set period after arrival. TIU handles this process for "
"you — just provide your passport and visa, and we take care of the rest."
msgstr ""
"O'zbekistondagi barcha xorijiy fuqarolar kelganidan keyin belgilangan muddat"
" ichida mahalliy migratsiya organlarida ro'yxatdan o'tishlari shart. TIU bu "
"jarayonni siz uchun amalga oshiradi — pasport va vizangizni bering, "
"qolganini biz hal qilamiz."

msgid "Can I travel outside Uzbekistan during my studies?"
msgstr "O'qish davomida O'zbekistondan tashqariga chiqsam bo'ladimi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. You can travel during academic breaks. Make sure your student visa and "
"registration remain valid. If you plan to leave and re-enter Uzbekistan, "
"check with the International Relations Department about re-entry "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Ta'til kunlarida sayohat qilishingiz mumkin. O'quv vizangiz va "
"ro'yxatingiz amal qilishiga ishonch hosil qiling. O'zbekistondan chiqib "
"qayta kirishni rejalashtirganingizda, qayta kirish talablari haqida Xalqaro "
"aloqalar bo'limidan ma'lumot oling."

msgid ""
"Get in touch with Tashkent International University. We're here to help with"
" admissions, academics, student life, and more."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent xalqaro universiteti bilan bog'laning. Qabul, o'qish, talabalar "
"hayoti va boshqa masalalarda yordam berishga tayyormiz."

msgid "LOCATION"
msgstr "JOYLASHUV"

msgid "Easy to reach,"
msgstr "Oson yetib kelish mumkin,"

msgid "wherever you are"
msgstr "qayerda bo'lsangiz ham"

msgid ""
"Located in the heart of Tashkent, TIU is easy to reach from anywhere in the "
"country. Excellent road, rail, and air connections — including Tashkent "
"International Airport just 20 minutes away — make getting here simple. "
"Exploring everything we offer? That's the exciting part."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent markazida joylashgan TIUga mamlakatning istalgan burchagidan oson "
"yetib kelish mumkin. Ajoyib avtomobil, temir yo'l va havo aloqalari — "
"jumladan, atigi 20 daqiqalik masofadagi Toshkent xalqaro aeroporti — "
"kelishni osonlashtiradi. Taklif etayotganlarimizni o'rganish esa — eng "
"qiziqarli qism."

msgid "By car"
msgstr "Avtomobilda"

msgid "By bus"
msgstr "Avtobusda"

msgid "By metro"
msgstr "Metroda"

msgid "By taxi"
msgstr "Taksida"

msgid "By plane"
msgstr "Samolyotda"

msgid "By train"
msgstr "Poyezda"

msgid "Main Entrance"
msgstr "Asosiy kirish"

msgid "Little Ring Road 7, Tashkent"
msgstr "Toshkent, Kichik halqa yo'li 7"

msgid "Free parking on campus"
msgstr "Kampusda bepul avtoturargoh"

msgid "Visitor Parking"
msgstr "Mehmonlar avtoturargohi"

msgid "Near the main administration building"
msgstr "Bosh ma'muriy bino yaqinida"

msgid "Nearest Bus Stop"
msgstr "Eng yaqin avtobus bekati"

msgid "Multiple routes stop within 5 minutes' walk"
msgstr "Bir nechta yo'nalish 5 daqiqalik yurish masofasida to'xtaydi"

msgid "Routes Available"
msgstr "Mavjud yo'nalishlar"

msgid "Regular services from all districts of Tashkent"
msgstr "Toshkentning barcha tumanlaridan muntazam qatnovlar"

msgid "Nearest Metro Station"
msgstr "Eng yaqin metro bekati"

msgid "Tashkent Metro — fastest way across the city"
msgstr "Toshkent metrosi — shahar bo'ylab eng tez yo'l"

msgid "Walking Distance"
msgstr "Piyoda masofa"

msgid "10 minutes from station to campus"
msgstr "Bekatdan kampusgacha 10 daqiqa"

msgid "Taxi Drop-off"
msgstr "Taksi to'xtash joyi"

msgid "Main gate — use Yandex Go or MyTaxi"
msgstr "Asosiy darvoza — Yandex Go yoki MyTaxi ishlating"

msgid "From City Center"
msgstr "Shahar markazidan"

msgid "15–20 minutes depending on traffic"
msgstr "Tirbandlikka qarab 15–20 daqiqa"

msgid "Tashkent International Airport"
msgstr "Toshkent xalqaro aeroporti"

msgid "Islam Karimov Airport (TAS) — 20 min from campus"
msgstr "Islom Karimov aeroporti (TAS) — kampusdan 20 daqiqa"

msgid "Airport Transfer"
msgstr "Aeroportdan transport"

msgid "Taxi, bus, and Aeroexpress available"
msgstr "Taksi, avtobus va Aeroexpress mavjud"

msgid "Tashkent Railway Station"
msgstr "Toshkent temir yo'l vokzali"

msgid "Afrosiyob high-speed trains from Samarkand, Bukhara"
msgstr "Samarqand, Buxorodan Afrosiyob tezkor poyezdlari"

msgid "From the Station"
msgstr "Vokzaldan"

msgid "15 minutes by taxi or metro"
msgstr "Taksi yoki metroda 15 daqiqa"

msgid ""
"Everything on one compact campus — it takes just 10 minutes to walk from one"
" end to the other. Download the map and find your way around."
msgstr ""
"Hamma narsa bitta ixcham kampusda — bir uchidan ikkinchi uchigacha atigi 10 "
"daqiqada yetib borish mumkin. Xaritani yuklab, yo'lingizni toping."

msgid "Download Campus Map"
msgstr "Kampus xaritasini yuklab olish"

msgid "Travel FAQs"
msgstr "Yo'l-yo'riq bo'yicha savollar"

msgid "How far is TIU from the airport?"
msgstr "TIU aeroportdan qanchalik uzoq?"

msgid ""
"About 20 minutes by car or taxi from Islam Karimov International Airport "
"(TAS). Use Yandex Go or MyTaxi for a direct ride to campus."
msgstr ""
"Islom Karimov xalqaro aeroportidan (TAS) avtomobil yoki taksida taxminan 20 "
"daqiqa. Kampusga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri yetib borish uchun Yandex Go yoki MyTaxi"
" ishlatishingiz mumkin."

msgid "Is there parking on campus?"
msgstr "Kampusda avtoturargoh bormi?"

msgid "Yes. Free parking for students and visitors near the main building."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Bosh bino yaqinida talabalar va mehmonlar uchun bepul avtoturargoh."

msgid "Can I get here by public transport?"
msgstr "Jamoat transportida yetib borsa bo'ladimi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. Multiple bus routes stop near campus, and the nearest metro station is "
"a 10-minute walk."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Kampus yaqinida bir nechta avtobus yo'nalishlari to'xtaydi, eng yaqin "
"metro bekati 10 daqiqalik yurish masofasida."

msgid "How to get here from other cities?"
msgstr "Boshqa shaharlardan qanday kelish mumkin?"

msgid ""
"Afrosiyob high-speed trains run from Samarkand (~2 hours) and Bukhara (~4 "
"hours). From Tashkent station, campus is 15 minutes by taxi."
msgstr ""
"Samarqanddan (~2 soat) va Buxorodan (~4 soat) Afrosiyob tezkor poyezdlari "
"qatnaydi. Toshkent vokzalidan kampusgacha taksida 15 daqiqa."

msgid "Which taxi apps work in Tashkent?"
msgstr "Toshkentda qaysi taksi ilovalari ishlaydi?"

msgid ""
"Yandex Go and MyTaxi. Both are affordable, reliable, and accept card "
"payments."
msgstr ""
"Yandex Go va MyTaxi. Ikkalasi ham arzon, ishonchli va karta orqali to'lashni"
" qabul qiladi."

msgid "Rector's Reception"
msgstr "Rektor qabulxonasi"

msgid "Send a Message"
msgstr "Xabar yuborish"

msgid ""
