"va brendingi himoyalangan tovar belgilaridir."

msgid "4. Online Applications & Student Portal"
msgstr "4. Onlayn arizalar va talabalar portali"

msgid ""
"Users submitting applications must provide accurate and truthful "
"information. Providing false information may result in rejection or "
"cancellation of enrollment. You are responsible for maintaining the "
"confidentiality of your login credentials. TIU is not responsible for "
"unauthorized access resulting from your failure to protect your credentials."
" Application submission does not guarantee admission."
msgstr ""
"Ariza topshiruvchilar aniq va to'g'ri ma'lumot berishlari shart. Yolg'on "
"ma'lumot berish arizaning rad etilishi yoki o'qishdan chetlashtirish bilan "
"yakunlanishi mumkin. Login ma'lumotlaringizning maxfiyligini saqlash sizning"
" javobgarligingizda. TIU sizning ma'lumotlaringizni himoya qila "
"olmaganligingiz natijasida yuzaga kelgan ruxsatsiz kirish uchun javobgar "
"emas. Ariza topshirish qabul qilinish kafolatini bermaydi."

msgid "5. Personal Data & Privacy"
msgstr "5. Shaxsiy ma'lumotlar va maxfiylik"

msgid ""
"TIU collects personal data through the website (application forms, contact "
"forms, analytics) in accordance with the Law on Personal Data of the "
"Republic of Uzbekistan. Data is used for processing applications, "
"communication, and improving the website. TIU does not sell personal data to"
" third parties. Data may be shared with partner universities (with consent),"
" government authorities (when required by law), and service providers (under"
" data processing agreements). Users have the right to access, correct, and "
"request deletion of their personal data."
msgstr ""
"TIU O'zbekiston Respublikasining Shaxsiy ma'lumotlar to'g'risidagi qonuniga "
"muvofiq veb-sayt orqali shaxsiy ma'lumotlarni (ariza shakllari, aloqa "
"shakllari, tahlillar) to'playdi. Ma'lumotlar arizalarni ko'rib chiqish, "
"muloqot va veb-saytni yaxshilash uchun ishlatiladi. TIU shaxsiy "
"ma'lumotlarni uchinchi tomonlarga sotmaydi. Ma'lumotlar hamkor "
"universitetlarga (rozilik bilan), davlat organlariga (qonun talab qilganda) "
"va xizmat ko'rsatuvchilarga (ma'lumotlarni qayta ishlash shartnomalari "
"asosida) uzatilishi mumkin. Foydalanuvchilar o'z shaxsiy ma'lumotlariga "
"kirish, tuzatish va o'chirilishini so'rash huquqiga ega."

msgid "6. Cookies & Analytics"
msgstr "6. Cookie fayllari va tahlillar"

msgid ""
"The website uses cookies to improve user experience: essential cookies for "
"functionality, analytical cookies for usage statistics, and preference "
"cookies for user settings. You can manage cookies through your browser "
"settings. TIU may use third-party analytics tools to understand website "
"traffic. Analytics data is collected anonymously."
msgstr ""
"Veb-sayt foydalanuvchi tajribasini yaxshilash uchun cookie fayllaridan "
"foydalanadi: funksionallik uchun zaruriy cookie'lar, foydalanish "
"statistikasi uchun tahliliy cookie'lar va foydalanuvchi sozlamalari uchun "
"afzallik cookie'lari. Cookie fayllarini brauzer sozlamalari orqali "
"boshqarishingiz mumkin. TIU veb-sayt trafigini tushunish uchun uchinchi "
"tomon tahlil vositalaridan foydalanishi mumkin. Tahlil ma'lumotlari anonim "
"tarzda to'planadi."

msgid "7. Accuracy of Information"
msgstr "7. Ma'lumotlarning aniqligi"

msgid ""
"TIU makes reasonable efforts to ensure accuracy of information on the "
"website. However, we do not guarantee that all content is complete, current,"
" or error-free. Programme details, tuition fees, admission requirements, and"
" deadlines are subject to change. For the most current information, contact "
"the relevant university department directly. Official information is "
"confirmed only through direct communication with TIU administration."
msgstr ""
"TIU veb-saytdagi ma'lumotlar aniqligini ta'minlash uchun barcha choralarni "
"ko'radi. Biroq, barcha kontent to'liq, dolzarb yoki xatosiz ekanligiga "
"kafolat bermaymiz. Dastur tafsilotlari, kontrakt to'lovlari, qabul talablari"
" va muddatlar o'zgarishi mumkin. Eng so'nggi ma'lumotlar uchun tegishli "
"bo'limga bevosita murojaat qiling. Rasmiy ma'lumotlar faqat TIU ma'muriyati "
"bilan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri muloqot orqali tasdiqlanadi."

msgid "8. Third-Party Links"
msgstr "8. Uchinchi tomon havolalari"

msgid ""
"This website may contain links to external websites. TIU does not endorse, "
"control, or accept responsibility for the content or privacy practices of "
"third-party sites. Accessing external links is at your own risk."
msgstr ""
"Veb-saytda tashqi veb-saytlarga havolalar bo'lishi mumkin. TIU uchinchi "
"tomon saytlarining kontenti yoki maxfiylik amaliyotlari uchun javobgarlik "
"qabul qilmaydi. Tashqi havolalarga o'tish sizning o'z javobgarligingizda."

msgid "9. Limitation of Liability"
msgstr "9. Javobgarlikni cheklash"

msgid ""
"To the maximum extent permitted by the laws of the Republic of Uzbekistan, "
"TIU shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or "
"consequential damages arising from use of the website. The website and its "
"content are provided 'as is' without warranties of any kind. TIU is not "
"liable for temporary unavailability due to maintenance or technical issues, "
"errors or omissions in content, or actions taken based on website "
"information without official confirmation."
msgstr ""
"O'zbekiston Respublikasi qonunlari ruxsat bergan eng yuqori darajada TIU "
"veb-saytdan foydalanish natijasida yuzaga kelgan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri, "
"bilvosita, tasodifiy yoki oqibatli zarar uchun javobgar emas. Veb-sayt va "
"uning kontenti hech qanday kafolatsiz, 'bor bo'lgan holda' taqdim etiladi. "
"TIU texnik xizmat ko'rsatish yoki texnik muammolar tufayli vaqtinchalik "
"ishlamaslik, kontentdagi xatolar yoki rasmiy tasdiqsiz veb-sayt ma'lumotlari"
" asosida qilingan harakatlar uchun javobgar emas."

msgid "10. Governing Law & Disputes"
msgstr "10. Amaldagi qonunchilik va nizolar"

msgid ""
"These Terms of Use are governed by the laws of the Republic of Uzbekistan. "
"Any disputes shall be resolved through negotiation first. If negotiation "
"fails, disputes shall be submitted to the competent courts of the Republic "
"of Uzbekistan located in Tashkent."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu Foydalanish shartlari O'zbekiston Respublikasi qonunlari asosida "
"boshqariladi va talqin etiladi. Har qanday nizolar avvalo muzokaralar yo'li "
"bilan hal etiladi. Muzokaralar natija bermasa, nizolar Toshkent shahridagi "
"O'zbekiston Respublikasi vakolatli sudlariga havola etiladi."

msgid "11. Severability"
msgstr "11. Ajralish qoidasi"

msgid ""
"If any provision of these terms is found to be invalid or unenforceable, the"
" remaining provisions shall continue in full force and effect."
msgstr ""
"Agar ushbu shartlarning biron-bir qoidasi haqiqiy emas yoki ijro etib "
"bo'lmaydigan deb topilsa, qolgan qoidalar to'liq kuchda qoladi."

msgid "If you have questions about these Terms of Use, please contact:"
msgstr ""
"Ushbu Foydalanish shartlari bo'yicha savollaringiz bo'lsa, murojaat qiling:"

msgid "Website"
msgstr "Veb-sayt"

msgid ""
"How Tashkent International University collects, uses, and protects your "
"personal information."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent xalqaro universiteti shaxsiy ma'lumotlaringizni qanday to'playdi, "
"ishlatadi va himoya qiladi."

msgid ""
"Tashkent International University (TIU) is committed to protecting your "
"privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what personal data we collect, how we "
"use it, and your rights. Data processing is carried out in accordance with "
"the Law on Personal Data of the Republic of Uzbekistan."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent xalqaro universiteti (TIU) maxfiyligingizni himoya qilishga sodiq. "
"Ushbu Maxfiylik siyosati qanday shaxsiy ma'lumotlar to'planishi, ular qanday"
" ishlatilishi va sizning huquqlaringizni tushuntiradi. Ma'lumotlarni qayta "
"ishlash O'zbekiston Respublikasining Shaxsiy ma'lumotlar to'g'risidagi "
"qonuniga muvofiq amalga oshiriladi."

msgid "1. Data Controller"
msgstr "1. Ma'lumotlarni boshqaruvchi"

msgid ""
"The data controller is Tashkent International University, located at Little "
"Ring Road 7, Tashkent, Uzbekistan. For data protection inquiries, contact: "
"privacy@tiu.uz."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlarni boshqaruvchi — Toshkent xalqaro universiteti, manzil: "
"Toshkent, Kichik halqa yo'li 7. Shaxsiy ma'lumotlar himoyasi bo'yicha "
"savollar uchun: privacy@tiu.uz."

msgid "2. What Data We Collect"
msgstr "2. Qanday ma'lumotlar to'playmiz"

msgid "We collect the following types of personal data:"
msgstr "Biz quyidagi turdagi shaxsiy ma'lumotlarni to'playmiz:"

msgid "Identity data:"
msgstr "Shaxsni aniqlash ma'lumotlari:"

msgid "name, date of birth, nationality, passport/ID number, photographs"
msgstr "ism, tug'ilgan sana, fuqaroligi, pasport/ID raqami, fotosuratlar"

msgid "Contact data:"
msgstr "Aloqa ma'lumotlari:"

msgid "email, phone number, address"
msgstr "elektron pochta, telefon raqami, manzil"

msgid "Academic data:"
msgstr "Akademik ma'lumotlar:"

msgid ""
"transcripts, grades, diplomas, English test scores, motivation letter, CV"
msgstr ""
"transkriptlar, baholar, diplomlar, ingliz tili test natijalari, motivatsion "
"xat, rezyume"

msgid "Technical data:"
msgstr "Texnik ma'lumotlar:"

msgid "IP address, browser type, device, pages visited, cookies"
msgstr ""
"IP manzil, brauzer turi, qurilma, ko'rilgan sahifalar, cookie fayllari"

msgid "Financial data:"
msgstr "Moliyaviy ma'lumotlar:"

msgid "tuition payment records, grant information"
msgstr "kontrakt to'lovlari yozuvlari, grant ma'lumotlari"

msgid "3. How We Use Your Data"
msgstr "3. Ma'lumotlaringizni qanday ishlatamiz"

msgid "Processing admission applications and managing enrollment"
msgstr "Qabul arizalarini ko'rib chiqish va ro'yxatdan o'tishni boshqarish"

msgid "Delivering educational programs and assessing academic performance"
msgstr "Ta'lim dasturlarini amalga oshirish va akademik natijalarni baholash"

msgid "Communicating university updates, events, and announcements"
msgstr "Universitet yangiliklari, tadbirlari va e'lonlari haqida xabar berish"

msgid "Processing tuition payments and grant allocation"
msgstr "Kontrakt to'lovlarini qayta ishlash va grantlarni taqsimlash"

msgid "Improving the website through analytics"
msgstr "Tahlillar orqali veb-saytni yaxshilash"

msgid "Complying with legal obligations under Uzbekistan law"
msgstr "O'zbekiston qonunchiligiga muvofiq huquqiy majburiyatlarni bajarish"

msgid "Issuing Letters of Invitation for visa purposes"
msgstr "Viza maqsadlarida taklif xatlarini berish"

msgid "4. Legal Basis for Processing"
msgstr "4. Qayta ishlashning huquqiy asosi"

msgid ""
"We process your data based on: your consent (when you submit forms or "
"applications), contractual necessity (enrollment agreements, educational "
"services), legal obligation (reporting to ministries, tax authorities), and "
"legitimate interest (website security, fraud prevention). You can withdraw "
"consent at any time for consent-based processing."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlaringizni quyidagi asoslarda qayta ishlaymiz: sizning roziligingiz "
"(shakl yoki ariza topshirganingizda), shartnomaviy zarurat (ro'yxatdan "
"o'tish kelishuvi, ta'lim xizmatlari), qonuniy majburiyat (vazirliklarga, "
"soliq organlariga hisobot), qonuniy manfaat (veb-sayt xavfsizligi, "
"firibgarlikni oldini olish). Rozilikka asoslangan qayta ishlash uchun "
"roziligingizni istalgan vaqtda qaytarib olishingiz mumkin."

msgid "5. Data Sharing"
msgstr "5. Ma'lumotlarni almashish"

msgid "We do not sell your personal data. We may share data with:"
msgstr ""
"Biz shaxsiy ma'lumotlaringizni sotmaymiz. Quyidagilarga ma'lumot uzatishimiz"
" mumkin:"

msgid "Partner universities"
msgstr "Hamkor universitetlar"

msgid "for 2+2 and exchange programs (with your consent)"
msgstr "2+2 va almashinuv dasturlari uchun (sizning roziligingiz bilan)"

msgid "Government authorities"
msgstr "Davlat organlari"

msgid ""
"as required by Uzbekistan law (Ministry of Higher Education, tax, migration)"
msgstr ""
"O'zbekiston qonuni talab qilganida (Oliy ta'lim vazirligi, soliq, "
"migratsiya)"

msgid "Service providers"
msgstr "Xizmat ko'rsatuvchilar"

msgid "hosting, email, analytics, payment processing (under data agreements)"
msgstr ""
"xosting, elektron pochta, tahlillar, to'lovlarni qayta ishlash (ma'lumotlar "
"shartnomasi asosida)"

msgid "6. Data Retention"
msgstr "6. Ma'lumotlarni saqlash"

msgid ""
"We keep data only as long as necessary. Student academic records are "
"retained permanently as required by education law. Application data for non-"
"enrolled applicants is kept for 3 years. Financial records are kept for 5 "
"years. Website analytics data is retained for 26 months in anonymized form. "
"After retention periods expire, data is securely deleted."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlarni faqat zarur bo'lgan muddatda saqlaymiz. Talabalarning akademik"
" yozuvlari ta'lim qonuni talabiga ko'ra doimiy saqlanadi. Qabul qilinmagan "
"abituriyentlar ma'lumotlari 3 yil saqlanadi. Moliyaviy yozuvlar 5 yil "
"saqlanadi. Veb-sayt tahlil ma'lumotlari 26 oy davomida anonim shaklda "
"saqlanadi. Saqlash muddati tugagandan so'ng ma'lumotlar xavfsiz tarzda "
"o'chiriladi."

msgid "7. Data Security"
msgstr "7. Ma'lumotlar xavfsizligi"

msgid ""
"We protect your data with SSL/TLS encryption, access controls, regular "
"security audits, firewalls, and staff training. Access to personal data is "
"limited to authorized personnel only. In case of a data breach, we will "
"notify affected individuals and relevant authorities as required by "
"Uzbekistan law."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlaringizni SSL/TLS shifrlash, kirish nazorati, muntazam xavfsizlik "
"tekshiruvlari, xavfsizlik devorlari va xodimlar treningi bilan himoya "
"qilamiz. Shaxsiy ma'lumotlarga faqat vakolatli xodimlar kirishi mumkin. "
"Xavfsizlik buzilishi yuz bergan taqdirda, O'zbekiston qonuniga muvofiq "
"ta'sirlangan shaxslarga va tegishli organlarga xabar beramiz."

msgid "8. Your Rights"
msgstr "8. Sizning huquqlaringiz"

msgid ""
"Under the Law on Personal Data of the Republic of Uzbekistan, you have the "
"right to:"
msgstr ""
"O'zbekiston Respublikasining Shaxsiy ma'lumotlar to'g'risidagi qonuniga "
"ko'ra siz quyidagi huquqlarga egasiz:"

msgid "Access the personal data we hold about you"
msgstr "Biz saqlayotgan shaxsiy ma'lumotlaringizga kirish"

msgid "Request correction of inaccurate data"
msgstr "Noto'g'ri ma'lumotlarni tuzatishni so'rash"

msgid ""
"Request deletion of your data (subject to legal retention requirements)"
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlaringizni o'chirilishini so'rash (qonuniy saqlash talablariga "
"bo'ysungan holda)"

msgid "Withdraw consent for data processing at any time"
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlarni qayta ishlash uchun rozilikni istalgan vaqtda qaytarib olish"

msgid "Object to marketing communications"
msgstr "Marketing xabarnomalariga e'tiroz bildirish"

msgid ""
"To exercise your rights, email privacy@tiu.uz. We will respond within 30 "
"calendar days."
msgstr ""
"Huquqlaringizdan foydalanish uchun privacy@tiu.uz ga yozing. 30 kalendar kun"
" ichida javob beramiz."

msgid "9. Cookies"
msgstr "9. Cookie fayllari"

msgid ""
"We use cookies to improve your experience: essential cookies for website "
"functionality, analytics cookies for usage statistics, and preference "
"cookies for your settings. You can manage cookies through your browser. We "
"may use Google Analytics for anonymous traffic analysis. Disabling essential"
" cookies may affect functionality."
msgstr ""
"Tajribangizni yaxshilash uchun cookie fayllaridan foydalanamiz: veb-sayt "
"ishlashi uchun zaruriy cookie'lar, foydalanish statistikasi uchun tahliliy "
"cookie'lar va sozlamalaringiz uchun afzallik cookie'lari. Cookie'larni "
"brauzer orqali boshqarishingiz mumkin. Anonim trafik tahlili uchun Google "
"Analytics ishlatishimiz mumkin. Zaruriy cookie'larni o'chirish "
"funksionallikka ta'sir qilishi mumkin."

msgid "10. Third-Party Links"
msgstr "10. Uchinchi tomon havolalari"

msgid ""
"Our website may link to external sites (partner universities, social media, "
"government portals). We are not responsible for their privacy practices. "
"Review their policies before sharing personal data."
msgstr ""
"Veb-saytimizda tashqi saytlarga (hamkor universitetlar, ijtimoiy tarmoqlar, "
"davlat portallari) havolalar bo'lishi mumkin. Ularning maxfiylik "
"amaliyotlari uchun javobgar emasmiz. Shaxsiy ma'lumotlar almashishdan oldin "
"ularning siyosatlarini ko'rib chiqing."

msgid "11. Children's Privacy"
msgstr "11. Bolalar maxfiyligi"

msgid ""
"The website is not directed at children under 16. We do not knowingly "
"collect data from children under 16. If we discover such data was collected "
"without proper consent, it will be deleted promptly. For applicants aged "
"16–18, parental consent may be required."
msgstr ""
"Veb-sayt 16 yoshdan kichik bolalarga mo'ljallanmagan. 16 yoshdan kichik "
"bolalardan ataylab ma'lumot to'plamaymiz. Agar bunday ma'lumotlar tegishli "
"rozilik bo'lmadan to'planganligi ma'lum bo'lsa, ular zudlik bilan "
"o'chiriladi. 16–18 yoshdagi abituriyentlar uchun ota-onaning roziligi talab "
"qilinishi mumkin."

msgid "12. Changes to This Policy"
msgstr "12. Siyosatdagi o'zgarishlar"

msgid ""
"We may update this policy at any time. Changes are posted on this page with "
"an updated date. Material changes will be communicated through a website "
"notice or email. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes "
"acceptance."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu siyosatni istalgan vaqtda yangilashimiz mumkin. O'zgarishlar "
"yangilangan sana bilan ushbu sahifada e'lon qilinadi. Muhim o'zgarishlar "
"haqida veb-sayt xabarnomasi yoki elektron pochta orqali xabar beriladi. "
"O'zgarishlardan keyin veb-saytdan foydalanishni davom ettirish yangilangan "
"siyosatni qabul qilish hisoblanadi."

msgid "13. Governing Law"
msgstr "13. Amaldagi qonunchilik"

msgid ""
"This Privacy Policy is governed by the laws of the Republic of Uzbekistan, "
"in particular the Law on Personal Data. Disputes shall be resolved through "
"direct communication with TIU first, then through the competent courts of "
"the Republic of Uzbekistan in Tashkent."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu Maxfiylik siyosati O'zbekiston Respublikasi qonunlari, xususan Shaxsiy"
" ma'lumotlar to'g'risidagi qonun asosida boshqariladi. Nizolar avvalo TIU "
"bilan bevosita muloqot orqali, keyin Toshkent shahridagi O'zbekiston "
"Respublikasi vakolatli sudlari orqali hal etiladi."

msgid "For questions about this Privacy Policy or your personal data:"
msgstr ""
"Maxfiylik siyosati yoki shaxsiy ma'lumotlaringiz bo'yicha savollar uchun:"

msgid "Data Protection Office"
msgstr "Ma'lumotlarni himoya qilish bo'limi"

msgid ""
"Critical thinking, global perspectives, and real-world impact — preparing "
"students for careers in legal practice, diplomacy, policy, and justice."
msgstr ""
"Tanqidiy fikrlash, xalqaro nuqtai nazar va amaliy ta'sir — talabalarni "
"yuridik amaliyot, diplomatiya, siyosat va adolat sohasidagi kareraga "
"tayyorlash."

msgid "Welcome from the Dean"
msgstr "Dekan so'zi"

msgid ""
"At the Faculty of Jurisprudence, we believe that understanding people, "
"societies, and systems of justice is the foundation for meaningful change."
msgstr ""
"Huquqshunoslik fakultetida biz insonlarni, jamiyatni va adolat tizimlarini "
"tushunish — mazmunli o'zgarishlarning poydevori deb bilamiz."

msgid ""
"Our scholars bring together expertise in international law, public law, "
"human rights, and constitutional studies — creating an environment where "
"students learn to think critically, argue persuasively, and act with "
"purpose."
msgstr ""
"Olimlarimiz xalqaro huquq, ommaviy huquq, inson huquqlari va "
"konstitutsiyaviy tadqiqotlar bo'yicha tajribani birlashtiradi. Natijada "
"talabalar tanqidiy fikrlash, ishonchli dalil keltirish va maqsadli harakat "
"qilishni o'rganadigan muhit yaratilgan."

msgid ""
"I'm proud of the community we've built — one that values diverse "
"perspectives, rigorous inquiry, and a genuine commitment to making Central "
"Asia and the wider world a more just place."
msgstr ""
"Biz yaratgan jamoadan faxrlanaman — turli nuqtai nazarlarni qadrlaydigan, "
"chuqur izlanishga intiluvchi va Markaziy Osiyo hamda butun dunyoni "
"adolatliroq qilishga chin dildan bel bog'lagan jamoa."

msgid ""
"Understanding people, societies, and systems of justice is the foundation "
"for meaningful change."
msgstr ""
"Insonlarni, jamiyatni va adolat tizimlarini tushunish — mazmunli "
"o'zgarishlarning poydevori."

msgid "Dean of Faculty"
msgstr "Fakultet dekani"

msgid ""
"Innovation, digital transformation, and industry-driven programs — taught "
"entirely in English by internationally experienced faculty."
msgstr ""
"Innovatsiya, raqamli transformatsiya va sohaga yo'naltirilgan dasturlar — "
"xalqaro tajribaga ega professor-o'qituvchilar tomonidan to'liq ingliz tilida"
" olib boriladi."

msgid ""
"At the Faculty of Business and Innovative Education, we live by the "
"principles that guide every modern organization: innovation, digital "
"transformation, and responsible leadership."
msgstr ""
"Biznes va innovatsion ta'lim fakultetida biz har bir zamonaviy tashkilotga "
"yo'l ko'rsatadigan tamoyillar asosida ishlaymiz: innovatsiya, raqamli "
"transformatsiya va mas'uliyatli yetakchilik."

msgid ""
"Our commitment to industry-relevant education is at the heart of everything "
"we do. We aim to make a lasting impact on technology, business, and "
"education — building connections with partners who share this vision."
msgstr ""
"Sohaga mos ta'limga sadoqatimiz barcha ishlarimiz markazida turadi. "
"Texnologiya, biznes va ta'limga uzoq muddatli ta'sir ko'rsatishni maqsad "
"qilganmiz — bu maqsadni baham ko'radigan hamkorlar bilan aloqalar "
"o'rnatamiz."

msgid ""
"I'm proud that our values have been recognized through a growing network of "
"international partnerships. The true measure of what we do is the impact our"
" colleagues, students, and alumni make in the world."
msgstr ""
"Qadriyatlarimiz tobora kengayib borayotgan xalqaro hamkorlik tarmog'i orqali"
" tan olinganidan faxrlanaman. Ishimizning haqiqiy mezoni — hamkasblarimiz, "
"talabalarimiz va bitiruvchilarimizning dunyodagi ta'siri."

msgid ""
"We aim to make a lasting impact on technology, business, and education — "
"building connections with partners who share this vision."
msgstr ""
"Texnologiya, biznes va ta'limga uzoq muddatli ta'sir ko'rsatishni maqsad "
"qilganmiz — bu maqsadni baham ko'radigan hamkorlar bilan aloqalar "
"o'rnatamiz."

msgid ""
"As a young and fast-growing university founded in 2023, TIU is building a "
"vibrant student community from the ground up. Our clubs and societies are "
"where friendships form, ideas come to life, and you find your place on "
"campus."
msgstr ""
"2023-yilda tashkil etilgan yosh va tez rivojlanayotgan universitet sifatida "
"TIU jonli talabalar jamoasini noldan quryapti. Klublar va to'garaklar — "
"do'stliklar boshlanadigan, g'oyalar hayotga kiruvchi va kampusda o'z "
"o'rningizni topadigan joy."

msgid ""
"From debate and programming to photography and volunteering, TIU's growing "
"list of clubs gives you the chance to explore your interests outside the "
"classroom and develop skills that employers value."
msgstr ""
"Munozara va dasturlashdan fotografiya va ko'ngillilikkacha — TIUning tobora "
"kengayayotgan klublar ro'yxati qiziqishlaringizni sinf tashqarisida "
"o'rganish va ish beruvchilar qadrlaydigan ko'nikmalar rivojlantirish "
"imkonini beradi."

msgid ""
"TIU currently has over 10 active student clubs, and the number keeps growing"
" every semester. Each club is student-led and open to all enrolled students,"
" regardless of department or year of study."
msgstr ""
"TIUda hozirda 10 dan ortiq faol talabalar klubi bor va ularning soni har "
"semestrda o'sib bormoqda. Har bir klub talabalar tomonidan boshqariladi va "
"kafedra yoki kursdan qat'i nazar barcha talabalarga ochiq."

msgid ""
"Whether you join a casual meetup or a competitive team, clubs are the "
"perfect way to make friends, build leadership skills, and add value to your "
"CV."
msgstr ""
"Erkin uchrashuv yoki raqobatli jamoaga qo'shilsangiz ham, klublar do'stlar "
"orttirish, yetakchilik ko'nikmalarini mustahkamlash va rezyumengizga qiymat "
"qo'shishning eng yaxshi yo'li."

msgid ""
"You'll be supported by dedicated club coordinators and TIU staff who help "
"students organise events, secure funding, and grow their clubs into lasting "
"communities."
msgstr ""
"Maxsus klub koordinatorlari va TIU xodimlari tadbirlar tashkil etish, "
"moliyalashtirish topish va klublarni barqaror jamoalarga aylantirish "
"bo'yicha yordam beradi."

msgid ""
"Don't see anything that suits you? At TIU, you can start your own club with "
"just 5 interested students. We'll help you get it off the ground."
msgstr ""
"Sizga mos narsa topa olmadingizmi? TIUda atigi 5 qiziquvchi talaba bilan o'z"
" klubingizni ochishingiz mumkin. Boshlashda yordam beramiz."

msgid ""
"Whether it's a robotics club, a book circle, a music group, or anything else"
" you're passionate about — TIU supports student initiative and creativity."
msgstr ""
"Robototexnika klubi, kitob to'garagi, musiqa guruhi yoki boshqa "
"qiziqishingiz bo'lsin — TIU talabalar tashabbusi va ijodkorligini qo'llab-"
"quvvatlaydi."

msgid ""
"TIU's Student Union represents the voice of all students. Every enrolled "
"student is automatically a member."
msgstr ""
"TIU Talabalar ittifoqi barcha talabalarning ovozini ifodalaydi. Ro'yxatdan "
"o'tgan har bir talaba avtomatik ravishda a'zo hisoblanadi."

msgid ""
"The Student Union organizes events, supports club activities, and ensures "
"student interests are represented in university decisions."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar ittifoqi tadbirlar tashkil etadi, klublar faoliyatini qo'llab-"
"quvvatlaydi va universitet qarorlarida talabalar manfaatlarini ifodalaydi."

msgid ""
"From cultural events and sports days to community projects, the Student "
"Union is at the heart of campus life."
msgstr ""
"Madaniy tadbirlar va sport kunlaridan jamoatchilik loyihalarigacha — "
"Talabalar ittifoqi kampus hayotining markazida."

msgid ""
"TIU is a young university, founded in 2023, and our sports programme is "
"growing every semester. We believe physical activity is essential for "
"academic success — it clears the mind, builds discipline, and creates "
"friendships that last beyond the classroom."
msgstr ""
"TIU — 2023-yilda tashkil etilgan yosh universitet va sport dasturimiz har "
"semestrda rivojlanmoqda. Jismoniy faollik akademik muvaffaqiyat uchun zarur "
"deb bilamiz — u ongni tiniqlashtiradi, intizomni shakllantiradi va sinf "
"tashqarisida ham davom etadigan do'stliklar yaratadi."

msgid ""
"We offer football, basketball, volleyball, table tennis, and regular fitness"
" classes. Our Sports Coordinator organises inter-faculty tournaments and "
"friendly matches throughout the academic year."
msgstr ""
"Futbol, basketbol, voleybol, stol tennisi va muntazam fitnes mashg'ulotlari "
"taklif qilamiz. Sport koordinatorimiz o'quv yili davomida fakultetlararo "
"turnirlar va do'stona o'yinlar tashkil qiladi."

msgid ""
"You do not need to be a professional to join. Our teams train regularly in "
"the multi-court sports hall and outdoor pitches, and everyone — from "
"beginners to experienced players — is welcome."
msgstr ""
"Qo'shilish uchun professional bo'lish shart emas. Jamoalarimiz ko'p tarmoqli"
" sport zalida va ochiq maydonlarda muntazam mashq qiladi. Boshlovchilardan "
"tortib tajribali o'yinchilargacha — hamma kutiladi."

msgid ""
"As a growing university, we are steadily expanding our sports "
"infrastructure. All facilities are free for enrolled TIU students."
msgstr ""
"Rivojlanayotgan universitet sifatida sport infratuzilmamizni bosqichma-"
"bosqich kengaytiryapmiz. Barcha inshootlar ro'yxatdan o'tgan TIU talabalari "
"uchun bepul."

msgid ""
"Training times and fitness class schedules are posted on the LMS portal and "
"the sports noticeboard in the main building."
msgstr ""
"Mashg'ulot vaqtlari va fitnes darslar jadvali LMS portalida va bosh "
"binongizdagi sport e'lon taxtasida joylashtiriladi."

msgid ""
"Most sessions are open to everyone. Just come to the sports hall or gym at "
"the listed time — no registration needed for recreational sessions."
msgstr ""
"Aksariyat mashg'ulotlar hamma uchun ochiq. Sport zali yoki trenajyor zaliga "
"ko'rsatilgan vaqtda keling — dam olish mashg'ulotlari uchun ro'yxatdan "
"o'tish shart emas."

msgid ""
"If you want to compete in inter-faculty tournaments, speak to the team "
"captain or the Sports Coordinator in the Student Affairs office."
msgstr ""
"Fakultetlararo turnirlarda qatnashmoqchi bo'lsangiz, jamoa sardori yoki "
"Talabalar ishlari bo'limidagi Sport koordinatori bilan gaplashing."

msgid ""
"Not at all. Our teams welcome all skill levels. Recreational sessions are "
"open to complete beginners, and competitive teams will help you develop "
"through regular training."
msgstr ""
"Umuman yo'q. Jamoalarimiz barcha darajadagi o'yinchilarni kutib oladi. Dam "
"olish mashg'ulotlari mutlaqo boshlovchilar uchun ochiq, raqobatli jamoalar "
"esa muntazam mashqlar orqali rivojlanishingizga yordam beradi."

msgid ""
"Yes. All on-campus sports facilities are free for enrolled TIU students. "
"Just bring your student ID when you visit the gym or sports hall."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Kampusdagi barcha sport inshootlari ro'yxatdan o'tgan TIU talabalari "
"uchun bepul. Trenajyor zali yoki sport zaliga kelganingizda talaba "
"guvohnomangizni olib keling."

msgid ""
"The gym and sports hall are open Monday to Saturday, 08:00–21:00. Team "
"training sessions are scheduled separately and posted on the LMS."
msgstr ""
"Trenajyor zali va sport zali dushanbadan shanbagacha, 08:00–21:00 ochiq. "
"Jamoaviy mashqlar alohida rejalashtiriladi va LMSda e'lon qilinadi."

msgid ""
"Yes. If you have at least 5 interested students, you can propose a new team "
"through the Student Union. The Sports Coordinator will help with scheduling "
"and equipment."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Kamida 5 qiziquvchi talaba bo'lsa, Talabalar ittifoqi orqali yangi jamoa"
" taklif qilishingiz mumkin. Sport koordinatori jadval va jihozlar bo'yicha "
"yordam beradi."

msgid ""
"Tashkent International University's Student Union — Talabalar Kengashi — is "
"the student-led body that represents all enrolled students. Every TIU "
"student is automatically a member."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent xalqaro universitetining Talabalar ittifoqi — Talabalar Kengashi — "
"barcha ro'yxatdan o'tgan talabalarni ifodalovchi talabalar boshqaruv organi."
" Har bir TIU talabasi avtomatik ravishda a'zo hisoblanadi."

msgid ""
"Our mission is simple: represent student interests, organize memorable "
"events, and serve as the bridge between students and university "
"administration."
msgstr ""
"Vazifamiz oddiy: talabalar manfaatlarini ifodalash, esda qolarli tadbirlar "
"tashkil etish va talabalar bilan universitet ma'muriyati o'rtasida ko'prik "
"bo'lish."

msgid ""
"The Student Union is where your ideas turn into real campus life. We are a "
"small but active team, and we are always looking for new voices and fresh "
"ideas."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar ittifoqi — g'oyalaringiz haqiqiy kampus hayotiga aylanadigan joy. "
"Biz kichik, ammo faol jamoamiz va doimo yangi ovozlar va yangi g'oyalar "
"kutamiz."

msgid ""
"The Student Union is run entirely by students. Our elected leaders work "
"closely with the university to improve campus life, support clubs and "
"societies, and make sure every student's voice is heard."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar ittifoqi to'liq talabalar tomonidan boshqariladi. Saylangan "
"yetakchilarimiz kampus hayotini yaxshilash, klublar va to'garaklarni "
"qo'llab-quvvatlash va har bir talabaning ovozi eshitilishini ta'minlash "
"uchun universitet bilan yaqin hamkorlik qiladi."

msgid ""
"Join a club, play sports, or volunteer — these are the best ways to find "
"your people at TIU."
msgstr ""
"Klubga qo'shiling, sport bilan shug'ullaning yoki ko'ngillilik qiling — "
"TIUda o'z odamlaringizni topishning eng yaxshi yo'llari."

msgid ""
"The Student Union represents your interests — from course feedback to "
"university decisions that affect your daily life."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar ittifoqi manfaatlaringizni ifodalaydi — dars bo'yicha fikr-"
"mulohazalardan tortib kundalik hayotingizga ta'sir qiladigan universitet "
"qarorlarigacha."

msgid ""
"From Navro'z celebrations and sport tournaments to cultural evenings and "
"end-of-year festivals — the Student Union is behind the events that make TIU"
" special."
msgstr ""
"Navro'z bayramlaridan sport turnirlarigacha, madaniy kechalardan yil "
"yakunidagi festivallargacha — TIUni o'ziga xos qiladigan tadbirlar ortida "
"Talabalar ittifoqi turadi."

msgid ""
"The Student Union serves as your direct link to the university "
"administration. If you have concerns, suggestions, or ideas — we will make "
"sure they are heard at the right level."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar ittifoqi — sizning universitet ma'muriyati bilan bevosita "
"aloqangiz. Tashvishlaringiz, takliflaringiz yoki g'oyalaringiz bo'lsa — "
"ularning tegishli darajada eshitilishini ta'minlaymiz."

msgid ""
"The Student Union office is located in the main building. Drop by during "
"working hours — our team is always happy to chat."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar ittifoqi ofisi bosh binoda joylashgan. Ish vaqtida tashrif "
"buyuring — jamoamiz doimo gaplashishga tayyor."

msgid ""
"Take a virtual tour of our modern campus, student spaces, and Tashkent "
"itself: a city that quickly feels like home."
msgstr ""
"Zamonaviy kampusimiz, talabalar makonlari va Toshkentning o'zi — tezda uyga "
"aylangan shahar — bo'ylab virtual sayohat qiling."

msgid "Building A — Main Academic Building"
msgstr "A bino — Asosiy o'quv binosi"

msgid ""
"Lecture halls, seminar rooms, faculty offices, IT Help Desk, computer labs"
msgstr ""
"Ma'ruza zallari, seminar xonalari, kafedra xonalari, AT yordam markazi, "
"kompyuter laboratoriyalari"

msgid "Building B — Coworking & Student Spaces"
msgstr "B bino — Kovorking va talabalar makoni"

msgid ""
"Coworking areas, group study rooms, Student Union office, recreation zone"
msgstr ""
"Kovorking hududlari, guruh o'quv xonalari, Talabalar ittifoqi ofisi, dam "
"olish zonasi"

msgid "Library & Information Resource Center"
msgstr "Kutubxona va Axborot-resurs markazi"

msgid ""
"5,000+ books, digital databases, quiet study zones, group rooms, printing "
"services"
msgstr ""
"5000+ kitob, raqamli bazalar, tinch o'quv hududlari, guruh xonalari, chop "
"etish xizmati"

msgid ""
"Gym, multi-court sports hall, outdoor pitches, table tennis, changing rooms"
msgstr ""
"Trenajyor zali, ko'p tarmoqli sport zali, ochiq maydonchalar, stol tennisi, "
"kiyinish xonalari"

msgid "Affordable meals, snacks, and beverages served daily"
msgstr "Har kuni arzon narxdagi taomlar, yengil ovqatlar va ichimliklar"

msgid "Administration & Admissions"
msgstr "Ma'muriyat va Qabul bo'limi"

msgid "Admissions office, finance, student services, Rector's Reception"
msgstr "Qabul bo'limi, moliya, talabalar xizmati, Rektor qabulxonasi"

msgid "Medical Point"
msgstr "Tibbiy punkt"

msgid "First aid, basic consultations, and referrals during working hours"
msgstr "Ish vaqtida birinchi yordam, asosiy konsultatsiyalar va yo'naltirish"

msgid ""
"The heart of TIU. Building A houses all lecture halls, seminar rooms, "
"faculty offices, computer labs, and the IT Help Desk. Smart classrooms are "
"equipped with projectors, interactive screens, and comfortable seating for "
"up to 100 students."
msgstr ""
"TIUning yuragi. A binoda barcha ma'ruza zallari, seminar xonalari, kafedra "
"xonalari, kompyuter laboratoriyalari va AT yordam markazi joylashgan. Aqlli "
"o'quv xonalari proyektorlar, interaktiv ekranlar va 100 tagacha talaba uchun"
" qulay o'rindiqlar bilan jihozlangan."

msgid ""
"A modern space for independent study, group projects, and student life. "
"Building B features open coworking areas, the Student Union office, a "
"recreation zone with foosball and lounge seating, and meeting rooms "
"available for booking."
msgstr ""
"Mustaqil o'qish, guruh loyihalari va talabalar hayoti uchun zamonaviy makon."
" B binoda ochiq kovorking hududlari, Talabalar ittifoqi ofisi, kicker va dam"
" olish o'rindiqlari bilan jihozlangan dam olish zonasi va band qilish mumkin"
" bo'lgan yig'ilishlar xonalari mavjud."

msgid ""
"Over 5,000 books and journals, access to JSTOR and other digital databases, "
"quiet study zones, group study rooms, computer stations, and printing "
"services. Open Monday–Saturday, with extended hours during exams."
msgstr ""
"5000 dan ortiq kitob va jurnallar, JSTOR va boshqa raqamli bazalarga kirish,"
" tinch o'quv hududlari, guruh xonalari, kompyuter stantsiyalari va chop "
"etish xizmatlari. Dushanba–shanba ochiq, imtihon davrida ish vaqti "
"uzaytiriladi."

msgid "Cafeteria & Dining"
msgstr "Oshxona va ovqatlanish"

msgid ""
"Fresh, affordable meals throughout the day — hot dishes, salads, snacks, and"
" beverages. Vegetarian and dietary options available. Seating for 150+ "
"students."
msgstr ""
"Kun davomida arzon va yangi taomlar — issiq ovqatlar, salatlar, yengil "
"taomlar va ichimliklar. Vegetarian va parhez variantlari mavjud. 150+ talaba"
" uchun o'rindiqlar."

msgid "Campus Buildings & Facilities"
msgstr "Kampus binolari va inshootlari"

msgid "How to get here"
msgstr "Qanday yetib kelish"
